    'https://us02web.zoom.us/j/85981404687?pwd=bdGJJvxEEtXnHHUUrFY8E5xxPuTASI.1',
    '{"id":"01KG2Q7RA0J2CK5SHAFTDEQP47","title":"Powerhouse Gym & Ideometry: Weekly Sync","summary":{"notes":"## **Geotargeted Advertising Strategy**\n\nThe team agreed to launch a geofencing ad campaign targeting competitors’ gym locations to increase qualified leads.\n\n- **Milan Wagner** emphasized the need to boost leads beyond the current average of **4–5 leads per day** across both clubs, proposing a new geotagged campaign to capture members from competitor gyms in Miami (05:08).\n    - The campaign will highlight unique benefits like month-to-month memberships, gym cleanliness, and group fitness classes to entice members to switch.\n    - Targeting will focus on specific gym addresses and zip codes to maximize relevance and reach.\n    - Milan committed to compiling a list of **6–8 competitor gyms** within a **10-minute drive radius** to segment and tailor ads effectively.\n    - The campaign aims to replicate successful geofencing done previously for a freight client, which showed lasting lead generation even after campaign end.\n    \n- **Yefei Jin** proposed financial incentives such as discounting the first three months or partially buying out competitor contracts to attract switchers, stressing the importance of understanding competitor membership terms and cancellation policies (16:35).\n    - He recommended focusing on gyms with higher prices than Powerhouse to compete mainly on price and value.\n    - Milan will research competitor contract terms and pricing to develop tailored offers for each target location.\n    - Yefei suggested also targeting corporate office buildings with dedicated membership offers, leveraging office proximity and employee concentration to generate leads with minimal new creative work (22:51).\n    - Milan will provide a list of corporate buildings for a separate ad campaign with messaging adjusted for corporate memberships.\n\n- **Nina Belina** confirmed technical feasibility, explaining that geo-targeting can be done at building-level addresses and highlighted prior success with such campaigns (20:21).\n    - She advised broadening location scope as much as possible to avoid overly narrow audiences.\n    - Nina will consult the paid media specialist for the best approach on whether to integrate geofencing into existing campaigns or create new ones.\n\n## **Ad Creative and Campaign Structure**\n\nThe team will test multiple creative formats to determine the most effective ad types for lead generation.\n\n- Milan requested delivery of the **group fitness video** and photo creatives to run split tests comparing video versus static image ad performance (12:23).\n    - Nina confirmed that due to technical constraints, campaigns must be separated by asset type (video-only campaign and image-only campaign).\n    - Yefei endorsed testing both formats over a **one-week period** to quickly identify the best performers.\n    - Creative messaging for group fitness will focus on **new class formats** recently launched, leveraging Instagram content for inspiration (50:08).\n\n- For corporate campaigns, Yefei emphasized simple messaging tweaks without needing new video production, aiming for quick deployment (23:26).\n    - Leads generated from corporate ads will be routed directly to Milan for follow-up.\n\n## **Lead Volume, Cost, and Budget Management**\n\nCurrent lead volume is below target, but cost per lead metrics show promising opportunities to scale effectively.\n\n- Nina reported that January yielded **334 total leads** across both clubs, short of the **600 leads monthly target** (about **20 leads per day**) that Milan and Yefei agreed would be sufficient to meet business goals (39:41).\n    - The conversion rate for leads currently ranges between **4% and 10%**, with a goal to increase closing rates to **15–20%** by improving lead quality (37:45).\n    - The current average daily ad spend is approximately **$114**, with a monthly budget of around **$4,000** for both clubs combined (31:52).\n    - Cost per lead varies by audience, with the best-performing segment (18–24 years old) at **$7.37 per lead**, while older demographics cost up to **$26 per lead** (25:11).\n    \n- Yefei stressed the importance of rapid budget adjustments when favorable cost per lead trends emerge, recommending doubling or tripling spend on ads consistently below **$8 per lead** to maximize lead volume quickly (29:50).\n    - Nina agreed to set up Slack reminders to alert Milan when cost per lead falls below this threshold for prompt action.\n    - Milan monitors daily ad performance himself and will flag opportunities to increase budgets immediately.\n    - The team agreed to keep ad schedules flexible, allowing ads to run outside the previous **8am–8pm window** to capture leads during off-hours if advised by the media specialist (44:31).\n\n- Nina will have the paid media specialist review current campaigns to identify what changes (budget, targeting, ad content) are needed to reach the **20 leads per day** goal sustainably (40:15).\n    - The review will also benchmark competitor ad tactics to find gaps and opportunities for improvement.\n    - Milan highlighted that lead form issues from previous campaigns had suppressed lead volume and that reverting to a more reliable form workflow helped stabilize results (41:56).\n\n## **SMS Campaign Compliance and Automation Improvements**\n\nCompliance and workflow automation for SMS lead capture are being finalized to ensure legal and operational readiness.\n\n- Nina is coordinating with a Squarespace developer to add a **privacy policy and terms** specific to SMS campaigns on the website, addressing previous compliance gaps (10:18).\n    - The SMS privacy policy will clarify opt-in/out processes, message frequency, and data use, tailored beyond the general website terms.\n    - Milan will confirm completion before final launch and integrate the updated link into the SMS form.\n    \n- Milan discovered irregularities in the **HubSpot lead workflow**, where Fort Lauderdale leads were incorrectly assigned and reassigned to Felipe’s list multiple times (45:51).\n    - Nina will task the developer to investigate and fix automation inconsistencies causing duplicate or misrouted leads.\n    - They verified that contact details are complete, indicating the issue is likely in workflow configuration rather than data gaps.\n\n## **Process Coordination and Next Steps**\n\nClear assignments and timelines were established to accelerate campaign launches and improve reporting.\n\n- Milan will compile and send lists of competitor gyms and corporate buildings with pricing and contract details for geofencing and corporate campaigns respectively (22:28, 24:00).\n- Nina will confirm with the paid media specialist whether to integrate geofencing into existing campaigns or create new ones and advise on ad scheduling and budget adjustments (07:54, 44:44).\n- Nina will request a comprehensive media specialist review to provide recommendations on increasing lead volume to **600 monthly**, including budget and competitor analysis (40:15).\n- Milan will deliver the group fitness video and coordinate production of one or two photo creatives for split testing (12:36).\n- Nina will notify Milan when SMS privacy policy updates are live to proceed with final approvals and campaign activation (12:12, 49:36).\n- Milan and Nina will monitor daily lead costs and volumes, using Slack alerts to rapidly scale budgets for ads under **$8 per lead** (29:50).\n- The team aims to launch targeted geofencing and corporate campaigns by **February** to maximize early-year lead growth (24:43).","outline":null,"keywords":["Geofencing","Lead Generation","Meta Ads","SMS Campaign","HubSpot Workflow","Corporate Partnership"],"overview":"- **Geofencing Campaign:** Launch target ads at competitor gyms to boost daily leads beyond 4–5 per day and increase brand visibility.\n\n- **Financial Incentives:** Offer discounts for new members and explore corporate partnerships near office buildings to attract switchers.\n\n- **Lead Volume Goals:** January had 334 leads, below the target of 600; aim to improve lead quality and increase conversion rates to 15–20%.\n\n- **Ad Spend Strategy:** Monitor and adjust budget based on cost per lead; focus on leads under $8 to maximize volume.\n\n- **SMS Compliance:** Finalize SMS privacy policies for lead capture, ensuring legal adherence and improving customer trust.\n\n- **Campaign Launches:** Target to launch geofencing and corporate campaigns by February, ensuring strategic planning and resource allocation.","action_items":"\n**Milan Wagner**\nProvide list of competitor gym addresses and terms/conditions for Miami area geo-targeted ads (14:49)\nSource and deliver missing yoga and boxing videos for group fitness campaign to Nina (08:06)\nSend list of corporate office buildings for targeted corporate membership campaigns (23:59)\nMonitor Meta ad cost-per-lead daily and notify team to increase budget on low CPL ads (27:00)\nInvestigate and clarify issues with HubSpot lead workflow misassignments and communicate findings (45:51)\n\n**Nina Belina**\nConsult with paid media specialist on best approach for geofencing in existing vs. new ads (07:15)\nConfirm addition of SMS privacy policy specific to SMS campaigns on Squarespace and notify Milan upon completion (10:18)\nCoordinate with paid media specialist to advise on increasing lead volumes to reach 20 leads/day target and review budget recommendations (40:15)\nRequest developer to investigate HubSpot lead workflow problems reported by Milan (49:15)\nAdapt messaging for group fitness campaign based on Instagram content and prepare for launch (50:16)\n\n**Yefei Jin**\nReview geofencing strategy and proposed promotions, provide feedback on messaging and campaign direction (00:00)\nCollaborate with Milan and Nina to finalize ad budget scaling plan based on daily CPL monitoring (27:00)\n"},"duration":51.4900016784668,"speakers":[{"id":0,"name":"Milan Wagner"},{"id":1,"name":"Nina Belina"},{"id":2,"name":"Yefei Jin"}],"sentences":[{"text":"All your what?","index":0,"end_time":219.04,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":218.24,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Hello.","index":1,"end_time":271.46,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":271.14,"speaker_name":"Nina Belina"},{"text":"Hey Nina, how we doing?","index":2,"end_time":275.22,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":273.94,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Good.","index":3,"end_time":276.26,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":275.86,"speaker_name":"Nina Belina"},{"text":"I was just in another meeting and then it went a little bit longer than I expected.","index":4,"end_time":281.06,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":276.34,"speaker_name":"Nina Belina"},{"text":"You''re good, you''re good.","index":5,"end_time":284.04,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":282.84,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"I''ve been in meetings all morning, so.","index":6,"end_time":286.52,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":284.44,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Yeah, we''re both on the same page here.","index":7,"end_time":288.6,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":286.68,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"No, please talk to me.","index":8,"end_time":292.6,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":289.64,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Oh, so I wanted to discuss efe''s latest request about geofencing that.","index":9,"end_time":300.28,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":292.76,"speaker_name":"Nina Belina"},{"text":"So would this be for the existing ads that we have currently on in Meta or a new ad?","index":10,"end_time":307.88,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":300.84,"speaker_name":"Nina Belina"},{"text":"I, I would say we would want to do.","index":11,"end_time":312.21,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":308.93,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"I don''t know.","index":12,"end_time":315.81,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":315.25,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"It''s up to you what''s going to be the most cost efficient way.","index":13,"end_time":319.57,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":315.81,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"So there''s a couple things with ads too.","index":14,"end_time":321.57,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":319.65,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"We need more leads.","index":15,"end_time":323.97,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":322.69,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"So it''s been like, I think we''re like averaging four or five leads at the moment a day for both clubs.","index":16,"end_time":329.81,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":324.37,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"So that''s total.","index":17,"end_time":331.01,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":330.13,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"So we''re, we absolutely need more leads.","index":18,"end_time":334.05,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":331.73,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"So.","index":19,"end_time":334.27,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":334.05,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"So if this geotag thing is going to affect the number of leads with our current campaigns, then let''s create a new campaign for it.","index":20,"end_time":345.14,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":334.42,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Does that make sense?","index":21,"end_time":347.62,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":346.82,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Because, because IFE mentions like, if I understood correctly, like using specific copy that is relevant for the gyms that are located in that area.","index":22,"end_time":361.66,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":347.62,"speaker_name":"Nina Belina"},{"text":"Yes, correct.","index":23,"end_time":366.7,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":364.54,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"So what he''s, what he''s saying is like for example, our competitors mainly in Miami, we want to do like a geotagged campaign so that we can get their members and, and whatever, anybody who''s inquiring into those gyms as well.","index":24,"end_time":383.1,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":367.34,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"And what would be like the main selling point to get them to use a different gym?","index":25,"end_time":388.72,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":383.18,"speaker_name":"Nina Belina"},{"text":"Just our gyms, I guess our gyms benefits are different membership terms and conditions.","index":26,"end_time":399.68,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":390.24,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"So like the month to months, it would be the cleanliness of the gym.","index":27,"end_time":404.4,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":399.68,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"It''d be, it''d be different benefits, be group fitness, for example, all kinds of stuff.","index":28,"end_time":410.72,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":404.4,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"We would just want all of these people that are at other gyms and inquiring into other gyms to also see our gym before they make a decision or yeah, if they''re current members, like make a decision to switch over.","index":29,"end_time":427.29,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":412.73,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"To.","index":30,"end_time":430.29,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":430.01,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"All of our normal benefits of joining our gym.","index":31,"end_time":433.05,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":430.29,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"We would want them to see.","index":32,"end_time":434.09,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":433.05,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Basically.","index":33,"end_time":434.57,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":434.09,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":34,"end_time":436.01,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":435.53,"speaker_name":"Nina Belina"},{"text":"I will ask our paid media specialist what she thinks is best course of action.","index":35,"end_time":443.77,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":437.85,"speaker_name":"Nina Belina"},{"text":"Because we have been switching like we have been changing content within the two ads that we have running, which I think that we should leave to, you know, breathe a little bit.","index":36,"end_time":455.35,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":443.85,"speaker_name":"Nina Belina"},{"text":"But also she thinks that there''s a way of changing something when it comes to the way that we are targeting and making like narrowing it down to specific areas and that it would work Better.","index":37,"end_time":468.39,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":455.43,"speaker_name":"Nina Belina"},{"text":"Then we can also add it to those ads.","index":38,"end_time":470.9,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":468.79,"speaker_name":"Nina Belina"},{"text":"Okay, so then we are.","index":39,"end_time":476.97,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":474.41,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Okay, so you''re going to ask your media specialist whether we should do these kind of things to our current ads or do it to a different ad set.","index":40,"end_time":484.09,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":477.21,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Yeah, okay.","index":41,"end_time":485.69,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":484.09,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Yeah, that''s fine.","index":42,"end_time":486.41,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":485.69,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Also, for the video for yoga and boxing, I was looking through the Dropbox file and all I could find is, like, images.","index":43,"end_time":495.37,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":486.89,"speaker_name":"Nina Belina"},{"text":"So I''m not sure if there''s a video there.","index":44,"end_time":497.92,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":495.53,"speaker_name":"Nina Belina"},{"text":"The marketing folder that you shared, it.","index":45,"end_time":502.76,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":498.4,"speaker_name":"Nina Belina"},{"text":"Should be in there.","index":46,"end_time":503.6,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":502.76,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"That''s where all of it was.","index":47,"end_time":505.04,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":503.6,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Give me a second, let me.","index":48,"end_time":512.72,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":511.36,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"I can''t even remember where I sent it.","index":49,"end_time":517.36,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":515.44,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"So this is the Dropbox.","index":50,"end_time":529.77,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":528.57,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"And then it was the.","index":51,"end_time":531.21,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":529.77,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"I think it was the we share.","index":52,"end_time":532.73,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":531.37,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Did you go to the we share or we transfer?","index":53,"end_time":537.29,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":534.89,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"The we transfer.","index":54,"end_time":538.53,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":537.53,"speaker_name":"Nina Belina"},{"text":"It only had photos from the, like the photo shoot that we used in one of the ads.","index":55,"end_time":544.09,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":538.53,"speaker_name":"Nina Belina"},{"text":"Okay, I''m downloading it now.","index":56,"end_time":549.5,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":547.69,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Just double check.","index":57,"end_time":550.46,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":549.5,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"I thought the video was on there, so give me a second.","index":58,"end_time":554.7,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":551.58,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"It''s pretty annoying that they didn''t put everything together.","index":59,"end_time":562.14,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":559.74,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"I mean, they did put a lot, just not that video.","index":60,"end_time":566.86,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":564.299,"speaker_name":"Nina Belina"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":61,"end_time":569.1,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":568.62,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Hi.","index":62,"end_time":571.34,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":570.86,"speaker_name":"Nina Belina"},{"text":"Right.","index":63,"end_time":574.59,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":574.35,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"You know, I just requested it.","index":64,"end_time":603.56,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":602.28,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"I didn''t realize it wasn''t on that we share or we transfer.","index":65,"end_time":609.88,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":604.76,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Yeah, so I''ll get that over to you asap.","index":66,"end_time":616.56,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":614.12,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Okay, great.","index":67,"end_time":617.88,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":616.56,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"And also for the SMS campaign, I have one of our developers in Squarespace to add the privacy policy and terms and conditions.","index":68,"end_time":630.2,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":618.28,"speaker_name":"Nina Belina"},{"text":"So they''re on the website.","index":69,"end_time":631.4,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":630.36,"speaker_name":"Nina Belina"},{"text":"Because one of the things that I think that I mentioned previously that I''m not sure if you should be using the main Powerhouse website instead.","index":70,"end_time":640.68,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":631.88,"speaker_name":"Nina Belina"},{"text":"You also have like already a privacy policy on the.","index":71,"end_time":645.64,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":641.4,"speaker_name":"Nina Belina"},{"text":"On your own soflow page.","index":72,"end_time":649.16,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":647,"speaker_name":"Nina Belina"},{"text":"So maybe just to use that one when you''re filling in the form.","index":73,"end_time":653.32,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":649.16,"speaker_name":"Nina Belina"},{"text":"But you''re.","index":74,"end_time":655.85,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":655.41,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"You''re creating it now, right?","index":75,"end_time":657.45,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":655.85,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"No, no, there''s always.","index":76,"end_time":658.77,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":657.45,"speaker_name":"Nina Belina"},{"text":"You already have one.","index":77,"end_time":660.05,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":658.93,"speaker_name":"Nina Belina"},{"text":"But we need to add like the sms.","index":78,"end_time":663.25,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":660.05,"speaker_name":"Nina Belina"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":79,"end_time":664.09,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":663.65,"speaker_name":"Nina Belina"},{"text":"Just in case they.","index":80,"end_time":665.41,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":664.09,"speaker_name":"Nina Belina"},{"text":"They are a bit more detailed.","index":81,"end_time":667.09,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":665.49,"speaker_name":"Nina Belina"},{"text":"But just to kind of keep it in mind to use the SoFlo one and not the powerhouse gym dot com.","index":82,"end_time":672.29,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":667.09,"speaker_name":"Nina Belina"},{"text":"Yeah, yeah, of course.","index":83,"end_time":673.41,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":672.29,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Can you just update me when that''s done so I can.","index":84,"end_time":675.61,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":673.49,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Yeah, yeah.","index":85,"end_time":676.21,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":675.61,"speaker_name":"Nina Belina"},{"text":"The, the.","index":86,"end_time":678.29,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":676.45,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"The approval process.","index":87,"end_time":679.57,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":678.53,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Okay.","index":88,"end_time":680.96,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":680.56,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Do we feel.","index":89,"end_time":682.6,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":681.92,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Is this what we need to do to.","index":90,"end_time":684.08,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":682.6,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Yes.","index":91,"end_time":684.96,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":684.56,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Like, are we sure this was going to work?","index":92,"end_time":686.48,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":684.96,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"I think so.","index":93,"end_time":689.04,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":688.24,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":94,"end_time":689.96,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":689.52,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"I think that''s what we didn''t have last time, because when I did.","index":95,"end_time":693.44,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":689.96,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Yeah, go ahead.","index":96,"end_time":694.88,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":693.92,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Oh.","index":97,"end_time":695.48,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":695.04,"speaker_name":"Nina Belina"},{"text":"So the issue was that we.","index":98,"end_time":697.68,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":695.48,"speaker_name":"Nina Belina"},{"text":"The form was using the privacy policy and website terms of service that were relevant for the website and not for the SMS campaign.","index":99,"end_time":706.16,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":697.84,"speaker_name":"Nina Belina"},{"text":"So for example, if you have an SMS campaign, SMS campaign, it has to be very specific and like how much, how the frequency is going to work, opt out, opt in.","index":100,"end_time":717.12,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":706.16,"speaker_name":"Nina Belina"},{"text":"And it has to be within the privacy policy.","index":101,"end_time":719.16,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":717.12,"speaker_name":"Nina Belina"},{"text":"So what they were asking is to be like, to have like that specific privacy policy and not just the general one.","index":102,"end_time":725.56,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":719.72,"speaker_name":"Nina Belina"},{"text":"Okay.","index":103,"end_time":729.96,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":729.4,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"But now we have it.","index":104,"end_time":733.68,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":732.68,"speaker_name":"Nina Belina"},{"text":"So like the moment we put in, it should be done today.","index":105,"end_time":737,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":733.68,"speaker_name":"Nina Belina"},{"text":"So I will just let you know when it''s there and you just put the link in and that''s it.","index":106,"end_time":742.67,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":737.16,"speaker_name":"Nina Belina"},{"text":"Perfect.","index":107,"end_time":744.27,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":743.71,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Perfect.","index":108,"end_time":746.27,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":745.71,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"In terms of that group fitness campaign that we were launching, we were going to do the video and then also some photo creatives.","index":109,"end_time":753.79,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":746.83,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Did you guys work on the photo creatives yet or, or.","index":110,"end_time":756.59,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":753.87,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"No, not yet.","index":111,"end_time":757.71,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":756.59,"speaker_name":"Nina Belina"},{"text":"I mean, I was thinking because you said the video that was going to be like our main visual to focus on and then move to the visuals, but the other visuals.","index":112,"end_time":768.48,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":757.71,"speaker_name":"Nina Belina"},{"text":"Okay, so I, I''ll get the.","index":113,"end_time":771.84,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":769.12,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Let''s.","index":114,"end_time":773.2,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":772.64,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"I''ll get the video over, sent over to you.","index":115,"end_time":776.4,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":773.6,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"And then can we also do like one or two photo creatives for group fitness to compare and see which ones are.","index":116,"end_time":782.839,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":776.4,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Are most effective in that campaign?","index":117,"end_time":784.4,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":782.839,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":118,"end_time":785.92,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":785.36,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"So do you want one campaign to be the video and the other one to be like a static image or.","index":119,"end_time":792.16,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":786.8,"speaker_name":"Nina Belina"},{"text":"Are we able to do it so that it''s in the same campaign?","index":120,"end_time":796.04,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":793.72,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Because we can.","index":121,"end_time":796.92,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":796.2,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"So one campaign has to be like either only video or only png?","index":122,"end_time":801.4,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":797,"speaker_name":"Nina Belina"},{"text":"Oh.","index":123,"end_time":803.24,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":802.76,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"I was surprised as well, because then my paid media specialist told me.","index":124,"end_time":808.88,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":805,"speaker_name":"Nina Belina"},{"text":"And I was like, oh, I didn''t think that was the case.","index":125,"end_time":812,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":808.88,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"I thought we were able to do both before.","index":126,"end_time":813.8,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":812,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Ife.","index":127,"end_time":815.2,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":814.6,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"What do you think?","index":128,"end_time":815.56,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":815.2,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Do you want to do one campaign with the video and one with the photos for group fitness or just do a video campaign?","index":129,"end_time":823.67,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":815.56,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Wait, why, why do we have to do the png?","index":130,"end_time":826.79,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":824.63,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Is that decision or is that a technology thing?","index":131,"end_time":830.95,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":827.83,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"No, we don''t have to do it because you mentioned that you wanted to use both types of assets.","index":132,"end_time":839.59,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":832.63,"speaker_name":"Nina Belina"},{"text":"So like, it, it just needs to be like from a technical standpoint, one campaign that needs to be video and the other one needs to be a static png.","index":133,"end_time":847.75,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":839.59,"speaker_name":"Nina Belina"},{"text":"Yeah, I, I just thought it may be smart to do both, just to see the effectiveness of.","index":134,"end_time":854.4,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":850.24,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Of both.","index":135,"end_time":855.36,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":854.4,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Okay, all right, let''s.","index":136,"end_time":858.72,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":857.04,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"I mean, look, let''s try it.","index":137,"end_time":860.28,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":858.72,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"But you know, same thing.","index":138,"end_time":861.12,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":860.28,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Like we, we, we generally like a week, no more than a week to determine if it''s good.","index":139,"end_time":869.76,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":861.12,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Okay.","index":140,"end_time":874,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":873.36,"speaker_name":"Nina Belina"},{"text":"And also if for the GEO targeting I already spoke with, do you have.","index":141,"end_time":881.26,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":874.08,"speaker_name":"Nina Belina"},{"text":"Can we expect like a list of addresses for the gyms or how are you thinking of.","index":142,"end_time":888.54,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":882.46,"speaker_name":"Nina Belina"},{"text":"I''ll do that, I''ll do that and I''ll send that over.","index":143,"end_time":891.42,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":889.18,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Okay.","index":144,"end_time":893.02,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":892.46,"speaker_name":"Nina Belina"},{"text":"Milan, can you.","index":145,"end_time":897.1,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":896.059,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"So we''re all on the same page.","index":146,"end_time":900.98,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":899.66,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"We''re gonna, we should be sending some very targeted promos to members in that location.","index":147,"end_time":908.56,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":900.98,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Okay, when you say very targeted, how far?","index":148,"end_time":911.92,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":909.2,"speaker_name":"Nina Belina"},{"text":"Well, I, I think it''s like we''re going to have specific addresses so they''re all going to work out in that building in terms of like the promos we can like.","index":149,"end_time":926.08,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":913.28,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"I''m thinking it''s something like we.","index":150,"end_time":931.76,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":926.16,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Some incentive to switch is likely we''re going to catch people who already have a subscription.","index":151,"end_time":937.25,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":931.76,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Right.","index":152,"end_time":938.37,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":937.97,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"It''s something that like that would frustrate and them at their gym.","index":153,"end_time":943.09,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":938.53,"speaker_name":"Nina Belina"},{"text":"And you say like you''re not going to experience that at Powerhouse.","index":154,"end_time":948.05,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":943.09,"speaker_name":"Nina Belina"},{"text":"So like don''t wait for, for your leg press or something like that.","index":155,"end_time":955.01,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":950.05,"speaker_name":"Nina Belina"},{"text":"Yeah, or something like.","index":156,"end_time":957.33,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":955.97,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Are you sick of, Are you.","index":157,"end_time":959.28,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":957.33,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Is this a good idea?","index":158,"end_time":961.07,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":960.39,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Like are you sick of working out in a, in a dirty place, Kona Powerhouse or something like that?","index":159,"end_time":965.95,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":961.07,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Or are you.","index":160,"end_time":966.47,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":965.95,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"I mean you wouldn''t call it dirty.","index":161,"end_time":968.11,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":966.47,"speaker_name":"Nina Belina"},{"text":"So we''re not calling other gems dirty, but maybe we like maybe saying like are you sick of people being on their phone on a, like on some kind of a device?","index":162,"end_time":980.47,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":968.11,"speaker_name":"Nina Belina"},{"text":"I don''t know.","index":163,"end_time":981.11,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":980.47,"speaker_name":"Nina Belina"},{"text":"Or ife.","index":164,"end_time":983.55,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":982.63,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Are you just thinking monetary.","index":165,"end_time":984.95,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":983.55,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Ideas like based off of like our month to month memberships compared to like the terms and things like that?","index":166,"end_time":994.82,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":989.7,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Yeah, I think what we need to do is understand the term contracts, how they cancel and those gems.","index":167,"end_time":1004.82,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":995.86,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"So if you have a gym, if you give you know, three gems, we need to understand that are they all month to month, do they also have term?","index":168,"end_time":1012.07,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1005.94,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"And then if we understand that penalties, we might be able to say something even like if we will buy out 50% of your contract, take advantage in the next like two weeks.","index":169,"end_time":1028.31,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1013.27,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Here''s a deadline.","index":170,"end_time":1029.27,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1028.31,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Oh, that''s an extreme thing, but that''s.","index":171,"end_time":1032.03,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1029.99,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"I think there is a financial component.","index":172,"end_time":1033.99,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1032.03,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Not to say we have to pay them, but maybe we offer them like three months free on us.","index":173,"end_time":1039.52,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1034.79,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Right?","index":174,"end_time":1041.72,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1041.36,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"One month free.","index":175,"end_time":1042.64,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1041.72,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":176,"end_time":1043.84,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1043.36,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"This is like what AT&T and T Mobile do, right.","index":177,"end_time":1048.24,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1044.8,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"We would give that, we''ll do it free and I don''t know.","index":178,"end_time":1055.08,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1048.32,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"So I want to understand like what is currently their policy on that.","index":179,"end_time":1060.88,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1055.08,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"I don''t think we would need to necessarily like talk bad about the other gym, but we know what we can compete on objectively is price for some of them.","index":180,"end_time":1073.31,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1063.52,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"So for the ones that are like in the high end gyms that are like 100 bucks more.","index":181,"end_time":1080.47,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1074.27,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"We comp, we have to compete on price and we, we compute them because we know how much they cost.","index":182,"end_time":1086.75,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1080.47,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"But we can give them a special promo for only the people in that area.","index":183,"end_time":1092.83,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1087.23,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"If they take advantage of our offer, we''re gonna give them the first three months at 50 discount.","index":184,"end_time":1100.15,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1093.63,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"I''m making this up.","index":185,"end_time":1100.99,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1100.15,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Yeah, yeah, yeah.","index":186,"end_time":1102.59,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1101.79,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"It''s not even.","index":187,"end_time":1103.15,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1102.59,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Because that''s how much we''re willing to pay to steal a customer away from a competitor.","index":188,"end_time":1107.79,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1103.31,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"We''re actually.","index":189,"end_time":1109.47,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1108.83,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Any revenue, some revenue.","index":190,"end_time":1111.83,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1110.43,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"That''s what we''re willing to do.","index":191,"end_time":1112.83,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1111.83,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Willing to, to do that.","index":192,"end_time":1115.31,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1113.87,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"And then you, you know, so we don''t know.","index":193,"end_time":1118.82,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1116.43,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"I don''t know what it is just yet.","index":194,"end_time":1120.5,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1118.9,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"I think we have to determine that that''s going to be based on the gyms that you, you, you want to give to Nina.","index":195,"end_time":1127.02,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1120.66,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Like that''s within, I don''t know, like a 10 minute driving distance for us.","index":196,"end_time":1134.74,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1127.02,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"And I would look for gyms that are, we have to do all gyms that are more expensive than us within walking distance, you know, and then any gym that is like a little bit less than us, we should do them as well.","index":197,"end_time":1149.23,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1134.74,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"And then once we have that list, like, I don''t know, maybe it''s like six or eight.","index":198,"end_time":1155.15,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1151.71,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"I don''t know how many gyms you want to do.","index":199,"end_time":1157.39,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1155.15,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"We can then determine how to bucket the ads so we can chunk them into groups.","index":200,"end_time":1163.95,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1157.63,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"I''m assuming that''s possible.","index":201,"end_time":1165.07,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1163.95,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Right.","index":202,"end_time":1165.47,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1165.07,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Like we can say these three are going to get this ad.","index":203,"end_time":1167.95,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1165.71,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"These three.","index":204,"end_time":1168.75,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1168.11,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"So then we chunk them and we, but we need, I think we need, we need some at least like six or eight to know how if this is working or not.","index":205,"end_time":1182.83,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1170.35,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Six or eight gyms?","index":206,"end_time":1185.23,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1184.19,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Yeah, yeah.","index":207,"end_time":1187.55,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1186.59,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Whether we do Miami or FTL Miami.","index":208,"end_time":1192.99,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1189.15,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"100% would be the better.","index":209,"end_time":1194.43,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1192.99,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"So let''s, let''s, let''s try Miami because there are more gyms nearby that are more expensive.","index":210,"end_time":1199.32,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1195,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Also try to really compile as much as you can because whenever you like geofence, like it does narrow the audience and then I mean it can be really good for a target that, but it''s also very, very narrow scope.","index":211,"end_time":1219.4,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1203.88,"speaker_name":"Nina Belina"},{"text":"So what do you, what do you think?","index":212,"end_time":1222.93,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1221.81,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"So the more locations, the better.","index":213,"end_time":1225.73,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1222.93,"speaker_name":"Nina Belina"},{"text":"More individual locations or more radius, Larger radius?","index":214,"end_time":1232.29,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1228.93,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Well, if you know that for example, within a certain radius there are a lot of gems that you find within that scope that you''re looking for, then yes.","index":215,"end_time":1242.93,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1234.53,"speaker_name":"Nina Belina"},{"text":"But if you want to start it like specific, specific locations, we would need addresses, for example from Equinox or the higher end gyms.","index":216,"end_time":1251.89,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1242.93,"speaker_name":"Nina Belina"},{"text":"Is that something You''ve seen before where we can target buildings?","index":217,"end_time":1255.54,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1252.58,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Yeah, we did that for a client who does freight work.","index":218,"end_time":1260.5,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1256.42,"speaker_name":"Nina Belina"},{"text":"We targeted all of the Costco locations that they delivered addresses for the area around the location.","index":219,"end_time":1270.74,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1261.14,"speaker_name":"Nina Belina"},{"text":"And what was the outcome of that?","index":220,"end_time":1274.5,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1271.78,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"It was really great because they stayed top of mind for people.","index":221,"end_time":1277.62,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1274.82,"speaker_name":"Nina Belina"},{"text":"So even when the campaign was over, we still saw leads coming from those locations.","index":222,"end_time":1283.46,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1277.7,"speaker_name":"Nina Belina"},{"text":"We, we can see leads.","index":223,"end_time":1287.91,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1286.31,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"So for example, if we saw like, if we saw leads lead within the geographical part of where the Costco Costco warehouse was located, we like logically understood that that was because of data that people remembered from when it was active.","index":224,"end_time":1308.31,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1288.79,"speaker_name":"Nina Belina"},{"text":"See, I see.","index":225,"end_time":1309.67,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1308.55,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Okay.","index":226,"end_time":1316.83,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1316.35,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"I mean at some point we should probably.","index":227,"end_time":1318.75,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1316.99,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":228,"end_time":1320.35,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1319.87,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Because people hang out in the gym long enough.","index":229,"end_time":1323.15,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1321.31,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"They hang out those gyms long enough to be on, on their phone.","index":230,"end_time":1325.95,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1323.23,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"So I think, yeah, I''m excited.","index":231,"end_time":1330.75,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1327.39,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Let''s, let''s do it.","index":232,"end_time":1331.59,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1330.75,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Milan.","index":233,"end_time":1332.15,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1331.59,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"So yeah, you know, as soon as.","index":234,"end_time":1335.83,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1332.15,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"You can and then call those places.","index":235,"end_time":1337.8,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1335.83,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Yeah, just ask them about their, their thing.","index":236,"end_time":1341.16,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1338.36,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"And you can also see the price region on Google as well.","index":237,"end_time":1346.24,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1342.6,"speaker_name":"Nina Belina"},{"text":"So.","index":238,"end_time":1346.6,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1346.24,"speaker_name":"Nina Belina"},{"text":"Yeah, no, so what I''ll do is I''ll, I''ll get the addresses, I''ll get all their terms and conditions, prices, things like that, and then I''ll come up with like some kind of like value add for each gym or at least radius of gyms.","index":239,"end_time":1363.32,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1348.36,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"And then we''ll do an ad campaign based off of geotag.","index":240,"end_time":1369.02,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1365.1,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Correct.","index":241,"end_time":1369.82,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1369.42,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Okay.","index":242,"end_time":1370.3,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1369.82,"speaker_name":"Nina Belina"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":243,"end_time":1371.02,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1370.54,"speaker_name":"Nina Belina"},{"text":"This makes me wonder like going beyond this is why not target corporations?","index":244,"end_time":1377.02,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1371.42,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Like if we want to do corporate partnerships, should we just target like some, the financial district or like a building, one tall building skyrise and just hit them up with corporate membership ad.","index":245,"end_time":1390.06,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1377.9,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Are you, are you, do you work for a company of more than 12, 15 people?","index":246,"end_time":1395.22,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1391.14,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Give us a call.","index":247,"end_time":1398.26,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1397.38,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"We offer up to 50 discount.","index":248,"end_time":1401.14,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1399.06,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"It''s just a difference in messaging.","index":249,"end_time":1405.86,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1404.02,"speaker_name":"Nina Belina"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":250,"end_time":1406.82,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1406.34,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"I mean Milan, other buildings down there that are like.","index":251,"end_time":1413.14,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1410.58,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Yeah, we should just like individual buildings where.","index":252,"end_time":1417.07,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1413.46,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Because all we need is like three people and where you, where you work, you spend eight hours of your day, you''re going to be on Instagram, you''re going to spend eight hours of your day, nine hours in that, in that, on that floor, you''re going to be checking your phone.","index":253,"end_time":1431.55,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1417.31,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"So others like kind of those structures in Miami that you think it''s like, aha, like there''s a thousand people.","index":254,"end_time":1440.03,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1432.35,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"We could hit 100%.","index":255,"end_time":1442.04,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1440.03,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":256,"end_time":1442.6,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1442.28,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"There''s specific buildings that we could hit.","index":257,"end_time":1444.2,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1442.6,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Absolutely.","index":258,"end_time":1444.72,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1444.2,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Okay.","index":259,"end_time":1445.16,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1444.72,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Do you want me to get a list as well?","index":260,"end_time":1449.48,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1447.16,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Yeah, put that list together.","index":261,"end_time":1451.16,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1449.72,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Just, you know, and then because the thing Is like the corporate side has to be really easy.","index":262,"end_time":1457.08,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1451.64,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"We don''t need to shoot a brand new video for corporates.","index":263,"end_time":1461.4,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1457.16,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"We just need to change the words on the ad.","index":264,"end_time":1463.72,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1461.4,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Right?","index":265,"end_time":1466.76,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1466.44,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"We need to change the words on the ad and any lead that comes from that ad.","index":266,"end_time":1470.92,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1466.76,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Milan, you handle it, right?","index":267,"end_time":1474.52,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1471.32,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Yeah, we, I mean, yeah, we could direct those directly to me 100%.","index":268,"end_time":1481.88,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1475.72,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Something like, something great, like we''re in the 50 and just keep offering that, I think.","index":269,"end_time":1489.16,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1483.64,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"But we put together the plan and let''s make, let''s try it.","index":270,"end_time":1493.52,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1489.24,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Let''s do it all on February, get it going.","index":271,"end_time":1495.77,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1493.52,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Okay, I''m good, I''m good.","index":272,"end_time":1499.93,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1496.57,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Like the other stuff is mostly about.","index":273,"end_time":1501.45,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1499.93,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"I don''t.","index":274,"end_time":1502.69,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1502.17,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Well, you keep going because I was also just curious generally about the cost per lead and how.","index":275,"end_time":1507.85,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1502.69,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"And how we''re going on the budget right now.","index":276,"end_time":1510.01,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1507.93,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Well, I haven''t gotten the report yet since we moved the meeting to a day earlier, but I can go through last week''s information which is that we noticed that for example, for Fort Lauderdale, and this is before we changed the message to be more, a little bit more forward when it comes to what we''re offering.","index":277,"end_time":1533.02,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1511.93,"speaker_name":"Nina Belina"},{"text":"The.","index":278,"end_time":1533.98,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1533.58,"speaker_name":"Nina Belina"},{"text":"The audience was 45 plus, which was higher than any age group.","index":279,"end_time":1542.46,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1535.34,"speaker_name":"Nina Belina"},{"text":"So from 18 to 45.","index":280,"end_time":1544.22,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1542.46,"speaker_name":"Nina Belina"},{"text":"And then we saw seven leads over 45 and three leads before below that age group for the Fort Lauderdale ad campaign.","index":281,"end_time":1555.57,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1544.7,"speaker_name":"Nina Belina"},{"text":"And then for the tofu campaign we saw mostly 18 to 24 year olds and the cost per lead was much less, which was the best responsive group.","index":282,"end_time":1568.53,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1556.21,"speaker_name":"Nina Belina"},{"text":"So it was $7.","index":283,"end_time":1570.4,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1568.69,"speaker_name":"Nina Belina"},{"text":"37, which is really great.","index":284,"end_time":1573.09,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1570.54,"speaker_name":"Nina Belina"},{"text":"And it had a better pace with younger groups.","index":285,"end_time":1576.69,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1573.49,"speaker_name":"Nina Belina"},{"text":"But that''s also because it was with the $1 down campaign.","index":286,"end_time":1580.53,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1576.69,"speaker_name":"Nina Belina"},{"text":"So I would.","index":287,"end_time":1581.41,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1580.61,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"What was the cost for the other more expensive group?","index":288,"end_time":1585.98,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1582.94,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"The more expensive group was the $26, the one that you asked about in.","index":289,"end_time":1591.22,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1586.94,"speaker_name":"Nina Belina"},{"text":"The channel that was on Google.","index":290,"end_time":1593.74,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1591.22,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Was it.","index":291,"end_time":1594.06,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1593.74,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Was it.","index":292,"end_time":1594.3,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1594.06,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Wait, no, sorry, that was.","index":293,"end_time":1595.58,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1594.3,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"That was a trial campaign.","index":294,"end_time":1598.7,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1597.34,"speaker_name":"Nina Belina"},{"text":"Trial campaign.","index":295,"end_time":1600.3,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1599.42,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Okay.","index":296,"end_time":1600.78,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1600.3,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":297,"end_time":1601.14,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1600.78,"speaker_name":"Nina Belina"},{"text":"So I mean it was interesting that even without a specific sale point other than special offer, it''s still like resonated with people who are over 45.","index":298,"end_time":1612.56,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1601.14,"speaker_name":"Nina Belina"},{"text":"So that''s.","index":299,"end_time":1614.48,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1613.68,"speaker_name":"Nina Belina"},{"text":"I mean usually you have to have some kind of a very specific offer and this was just special offer.","index":300,"end_time":1620,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1614.48,"speaker_name":"Nina Belina"},{"text":"What.","index":301,"end_time":1621.28,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1620.88,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"What do we, what do we need to.","index":302,"end_time":1623.04,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1621.28,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"How do we work together so that if we see a $7, like in my mind, if something drops to like under $8 per lead, we have to go hard at those people.","index":303,"end_time":1634.16,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1623.84,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"I''m also thinking about how sometimes it''s just a random spike.","index":304,"end_time":1640.1,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1634.72,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"We don''t really Know, maybe it just happened and then it might go back to $12 a lead in three hours.","index":305,"end_time":1646.1,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1640.5,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"So, I mean, it''s not like, it''s not like a stock market.","index":306,"end_time":1652.26,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1646.66,"speaker_name":"Nina Belina"},{"text":"So, I mean, it''s not going to go up or down that much.","index":307,"end_time":1655.9,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1652.58,"speaker_name":"Nina Belina"},{"text":"But we usually ask our paid media specialists to do weekly management.","index":308,"end_time":1660.5,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1655.9,"speaker_name":"Nina Belina"},{"text":"So, for example, if they notice an opportunity to improve the ads, they are proactive and, you know, putting any kind of new filter or any kind of change that would make those dollars count.","index":309,"end_time":1674.51,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1660.58,"speaker_name":"Nina Belina"},{"text":"But we can see, like, I think one of the good things that we did last week was to choose.","index":310,"end_time":1680.91,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1675.23,"speaker_name":"Nina Belina"},{"text":"We switched the visuals to men because we saw that men were mostly responsive to the ad with the woman.","index":311,"end_time":1688.83,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1681.07,"speaker_name":"Nina Belina"},{"text":"And we also added some additional, like, for example, free trial and something very specific that people can say, oh, this looks interesting, rather than just a special offer.","index":312,"end_time":1700.2,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1689.31,"speaker_name":"Nina Belina"},{"text":"So I, I think it might take a while for the ads to.","index":313,"end_time":1710.519,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1704.36,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"If we don''t capitalize immediately, we might lose a week.","index":314,"end_time":1715.48,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1711.48,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Right.","index":315,"end_time":1716.28,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1715.96,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Like, like, what if there was $7 today, $7 tomorrow, and $7 the next day, third day?","index":316,"end_time":1722.69,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1716.28,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Should we be pumping more dollars like kind of in that same week?","index":317,"end_time":1728.13,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1723.01,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Or, or do we.","index":318,"end_time":1729.25,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1728.13,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Is there a reason we need to wait until the following week?","index":319,"end_time":1731.41,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1729.25,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"If you don''t have to wait until the following week, you can do it right away.","index":320,"end_time":1735.65,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1732.29,"speaker_name":"Nina Belina"},{"text":"You just need to tell us that we need to increase the budget because we wouldn''t spend more money than what we initially agreed on.","index":321,"end_time":1746.53,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1735.65,"speaker_name":"Nina Belina"},{"text":"So can you, can you tell us, can you.","index":322,"end_time":1755.5,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1752.94,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Can you put a reminder in Slack, like just tell in.","index":323,"end_time":1758.9,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1755.5,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"In the channel, whenever there is a ad that has been consistently over under $8, when it hits $8, can you just.","index":324,"end_time":1772.62,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1758.9,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Well, like pink tag Milan.","index":325,"end_time":1775.43,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1773.87,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"So he can watch that.","index":326,"end_time":1776.51,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1775.43,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":327,"end_time":1777.47,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1776.99,"speaker_name":"Nina Belina"},{"text":"And we can decide like, okay, let''s do it or let''s not do it.","index":328,"end_time":1780.99,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1777.63,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Okay.","index":329,"end_time":1782.11,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1781.47,"speaker_name":"Nina Belina"},{"text":"Because I think your team should be yours.","index":330,"end_time":1784.55,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1782.59,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Is your team watching that every day?","index":331,"end_time":1786.03,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1784.55,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Are they, Are they seeing the.","index":332,"end_time":1787.79,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1786.43,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Logging into meta every day?","index":333,"end_time":1788.99,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1787.79,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Seeing the numbers?","index":334,"end_time":1790.03,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1788.99,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Well, for most of our clients that have ads, we have a spade media specialist that does it every day.","index":335,"end_time":1796.87,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1790.67,"speaker_name":"Nina Belina"},{"text":"So I don''t know if she''s there every single day, but every week she''s very active.","index":336,"end_time":1801.51,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1796.87,"speaker_name":"Nina Belina"},{"text":"I''m logging in every day to check that too.","index":337,"end_time":1804.79,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1802.63,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"E. So as soon as I see something that''s under $8, I''ll also mention that we need to pump more money into it.","index":338,"end_time":1811.43,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1804.95,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"What''s, what''s our average.","index":339,"end_time":1813.03,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1811.83,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Our current daily spend?","index":340,"end_time":1814.95,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1813.03,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"I would have to look.","index":341,"end_time":1821.59,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1820.39,"speaker_name":"Nina Belina"},{"text":"I don''t know if you have maybe meta open.","index":342,"end_time":1823.59,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1821.75,"speaker_name":"Nina Belina"},{"text":"I haven''t.","index":343,"end_time":1825.11,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1824.47,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Yeah, let''s just do this month.","index":344,"end_time":1830.19,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1825.11,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Why is it not showing me?","index":345,"end_time":1844.59,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1842.75,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Well, let me share my screen.","index":346,"end_time":1846.99,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1845.63,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"So these are the two campaigns.","index":347,"end_time":1857.08,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1855.4,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Cost per leads.","index":348,"end_time":1859.72,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1858.52,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Where''s the.","index":349,"end_time":1860.44,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1859.72,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Oh, here we go.","index":350,"end_time":1861.64,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1860.6,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"So this is how much we spent in the last three days.","index":351,"end_time":1865.72,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1862.28,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Like 340.","index":352,"end_time":1879.49,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1878.69,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Comes to about like 220 per day.","index":353,"end_time":1887.25,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1883.01,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"We haven''t.","index":354,"end_time":1889.65,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1888.93,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Well, I guess we haven''t really done all of today either.","index":355,"end_time":1892.29,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1889.73,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Let me see what is.","index":356,"end_time":1894.89,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1893.65,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"So it''s 70.","index":357,"end_time":1895.57,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1894.89,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Wait, I thought it was one.","index":358,"end_time":1896.93,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1895.65,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"163 plus 180.","index":359,"end_time":1899.73,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1897.81,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Yeah, we spent 340, but then you divided by the number of days.","index":360,"end_time":1907.98,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1900.85,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"So the average spend.","index":361,"end_time":1909.34,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1908.14,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"114.","index":362,"end_time":1911.58,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1910.94,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Sorry.","index":363,"end_time":1912.5,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1912.06,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Yeah, 114.","index":364,"end_time":1913.66,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1912.5,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"So we can, we can say generally.","index":365,"end_time":1917.42,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1913.9,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Right.","index":366,"end_time":1918.66,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1918.299,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Generally the ad that goes.","index":367,"end_time":1920.7,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1918.66,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"That is.","index":368,"end_time":1922.38,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1921.82,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"That''s under 8.","index":369,"end_time":1923.974,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1922.62,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"$8.","index":370,"end_time":1924.7,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1924.106,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"We just need to.","index":371,"end_time":1925.82,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1924.86,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"We should just like double that.","index":372,"end_time":1929.1,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1927.74,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Double that.","index":373,"end_time":1931.54,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1931.06,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"That daily budget and then see, and then if it continues to perform well, then we''ll triple it.","index":374,"end_time":1937.06,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1931.54,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"We have to kind of make it act really quickly here.","index":375,"end_time":1942.02,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1937.86,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":376,"end_time":1942.5,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1942.02,"speaker_name":"Nina Belina"},{"text":"And also, if you count it, when you have a bigger budget, you have a better frequency of ads and then you will definitely get more leads.","index":377,"end_time":1951.98,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1944.34,"speaker_name":"Nina Belina"},{"text":"If people are seeing an ad often enough, for example, now, if they see it 1.8 time times, it''s, you know, not the same as seeing it twice a day.","index":378,"end_time":1961.67,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1951.98,"speaker_name":"Nina Belina"},{"text":"Correct.","index":379,"end_time":1962.83,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1962.31,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"What, what monthly budget did we set for you guys?","index":380,"end_time":1967.51,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1962.83,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"I think that we talked about 2,500 per.","index":381,"end_time":1974.15,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1968.63,"speaker_name":"Nina Belina"},{"text":"Oh, no, the, the last.","index":382,"end_time":1976.55,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1974.71,"speaker_name":"Nina Belina"},{"text":"The previous budgets were 220500 and I think that we upped it to 4000.","index":383,"end_time":1982.95,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1977.11,"speaker_name":"Nina Belina"},{"text":"For both clubs, like, to.","index":384,"end_time":1986.12,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1984.32,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"All together.","index":385,"end_time":1986.56,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1986.12,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"All together.","index":386,"end_time":1987.68,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1987.04,"speaker_name":"Nina Belina"},{"text":"Yeah, all together.","index":387,"end_time":1989.72,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1988.32,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Okay.","index":388,"end_time":1990.24,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1989.72,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Okay.","index":389,"end_time":1991.2,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1990.64,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"I think that''s.","index":390,"end_time":1992.6,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1991.84,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"That''s right.","index":391,"end_time":1993.2,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1992.6,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"But let''s watch that, like, real carefully.","index":392,"end_time":1997.68,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1994.48,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"It starts to trend down.","index":393,"end_time":1999.52,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1998.16,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"That''s, that''s all good.","index":394,"end_time":2001.64,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2000.64,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"And, and I think that''s.","index":395,"end_time":2002.6,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2001.64,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Right, there''s going to be some curve.","index":396,"end_time":2007.16,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2002.6,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Like, it will become easier to get ads if we have a big.","index":397,"end_time":2011.53,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2007.16,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"If we find the right ones and we hit them more often because.","index":398,"end_time":2014.72,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2012.16,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Because the frequency will start to make people want to be like, oh, I''ve seen this ad.","index":399,"end_time":2017.92,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2014.8,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Seen this ad like four times.","index":400,"end_time":2018.92,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2017.92,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"I want to buy it now.","index":401,"end_time":2020,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2018.92,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":402,"end_time":2020.88,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2020.32,"speaker_name":"Nina Belina"},{"text":"Okay.","index":403,"end_time":2023.2,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2022.64,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"I think that''s great.","index":404,"end_time":2024.72,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2023.92,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"I''m glad to see, like, we''re staying under 15.","index":405,"end_time":2027.68,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2024.72,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Did we.","index":406,"end_time":2029.44,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2028.96,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"What was the goal here?","index":407,"end_time":2030.48,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2029.44,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Milan?","index":408,"end_time":2031.36,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2030.88,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Do you remember, like, I think we said the month that we wanted you guys to come, we want to get under $12.","index":409,"end_time":2035.52,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2031.36,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Like, that was January.","index":410,"end_time":2038.33,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2037.45,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"We wanna, we wanna get under 12 bucks.","index":411,"end_time":2041.53,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2039.69,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Right.","index":412,"end_time":2041.85,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2041.53,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"So what''s our goal for, for February?","index":413,"end_time":2046.17,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2043.69,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Because, like, do we want to set it even lower or do we want to go by then we have to go by leads.","index":414,"end_time":2061.21,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2048.89,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Yeah, I''ll go by the number.","index":415,"end_time":2063.21,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2061.53,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"And the cost too.","index":416,"end_time":2066.33,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2065.49,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Right.","index":417,"end_time":2066.69,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2066.33,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"But for example, we would keep it at like 12 this month, but then try and pump up the number of leads.","index":418,"end_time":2075.17,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2069.81,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Okay, yeah, well, this one, pump up the number of leads, but then if we get the number of leads without changing the budget, then the 12 would drop to like 10.","index":419,"end_time":2086.29,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2076.85,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Has to.","index":420,"end_time":2087.25,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2086.61,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Right.","index":421,"end_time":2089.9,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2089.66,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":422,"end_time":2092.22,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2091.74,"speaker_name":"Nina Belina"},{"text":"How?","index":423,"end_time":2093.98,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2093.58,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Okay, so this is like the bear.","index":424,"end_time":2098.06,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2095.74,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Like, if I didn''t know anything about ads, I would say, like, how can we get over 400 leads a month if I didn''t know anything?","index":425,"end_time":2111.1,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2098.06,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"That''s the bare minimum.","index":426,"end_time":2113.5,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2112.06,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"I think we should aim for much higher than that.","index":427,"end_time":2117.85,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2113.5,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Like 500.","index":428,"end_time":2118.61,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2117.85,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Over 500 leads a month from Social.","index":429,"end_time":2122.29,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2119.65,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"I think that you would have to first have a really good selling point on the visuals that, you know, separate.","index":430,"end_time":2130.45,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2123.57,"speaker_name":"Nina Belina"},{"text":"All the other teams.","index":431,"end_time":2132.05,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2130.93,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"What do we get in January?","index":432,"end_time":2133.49,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2132.21,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Number of leads across.","index":433,"end_time":2136.93,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2133.65,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Across both?","index":434,"end_time":2138.77,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2137.81,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Well, there was, we, we switched marketing teams and then there was some, some stoppages in between the two campaigns.","index":435,"end_time":2147.26,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2139.49,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"But hold on.","index":436,"end_time":2148.78,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2147.26,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"I know we had the, the issue with the delete forms.","index":437,"end_time":2162.46,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2154.22,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"We got 177.","index":438,"end_time":2176.23,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2175.11,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"177.","index":439,"end_time":2181.99,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2180.95,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"What the healthy number of leads you need, Milan, across both.","index":440,"end_time":2187.11,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2183.51,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Both clubs?","index":441,"end_time":2188.47,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2187.59,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Well, it depends.","index":442,"end_time":2195.43,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2193.75,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"If, because with, with the current goals, because they''re so much more aggressive, I would, I''d like more leads, but they obviously need to be qualified leads.","index":443,"end_time":2203.02,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2195.43,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"And since Hydrimetry has taken over, we''ve.","index":444,"end_time":2205.26,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2203.02,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Had.","index":445,"end_time":2205.54,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2205.26,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"I mean, slightly less leads, but, but way more qualified leads.","index":446,"end_time":2212.18,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2207.86,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"So.","index":447,"end_time":2214.42,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2214.02,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"And, and then also the, the, the ads are not just affecting the, the number of leads that we''re getting, but also just general.","index":448,"end_time":2223.67,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2215.78,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Like the public is just starting to know more about Powerhouse.","index":449,"end_time":2230.87,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2227.27,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"How many qualified leads do you think you need?","index":450,"end_time":2235.67,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2232.95,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"At minimum?","index":451,"end_time":2236.39,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2235.67,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"If we can close our, our leads at a higher rate because they''re more qualified, then I would say just that we could keep the same number of leads, which is like 250 or 300 leads per club, and close them an extra 5 or 10%.","index":452,"end_time":2255.99,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2239.189,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Right, that would help us say that again.","index":453,"end_time":2261.51,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2257.83,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"What''s the close closing rate on those at the moment?","index":454,"end_time":2264.95,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2261.83,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Like 5, sometimes under 5%.","index":455,"end_time":2268.23,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2265.59,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"And they sometimes take longer.","index":456,"end_time":2275.11,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2273.51,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"So they can, they can go.","index":457,"end_time":2277.91,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2276.47,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"It ranges between, I want to say like 4 and 10%.","index":458,"end_time":2282.13,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2278.07,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"If we can close them at 15 or 20%, then we''re winning.","index":459,"end_time":2286.05,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2282.45,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Okay, so 2.","index":460,"end_time":2287.632,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2286.61,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"2.","index":461,"end_time":2288.05,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2287.708,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"But let''s say you said what, 300 per club.","index":462,"end_time":2291.25,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2288.05,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"250, 300 per club.","index":463,"end_time":2293.09,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2291.41,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"So that''s, that''s like 600 across.","index":464,"end_time":2295.17,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2293.25,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"We''re doing 177.","index":465,"end_time":2297.57,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2296.05,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"We did 177 in January.","index":466,"end_time":2299.01,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2297.57,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Let''s, let''s give ourselves.","index":467,"end_time":2301.05,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2299.89,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Let''s say, hey, if we had the ads up and everything was working, we would been at 250.","index":468,"end_time":2304.53,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2301.05,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"That''s still like half the amount of leads we.","index":469,"end_time":2309.18,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2305.26,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"You''re saying we.","index":470,"end_time":2310.78,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2309.82,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"You would like to have.","index":471,"end_time":2312.02,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2311.02,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Even with a higher closing rate, you''re aiming for 600.","index":472,"end_time":2316.7,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2312.02,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"We''re nowhere close to that.","index":473,"end_time":2318.54,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2317.1,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Right.","index":474,"end_time":2320.26,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2319.9,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"But not, not, not all of our leads are coming.","index":475,"end_time":2323.1,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2320.26,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Wait, say that again.","index":476,"end_time":2324.58,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2323.58,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Sorry.","index":477,"end_time":2324.94,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2324.58,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Ife.","index":478,"end_time":2325.5,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2324.94,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"I''m just asking about social.","index":479,"end_time":2327.18,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2325.82,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Like, are you saying 600 total?","index":480,"end_time":2330.38,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2328.38,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Like everything.","index":481,"end_time":2331.02,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2330.38,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"So what, what percentage of that should be from Internet?","index":482,"end_time":2334.56,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2331.76,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"I''m saying no, I would like 600 page social leads for both clubs.","index":483,"end_time":2340.8,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2335.6,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"600 page.","index":484,"end_time":2342.8,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2342,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"So right now in January, we only have like 177.","index":485,"end_time":2345.28,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2342.8,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Correct.","index":486,"end_time":2348.48,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2347.92,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"We had, we had very little leads come in, but there was issues with the lead form.","index":487,"end_time":2355.12,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2350,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Then we, we let go of Flavio''s team.","index":488,"end_time":2359.13,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2355.84,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"So the last month was not the best month for, for leads.","index":489,"end_time":2363.49,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2359.13,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Okay, so if you, if we just did the math right, 600 leads divided by 30 days in a month is like 20.","index":490,"end_time":2373.49,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2367.33,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"20.","index":491,"end_time":2374.29,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2373.65,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"20 to 25, 21, 22.","index":492,"end_time":2377.81,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2374.45,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"That''s how many leads we should be getting a day.","index":493,"end_time":2380.29,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2378.29,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"We.","index":494,"end_time":2381.41,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2381.01,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Yeah, and Sorry, we got 334 leads last month.","index":495,"end_time":2386.36,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2381.73,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Not 177.","index":496,"end_time":2388.04,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2386.52,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"There was an additional line here with 157.","index":497,"end_time":2391.96,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2388.12,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"So we had a little better than what I initially said.","index":498,"end_time":2395.8,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2392.92,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"So we''re 50%.","index":499,"end_time":2396.76,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2395.8,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"We''re like 50.","index":500,"end_time":2398.92,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2397.96,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"A little better than 50 to what we need to be.","index":501,"end_time":2401.88,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2399.16,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"We need to double the number of leads.","index":502,"end_time":2403.88,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2401.96,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"20 leads a day.","index":503,"end_time":2405.08,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2403.96,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"So the charge for this group is how do we get 20 leads a day at least.","index":504,"end_time":2412.43,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2405.96,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"What do we need to do to get 20 leads a day?","index":505,"end_time":2414.51,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2412.51,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Do you want me to ask our media specialists to make a review and see what needs to be done to get to that number?","index":506,"end_time":2421.47,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2415.63,"speaker_name":"Nina Belina"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":507,"end_time":2422.91,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2422.51,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"What does it need?","index":508,"end_time":2423.47,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2422.91,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"What do we need to do?","index":509,"end_time":2424.51,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2423.47,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"What is the ad spend they recommend that we should be thinking about?","index":510,"end_time":2429.87,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2424.83,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"And some of it might not be changing the ad spend.","index":511,"end_time":2433.59,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2431.47,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"It''s just running better.","index":512,"end_time":2434.75,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2433.59,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"You know, it''s everything that''s not related to money.","index":513,"end_time":2437.52,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2435.64,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"So I want to see all of it money.","index":514,"end_time":2439,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2437.52,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Do we need to increase our budget a little bit?","index":515,"end_time":2441.4,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2439.4,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Are there some kind of ad that''s just better?","index":516,"end_time":2445.48,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2442.2,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"We can see what competitors are doing just, just to kind of see what.","index":517,"end_time":2453.32,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2447.8,"speaker_name":"Nina Belina"},{"text":"Because we.","index":518,"end_time":2454.68,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2453.8,"speaker_name":"Nina Belina"},{"text":"Within all ads, there''s always some bidding, you know, coming from competitors.","index":519,"end_time":2459.24,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2454.84,"speaker_name":"Nina Belina"},{"text":"So just to know like what other people are adding to their ads and what we could improve in our own.","index":520,"end_time":2466.9,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2459.24,"speaker_name":"Nina Belina"},{"text":"In the initial audit that you guys sent over, Nina, you had a section where you guys proposed, like, increasing the budget and changing the different, like, workflows for our process for our, like, leads.","index":521,"end_time":2484.02,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2470.42,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":522,"end_time":2484.82,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2484.42,"speaker_name":"Nina Belina"},{"text":"So that would go to, like, specific pages on our website, the join online now links, or just, you know, complete a form and things like that.","index":523,"end_time":2492.1,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2484.82,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":524,"end_time":2492.88,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2492.64,"speaker_name":"Nina Belina"},{"text":"Adding variety like that would help and then also increasing the budget.","index":525,"end_time":2496.56,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2492.88,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"And then we decided, like, that was the form issue that we went back to the ones that we had previously.","index":526,"end_time":2506,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2498.96,"speaker_name":"Nina Belina"},{"text":"I mean, not that there''s anything wrong with it.","index":527,"end_time":2508.159,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2506,"speaker_name":"Nina Belina"},{"text":"Just so we are aware, like, that that was the workflow that we ended up with.","index":528,"end_time":2515.76,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2508.159,"speaker_name":"Nina Belina"},{"text":"Yeah, Yeah.","index":529,"end_time":2523.25,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2516.32,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Because IFA currently, we''re averaging, like, five leads a day total.","index":530,"end_time":2529.13,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2523.25,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Wait, say that again.","index":531,"end_time":2532.25,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2531.29,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"We''re currently averaging five leads a day this month.","index":532,"end_time":2535.77,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2532.81,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Okay.","index":533,"end_time":2536.89,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2536.33,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Total.","index":534,"end_time":2537.69,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2537.29,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"So it''s like, between both clubs.","index":535,"end_time":2541.45,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2537.93,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Okay, so that sounds a little low.","index":536,"end_time":2546.02,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2542.41,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Yes.","index":537,"end_time":2547.14,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2546.66,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Two leads a day.","index":538,"end_time":2548.1,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2547.14,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"How.","index":539,"end_time":2548.74,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2548.34,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"How do we get two leads a day?","index":540,"end_time":2550.06,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2548.74,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"If our cost per lead is, like, $8, $7.","index":541,"end_time":2554.18,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2550.06,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"We''re spending 400 bucks.","index":542,"end_time":2556.9,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2554.98,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"70 and 75.","index":543,"end_time":2558.66,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2557.22,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"I mean, that''s what I''m seeing here.","index":544,"end_time":2562.26,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2558.9,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Right.","index":545,"end_time":2562.5,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2562.26,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"It''s 15 and 13 total leads collected from both campaigns.","index":546,"end_time":2566.42,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2562.5,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Nina, could you share a screen?","index":547,"end_time":2569.3,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2566.42,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Yeah, yeah, let me share right now.","index":548,"end_time":2571.1,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2569.66,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"So I have February, which is this month, and then these are the leads right here.","index":549,"end_time":2581.9,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2576.62,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Cost per lead is right here, which is, I mean, in our range.","index":550,"end_time":2588.14,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2584.06,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"And then this is our budget per day.","index":551,"end_time":2593.42,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2588.78,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":552,"end_time":2596.87,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2596.47,"speaker_name":"Nina Belina"},{"text":"And that''s.","index":553,"end_time":2604.35,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2603.67,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Yeah, that''s around 4,000 as well for the month.","index":554,"end_time":2607.83,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2604.35,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Can you ask your ad specialist how we can start increasing leads here?","index":555,"end_time":2618.79,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2615.43,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Yeah, So ask her.","index":556,"end_time":2626.4,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2619.35,"speaker_name":"Nina Belina"},{"text":"Changing this.","index":557,"end_time":2627.52,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2626.8,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Right, this.","index":558,"end_time":2630,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2627.76,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"So a total of 4,000.","index":559,"end_time":2631.28,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2630,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Around 4,000.","index":560,"end_time":2632.64,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2631.68,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"It was a perfect thing.","index":561,"end_time":2634.64,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2633.36,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":562,"end_time":2639.36,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2638.8,"speaker_name":"Nina Belina"},{"text":"So I will ask her first about the 600 that you mentioned across the two campaigns, and also to see what needs to be done to increase the 15 we have at the moment.","index":563,"end_time":2654.57,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2641.28,"speaker_name":"Nina Belina"},{"text":"That''s so five leads per day.","index":564,"end_time":2657.77,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2654.81,"speaker_name":"Nina Belina"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":565,"end_time":2659.13,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2658.65,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"And did we.","index":566,"end_time":2660.01,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2659.13,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Did we set our ads to only be active between 8am and 8pm like, when the reps were working?","index":567,"end_time":2668.73,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2661.53,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Is that something that we ended up doing so that.","index":568,"end_time":2671.29,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2669.21,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Oh, yeah, yeah.","index":569,"end_time":2672.33,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2671.29,"speaker_name":"Nina Belina"},{"text":"We went with the budget schedule.","index":570,"end_time":2674.33,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2672.57,"speaker_name":"Nina Belina"},{"text":"Okay.","index":571,"end_time":2676.52,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2676.04,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Do you think that''s affecting the number of leads that we''re getting?","index":572,"end_time":2680.12,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2677.56,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Because people are working during those times rather than on their phones, like, in the evening.","index":573,"end_time":2684.36,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2680.2,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"How we can remove it if you want.","index":574,"end_time":2687.16,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2684.84,"speaker_name":"Nina Belina"},{"text":"It can be, like, during the whole week, equally allocated?","index":575,"end_time":2692.84,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2687.32,"speaker_name":"Nina Belina"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":576,"end_time":2694.2,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2693.64,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Well, I guess I would like to ask your ad specialist to see what they suggest to see if it affects the leads.","index":577,"end_time":2703.33,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2695.08,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Okay.","index":578,"end_time":2705.97,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2705.33,"speaker_name":"Nina Belina"},{"text":"Is there anything else?","index":579,"end_time":2717.97,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2716.85,"speaker_name":"Nina Belina"},{"text":"There''s.","index":580,"end_time":2720.21,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2719.73,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"I have Some HubSpot stuff.","index":581,"end_time":2721.41,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2720.21,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"But Efair, are you done with the ads?","index":582,"end_time":2724.93,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2721.41,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Yeah, yeah, I''m good.","index":583,"end_time":2728.54,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2726.38,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Let''s come up with a plan.","index":584,"end_time":2730.3,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2729.26,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"We need to get to 20 a day however way it happens.","index":585,"end_time":2734.22,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2730.3,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"So let''s try it.","index":586,"end_time":2740.34,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2737.82,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"We''re gonna Milan, you''re send those, those addresses.","index":587,"end_time":2743.18,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2740.34,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"So that''s going to help maybe.","index":588,"end_time":2744.46,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2743.18,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":589,"end_time":2745.58,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2745.1,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Okay, I''ll let you, I''m gonna hop off.","index":590,"end_time":2748.58,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2746.38,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"I''ll let you all get to the HubSpot stuff.","index":591,"end_time":2750.78,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2748.58,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Okay.","index":592,"end_time":2751.75,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2751.35,"speaker_name":"Nina Belina"},{"text":"Okay.","index":593,"end_time":2752.23,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2751.75,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Okay.","index":594,"end_time":2755.99,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2755.35,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"So Nina, I''m going to draw an account here.","index":595,"end_time":2760.63,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2756.55,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"So that right there is an account that is on HubSpot.","index":596,"end_time":2769.11,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2763.59,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"And if you look at the workflow, so the activities, it''s a Fort Lauderdale lead.","index":597,"end_time":2781.75,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2770.31,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"But for some reason it was put into Felipe''s list, then taken out of Philippe''s list, then put back into Philippe''s list and then taken out again.","index":598,"end_time":2791.03,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2782.15,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"And this happened to multiple leads.","index":599,"end_time":2795.59,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2791.83,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"I believe that''s true.","index":600,"end_time":2798.07,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2795.59,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":601,"end_time":2799.51,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2799.03,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"And I asked Felipe if he manually did it and he said no, he hasn''t touched any Fort Lauderdale lead.","index":602,"end_time":2804.95,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2799.51,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"So I was just trying to figure out what happened there.","index":603,"end_time":2807.85,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2805.77,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"And did you go through the, like the version history to see if it''s visible in HubSpot?","index":604,"end_time":2813.85,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2808.81,"speaker_name":"Nina Belina"},{"text":"I looked at the activities and the.","index":605,"end_time":2818.73,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2816.65,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"No, I didn''t look at the history.","index":606,"end_time":2823.45,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2822.01,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Where would I do that?","index":607,"end_time":2824.81,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2823.77,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"It usually like when you click on the contact you see like view all properties or like it''s view history some one of those two things.","index":608,"end_time":2833.61,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2825.61,"speaker_name":"Nina Belina"},{"text":"Okay.","index":609,"end_time":2836.8,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2836.32,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Oh, view property history.","index":610,"end_time":2842.32,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2840.88,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":611,"end_time":2842.96,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2842.48,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Last contacted, last modified date, SMS timestamp.","index":612,"end_time":2851.84,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2847.52,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Should I just search what I.","index":613,"end_time":2854.28,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2852.24,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Should I search Felipe?","index":614,"end_time":2855.92,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2854.28,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"No.","index":615,"end_time":2856.56,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2856.16,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Well, it''s difficult now because I don''t see the.","index":616,"end_time":2860.56,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2858.08,"speaker_name":"Nina Belina"},{"text":"To do it by memory.","index":617,"end_time":2862.82,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2861.38,"speaker_name":"Nina Belina"},{"text":"How do you see it?","index":618,"end_time":2865.3,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2864.18,"speaker_name":"Nina Belina"},{"text":"Because I know that it''s pretty easy because whenever I ask our developer, he gets it right away.","index":619,"end_time":2871.38,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2865.94,"speaker_name":"Nina Belina"},{"text":"Just a second.","index":620,"end_time":2873.06,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2872.18,"speaker_name":"Nina Belina"},{"text":"You want me to share my screen?","index":621,"end_time":2875.62,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2874.26,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":622,"end_time":2876.58,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2876.1,"speaker_name":"Nina Belina"},{"text":"This is the property history.","index":623,"end_time":2881.14,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2879.22,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"So last modified date integration.","index":624,"end_time":2887.14,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2884.18,"speaker_name":"Nina Belina"},{"text":"Go to page one.","index":625,"end_time":2888.79,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2887.91,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"I mean it seems like it got through the workflow twice.","index":626,"end_time":2911.43,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2906.07,"speaker_name":"Nina Belina"},{"text":"Yeah, but an incorrect workflow.","index":627,"end_time":2914.95,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2912.79,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Yeah, because it shouldn''t have gone to Felipe.","index":628,"end_time":2918.93,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2916.05,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"And he has all of his info.","index":629,"end_time":2923.89,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2922.05,"speaker_name":"Nina Belina"},{"text":"Like when you go on click on the contact, he has like, like the contact email, everything.","index":630,"end_time":2930.77,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2923.89,"speaker_name":"Nina Belina"},{"text":"Everything.","index":631,"end_time":2932.05,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2931.65,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"That''s strange.","index":632,"end_time":2934.37,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2933.49,"speaker_name":"Nina Belina"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":633,"end_time":2935.25,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2934.77,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"The only reason why it would be put through the workflow twice is if it doesn''t have like a contact owner or an email or something that needs to be filled.","index":634,"end_time":2946.26,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2935.25,"speaker_name":"Nina Belina"},{"text":"Yeah, I, I, yeah, I don''t know.","index":635,"end_time":2950.34,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2947.46,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"That''s why I wanted, because I, I was super confused when I saw it.","index":636,"end_time":2955.54,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2950.82,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Yeah, yeah, yeah.","index":637,"end_time":2956.74,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2955.86,"speaker_name":"Nina Belina"},{"text":"I will ask our developer to see what''s up because, like, especially if it happened, like with a couple of contacts.","index":638,"end_time":2963.22,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2956.82,"speaker_name":"Nina Belina"},{"text":"Yeah, okay, perfect.","index":639,"end_time":2965.62,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2963.94,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"So there was that SMS automation.","index":640,"end_time":2968.7,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2966.74,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"You''re going to let me know when that page is done and then I can confirm complete everything and the locations.","index":641,"end_time":2976.04,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2968.7,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"And also like the message for.","index":642,"end_time":2977.8,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2976.12,"speaker_name":"Nina Belina"},{"text":"For example, if one of the campaigns is gyms, then a message for gyms.","index":643,"end_time":2982.44,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2977.8,"speaker_name":"Nina Belina"},{"text":"And if the other one is corporate.","index":644,"end_time":2984.44,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2982.44,"speaker_name":"Nina Belina"},{"text":"Just a message for corporate.","index":645,"end_time":2985.96,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2984.44,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Yeah, correct.","index":646,"end_time":2988.56,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2986.76,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":647,"end_time":2988.88,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2988.56,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"So I got to do the corporate buildings too.","index":648,"end_time":2990.76,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2988.88,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Okay.","index":649,"end_time":2992.6,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2991.96,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Group fitness video.","index":650,"end_time":2997,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2995.8,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"I need to get you that video.","index":651,"end_time":2998.2,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2997,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Video.","index":652,"end_time":2998.59,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2998.35,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"So I''ll do that as well.","index":653,"end_time":3000.55,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2999.15,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"And then you''re going to just do a campaign specific for group fitness and then.","index":654,"end_time":3006.35,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":3000.55,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Yeah, we just need more leads and.","index":655,"end_time":3008.95,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":3006.59,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Does group fitness have any, like, specific message?","index":656,"end_time":3012.03,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":3008.95,"speaker_name":"Nina Belina"},{"text":"I don''t know.","index":657,"end_time":3017.79,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":3016.99,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"I would say yes.","index":658,"end_time":3020.51,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":3019.47,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"It like new classes, new group fitness.","index":659,"end_time":3023.43,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":3020.67,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Formats, I think that I saw on your Instagram, like the yoga one.","index":660,"end_time":3028.05,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":3023.43,"speaker_name":"Nina Belina"},{"text":"So I can maybe just take that message and.","index":661,"end_time":3030.85,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":3028.05,"speaker_name":"Nina Belina"},{"text":"Yeah, okay, cool.","index":662,"end_time":3032.45,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":3030.85,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Yeah, let''s do that.","index":663,"end_time":3034.17,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":3032.45,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"It''s all new.","index":664,"end_time":3036.17,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":3035.21,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"So like we''re just, we''re, we''re promoting like a brand new, like, program that''s kind of how we want to, we want to post it.","index":665,"end_time":3043.33,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":3036.17,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Like, classes are now available at Powerhouse, you know, crap like that.","index":666,"end_time":3047.53,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":3043.33,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"And we''ll go from there and then I will get you those addresses.","index":667,"end_time":3052.65,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":3049.05,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Perfect.","index":668,"end_time":3053.21,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":3052.65,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"And yeah, that''s it.","index":669,"end_time":3055.73,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":3053.81,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Great.","index":670,"end_time":3057.17,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":3056.77,"speaker_name":"Nina Belina"},{"text":"Cool.","index":671,"end_time":3058.45,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":3057.97,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"All right, sweet.","index":672,"end_time":3059.89,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":3058.77,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Thank you.","index":673,"end_time":3060.93,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":3060.29,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Thank you.","index":674,"end_time":3061.57,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":3060.93,"speaker_name":"Nina Belina"},{"text":"Bye.","index":675,"end_time":3062.13,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":3061.65,"speaker_name":"Nina Belina"},{"text":"Bye.","index":676,"end_time":3063.01,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":3062.53,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"}],"dateString":"2026-02-03T16:00:00.000Z","host_email":"nina.belina@marketersindemand.com","meeting_link":"https://us02web.zoom.us/j/85981404687?pwd=bdGJJvxEEtXnHHUUrFY8E5xxPuTASI.1","participants":["yefei@yhatinvest.com,alex.white@yhatinvest.com,tatiana@powerhousegymsoflo.com,wyattc@yhatinvest.com,robert.rudder@powerhousesoflo.com,colin.costigan@marketersindemand.com,tatiana.fernandez@powerhousesoflo.com,milan.wagner@powerhousesoflo.com,nina.belina@marketersindemand.com,cr