    3474,
    'https://us02web.zoom.us/j/85828735088?pwd=b9W3cDKwBeJQyK00Qs0iP3vvCmTxIZ.1',
    '{"id":"01KG5NMVVRJ8WT9RBS331ARMPH","title":"Ricoh // New North: Weekly Meeting","summary":{"notes":"## **Video Content Production**\n\nThe team is progressing on video projects for **IPM** and **RPD**, with scripts and live video assets still pending but storyboard work starting immediately.\n\n- **Roz confirmed readiness to start storyboarding the IPM video** using available **screenshots and existing scripts**, despite missing live video, aiming to replicate the style from the **Optimizer video** as a proven template (01:08)  \n    - Roz will send video briefs for both IPM and RPD as soon as scripts and assets are finalized  \n    - Awaiting feedback and script completion from a key stakeholder who is currently on vacation, causing delays  \n    - Roz committed to nudging the reviewer to expedite the RPD script for designer handoff within the week  \n    - Sales guide updates for RPD have not yet shifted to the new template but will start soon, with Roz sending the current version promptly  \n\n- The video content is expected to follow a **solution overview format** similar to previous successful assets, ensuring consistency and faster production turnaround (02:00)  \n    - The RPD brochure content is largely approved with minor content refreshes planned alongside design updates  \n    - Roz emphasized balancing quality with realistic timelines given ongoing review delays  \n\n## **Automation Suite Video Initiative**\n\nA significant new video project focused on the **Automation Suite and Smart Start Function** for the **VC80000 press** is upcoming, requiring creative approaches to visualize complex, mostly invisible automation processes.\n\n- Roz flagged this as a **larger-scale project** needing detailed planning and assets including **CAD files, workflow diagrams, and raw video footage** of the press, with a target to finalize style and briefing before the fiscal year-end in **March** (06:04)  \n    - The goal is to produce a marketing asset that clearly shows AI-driven automation functions like **automatic registration, uniformity, density calibration, and faster startup times**  \n    - Roz and Nathalie agreed to collaborate with video experts early to explore visualization techniques that avoid overly cartoonish CGI, aiming for a **more polished, engaging style** than the prior “factory automation” video (14:00)  \n    - Roz requested sample styles and creative concepts to align expectations and guide the storyboard before committing resources (16:00)  \n    - The budget constraint prohibits Hollywood-level CGI; Roz estimated true CGI costs could reach **tens of thousands of dollars**, so practical and cost-effective solutions are needed (27:00)  \n\n- Emphasis on showing “invisible” backend processes like data flow, AI analytics, and job batching, possibly through **superimposed graphics on live video** or innovative workflow visuals (34:40)  \n    - The audience is expected to have basic press operation knowledge, so explanations will focus on what makes the automation functions smart and valuable, not on basic press mechanics (37:40)  \n    - Roz stressed the importance of demonstrating automation’s impact on quality, speed, and cost reduction to justify the product’s value proposition (38:00)  \n    - The project timeline aims to secure approval and production commencement within the current fiscal year (ends March), with the new fiscal year starting April (16:50)  \n\n## **Creative Direction and Resource Management**\n\nThe team recognizes the challenge of balancing creativity and budget while meeting marketing goals for technical video projects.\n\n- Roz emphasized the need to **set clear expectations** with stakeholders about feasible production styles and costs, especially regarding CGI and AI animation (25:50)  \n    - Prior use of AI-assisted graphics in the IPM video shows openness to experimenting with AI-driven visuals if aligned with budget and style goals (26:40)  \n    - Roz shared insights on manual visual effects work costs and complexity to caution unrealistic expectations for fully CGI videos (27:40)  \n    - The team plans to leverage existing resources such as raw video footage and CAD files to reduce costs and improve authenticity (19:00)  \n    - Roz and Nathalie agreed on an iterative approach starting with sample visuals and styles, avoiding full-scale production until a preferred look and feel are agreed upon (20:50)  \n\n- The team discussed potential competitor and high-profile brand inspirations like **Apple and Adobe** for polish, while acknowledging budget limitations and printing press product complexity (21:30)  \n    - Roz highlighted the importance of a marketing asset that is engaging and externally polished, beyond internal-use videos, to better support sales and brand positioning (18:00)  \n    - Nathalie will coordinate with video experts to source or create style samples, focusing on workflow visualization and animation techniques applicable to automation (40:00)  \n\n## **Project Scheduling and Team Availability**\n\nUpcoming scheduling constraints and team availability were clarified to ensure smooth coordination.\n\n- Roz will be traveling for business in **Denver next week**, limiting availability and making the next meeting tentative or cancellable, with email communication prioritized for urgent matters (52:50)  \n- Roz plans a **two-and-a-half-week leave in April** for personal reasons, which requires advancing deliverables before departure (54:30)  \n- Nathalie will be off the following week but will continue delivering work via email, with a possible catch-up meeting scheduled earlier than usual afterwards (53:40)  \n- Roz encouraged flexibility and proactive communication to handle workload and deadlines given these absences (54:50)  \n\n## **Long-Term Vision and Market Impact**\n\nThe new video initiatives aim to strengthen market positioning by clearly communicating technological advantages in an accessible and engaging way.\n\n- Roz underscored the importance of showcasing the **end-to-end automation and AI capabilities** as critical differentiators against competitors, helping customers understand the value beyond hardware specs (38:00)  \n- The approach aims to educate both internal teams and external customers, improving sales effectiveness and customer engagement (18:00)  \n- The videos will highlight **cost efficiency, quality control, and faster production times** as measurable business benefits of the automation suite (34:00)  \n- This marketing direction aligns with the company’s broader strategy to evolve from hardware-centric to software-enhanced, intelligent press solutions (37:00)","outline":null,"keywords":["Video Production","Automation Suite","Smart Start","VC80000 Press","Workflow Visualization","CGI Budget Constraints"],"overview":"- **Video Production Progress:** Team is starting storyboarding for IPM video while awaiting scripts and assets due to vacation-related delays.  \n- **Automation Suite Initiative:** New project targets AI-driven automation features; deadline to finalize style and briefing is by March fiscal year-end.  \n- **Visual Strategy Challenges:** Team seeks cost-effective solutions for showing invisible processes; high-quality visuals are essential despite budget limits.  \n- **Resource Management Approach:** Existing footage and CAD files will reduce costs; AI-driven visuals to be explored if budget allows.  \n- **Team Availability Notice:** Roz traveling next week; two-and-a-half-week personal leave in April may impact deliverable timelines and coordination.  \n- **Market Positioning Goals:** New videos will highlight automation benefits like efficiency and quality control, shifting focus from hardware to intelligent solutions.","action_items":"\n**Rozalynne Regan**\nSend video briefs for IPM and RPD projects to the design team (02:50)\nFollow up with colleague on RPD overview video script status and sales guide content shift to new template (03:50)\nProvide current RPD sales guide version to the team promptly (04:56)\nCoordinate with Linnea Wolken to clarify project scope and requirements for the Automation Suite video (06:30)\nRequest raw video footage of VC80000 press and workflow diagrams from the relevant internal teams (19:00)\nCollaborate with video production team to gather and review style samples for automation workflow demonstration (20:37)\nCommunicate budget and feasibility constraints to stakeholders regarding CGI expectations (16:38)\nCoordinate schedules and manage meetings during upcoming Denver business trip and April travel (53:00)\n\n**Nathalie Mintjens**\nInitiate brainstorm with video experts to explore creative approaches for Automation Suite video visualization (15:40)\nSource or create stylistic samples re-imagining previous factory automation video with different looks and feels for client review (20:37)\nConfirm technical feasibility of client-proposed video concepts with video production team and relay feedback (36:00)\nManage meeting scheduling adjustments considering Roz’s and her own upcoming travel plans (53:44)\n"},"duration":57.900001525878906,"speakers":[{"id":0,"name":"Roz"},{"id":1,"name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"id":2,"name":"Nina Belina"}],"sentences":[{"text":"Yeah, because I just.","index":0,"end_time":2.16,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1.36,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Unless there''s something like burning a hole, I know I owe you guys, like the video stuff.","index":1,"end_time":7.32,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2.16,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"And I''ve been trying to just get the scripts reviewed before I send them to you, and that''s kind of taken a bit of time.","index":2,"end_time":14.96,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":7.32,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"One of the gentlemen I need to speak to is.","index":3,"end_time":17.2,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":15.04,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Is on vacation, and that''s for ipm, so he''s on vacation right now, which is fine.","index":4,"end_time":25.08,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":19.28,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"He did review the script.","index":5,"end_time":27.32,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":25.08,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"But what I asked him for before he left if he could manage with some live video of that particular.","index":6,"end_time":32.6,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":27.32,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"What do you call it, Product.","index":7,"end_time":37.56,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":35.4,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Like, something new.","index":8,"end_time":38.96,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":37.96,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Like the stuff I have is.","index":9,"end_time":40.28,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":38.96,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Is a few years old.","index":10,"end_time":41.44,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":40.28,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"And I wanted, of course, the latest and greatest.","index":11,"end_time":43.96,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":41.44,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"And unfortunately, he wasn''t able to get that to me in time.","index":12,"end_time":47.24,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":44.36,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"So I kind of.","index":13,"end_time":47.92,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":47.24,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"I''m trying to, you know, gather all the.","index":14,"end_time":50.36,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":47.92,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"The parts of the puzzle for you.","index":15,"end_time":52.84,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":50.92,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"So, I mean, I can send it through now if you guys want to at least get started.","index":16,"end_time":56.29,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":52.92,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Started with, like, some screenshots and stuff, and then I can follow up with the live video of that.","index":17,"end_time":61,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":56.44,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Or we can wait.","index":18,"end_time":62.4,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":61,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"It''s.","index":19,"end_time":62.72,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":62.4,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"It.","index":20,"end_time":62.92,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":62.72,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"I kind of want to talk to you guys about it and see how you wanted to proceed.","index":21,"end_time":66.76,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":62.92,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":22,"end_time":69.04,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":68.6,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"So it would be.","index":23,"end_time":69.72,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":69.04,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"You already have the script, but you''re just waiting for the actual live video.","index":24,"end_time":73.48,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":69.72,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":25,"end_time":74.36,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":73.88,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Okay.","index":26,"end_time":76.04,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":75.48,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"We can get started on it because we always start, like, the same process as last time of.","index":27,"end_time":81,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":76.44,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"With the storyboard and everything.","index":28,"end_time":83.32,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":81.24,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":29,"end_time":83.72,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":83.32,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Okay.","index":30,"end_time":84.12,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":83.72,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"And I do have, like.","index":31,"end_time":85.61,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":84.12,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"I do have some, like, decent screenshots and stuff we can use in Lou, you know what I mean?","index":32,"end_time":90.05,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":85.61,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"So we can at least get the storyboard going.","index":33,"end_time":91.97,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":90.05,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Okay, So I will do that.","index":34,"end_time":93.57,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":91.97,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"And then the.","index":35,"end_time":97.81,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":94.85,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"What do you call it, the one for Rico process director.","index":36,"end_time":104.21,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":99.73,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"I''m waiting on the gentleman to get back to me on that script, so I will poke him with a sharp stick and ask him with him.","index":37,"end_time":111.21,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":105.41,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"I''ve got a ton of new video, and we can use, like.","index":38,"end_time":114.69,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":111.21,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"I''ve got, like, hours and hours of video for our pd.","index":39,"end_time":117.41,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":114.69,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"So it''s funny.","index":40,"end_time":118.53,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":117.41,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"It''s.","index":41,"end_time":118.89,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":118.53,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"I have one problem with one and one problem with the others, so.","index":42,"end_time":122.13,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":118.89,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":43,"end_time":122.61,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":122.13,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":44,"end_time":123.81,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":123.25,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"So at least.","index":45,"end_time":124.37,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":123.81,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Okay, well, we''ll get started on ipm, then I will send through the brief on that.","index":46,"end_time":128.21,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":124.37,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"We''ll use the same, you know, look and feel that we did for Optimizer, if we could.","index":47,"end_time":134.85,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":129.41,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"It will be a solution overview.","index":48,"end_time":137.73,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":135.81,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"So it''s kind of like step and repeat of that Optimizer video, just IPM and then rpd.","index":49,"end_time":143.85,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":137.73,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"So I think that.","index":50,"end_time":147.21,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":145.05,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Yeah, I think that gets me there for those.","index":51,"end_time":150.01,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":147.29,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"And I''m Gonna poke him with a sharp stick right now and ask him if he''s had a chance, A chance to look at the RPD overview video script.","index":52,"end_time":168.01,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":151.21,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"I would like to get that into the designers this week.","index":53,"end_time":175.75,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":169.75,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Okay.","index":54,"end_time":179.67,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":179.03,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"All right.","index":55,"end_time":180.11,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":179.67,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"I have poked him with a sharp stick, so I think that''s it for now.","index":56,"end_time":185.59,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":180.11,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Unless.","index":57,"end_time":186.15,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":185.59,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Unless I had anything that you guys were waiting on for me other than those two videos, which I''ve been promising for weeks.","index":58,"end_time":193.59,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":186.71,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"I know.","index":59,"end_time":194.23,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":193.67,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"No, that is it.","index":60,"end_time":196.53,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":195.49,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"Only other thing is the battle card is sitting with you.","index":61,"end_time":200.37,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":197.01,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"Process director.","index":62,"end_time":205.25,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":204.45,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"Okay.","index":63,"end_time":207.21,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":206.61,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Yeah, that''s in with the.","index":64,"end_time":208.53,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":207.21,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"That''s in with the PM as well.","index":65,"end_time":210.29,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":208.69,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"I''m going to be seeing him next week on this call, so on this meeting, rather that I''m going into.","index":66,"end_time":216.53,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":211.41,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"For.","index":67,"end_time":217.09,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":216.69,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Into Denver for.","index":68,"end_time":218.45,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":217.33,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"So I will bug him about that as well.","index":69,"end_time":222.13,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":218.69,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"And yeah, we''ll.","index":70,"end_time":224.63,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":223.75,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"We''ll.","index":71,"end_time":226.39,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":225.99,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"We''ll get there eventually.","index":72,"end_time":227.59,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":226.39,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"It''s just sometimes these reviews can take, like, a hot minute.","index":73,"end_time":231.11,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":227.67,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"So he owes me a bunch of stuff for.","index":74,"end_time":233.03,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":231.11,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"For rpd.","index":75,"end_time":233.99,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":233.03,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Now, did we start shifting RPD sales guide over yet to the new template or.","index":76,"end_time":241.51,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":234.31,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"No, I don''t believe so.","index":77,"end_time":243.83,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":241.51,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"No, I don''t think so either.","index":78,"end_time":245.59,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":244.07,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"So let me make a note and I will say at least we can get started on that as well.","index":79,"end_time":250.95,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":247.11,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"So.","index":80,"end_time":251.64,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":251.4,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":81,"end_time":253,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":252.44,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Okay.","index":82,"end_time":257.48,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":256.76,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"So he said he''s not had a chance yet with the script, but he''s either looking at later today or tomorrow is looking quieter, knock on wood.","index":83,"end_time":266.6,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":259.32,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"So I should be able to.","index":84,"end_time":268.28,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":267.16,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Okay.","index":85,"end_time":268.76,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":268.28,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"All right.","index":86,"end_time":269.24,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":268.76,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Okay.","index":87,"end_time":270.76,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":270.2,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"So I owe you guys the video briefs, and then I will send over the RPD sales guide in its current form.","index":88,"end_time":282.31,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":271.24,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Okay.","index":89,"end_time":285.51,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":284.95,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"And we did do the RPD brochure.","index":90,"end_time":288.31,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":285.99,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"Yes.","index":91,"end_time":289.51,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":289.03,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"And that''s.","index":92,"end_time":290.39,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":289.75,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"I think all of it sits with.","index":93,"end_time":291.75,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":290.39,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"I think actually he was okay with the brochure, if memory serves.","index":94,"end_time":295.59,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":291.75,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Like, it''s very.","index":95,"end_time":296.55,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":295.59,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Like when we go through and we look at these once a year, sometimes it''s just.","index":96,"end_time":300.35,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":296.63,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"It''s super light.","index":97,"end_time":301.19,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":300.35,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"And in this instance, it''s light in the respect of content, but less so for the design because, of course, we''re switching over to this refresh design that you guys have done for us.","index":98,"end_time":309.75,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":301.27,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"So.","index":99,"end_time":310.43,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":310.19,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Yeah, so I think the content for most of the stuff we''re doing for him will actually be okay.","index":100,"end_time":316.99,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":311.31,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"I think the sales guide, we might have some content, but we''ll see how that goes.","index":101,"end_time":322.35,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":318.03,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"So.","index":102,"end_time":322.83,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":322.43,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Okay, so video briefs for RPD and IPM is what I owe you.","index":103,"end_time":330.99,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":324.59,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"We can get started on that sales guide.","index":104,"end_time":333.31,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":330.99,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Okay.","index":105,"end_time":334.35,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":333.79,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"All right.","index":106,"end_time":336.96,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":336.52,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"I think that gets me there.","index":107,"end_time":339.36,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":336.96,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"I owe you a bunch of stuff, so I will.","index":108,"end_time":342.76,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":339.36,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"What I can do sooner, rather than later is get the RPD sales guide into you.","index":109,"end_time":348.88,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":343.4,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"That''s pretty straightforward because I''ve got all those files and everything we need.","index":110,"end_time":352.36,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":348.88,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"And then I will follow up with the, the video briefs because that may take me just a little bit longer to get them into the, into the, you know, the, the, the platform that you guys have, so.","index":111,"end_time":363.77,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":353.32,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Okay.","index":112,"end_time":365.17,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":364.57,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":113,"end_time":365.61,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":365.17,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Okay, good.","index":114,"end_time":366.57,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":365.61,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"All righty.","index":115,"end_time":367.77,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":367.05,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Well, short and sweet today.","index":116,"end_time":369.53,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":367.77,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Well, I just wanted to give you guys a little bit of an update of what was going on and I will also let you know.","index":117,"end_time":377.849,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":370.25,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"And I need to talk to Linia, so this probably won''t happen until next week, but we were asked to do another video and it''s this one she and I need to chat about.","index":118,"end_time":391.15,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":377.849,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"But I just want to give you a heads up that it will more likely than not be coming.","index":119,"end_time":396.19,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":391.15,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Just a sec.","index":120,"end_time":398.15,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":397.55,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"I''m just trying to find that, that email.","index":121,"end_time":405.39,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":398.15,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Just a quick minute.","index":122,"end_time":406.75,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":405.39,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"So there, there''s a group that''s looking to do a, a video.","index":123,"end_time":415.56,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":407.31,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"It''s called like the Automation Suite and Smart Start Function.","index":124,"end_time":423.32,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":418.68,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"And they want to try and do how like our automation works with inside one of our specific presses called the VC80000.","index":125,"end_time":433.56,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":425,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"So it''s, you know, we''re just.","index":126,"end_time":441,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":435.96,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Right now we''re just sort of in the midst of trying to gather all the bits and pieces that we would need, like, you know, like full CAD files of like the VC80000 because that''s a full big machine and water, you know, like it''s got all these print engines and scanners and paper path and all this stuff.","index":127,"end_time":458.22,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":441,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Like we need to know what that looks like.","index":128,"end_time":460.02,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":458.22,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Of course we wanted some reference photos of the press itself, like stills, a bunch of other stuff, like a workflow diagram and all the rest of it to kind of try and show this automation.","index":129,"end_time":474.14,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":460.02,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Because automation is really of course hard to show.","index":130,"end_time":476.42,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":474.14,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"It''s like stuff flying around on, on, you know, in the air and that''s obviously kind of hard to show.","index":131,"end_time":481.6,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":476.42,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"So I think Lenny and I need to have a chat about this and we probably will next week to get this into you because it will be, it will be a bigger project for sure to show this kind of, you know, automation, you know, functional kind of detail.","index":132,"end_time":498.96,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":481.84,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"And we''re looking of course to get like a step by step breakdown also of like all the different, you know, features and what they do and what triggers them and all this other stu.","index":133,"end_time":510,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":500.72,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Then somehow we need to show like AI doing like analytics and things of that nature.","index":134,"end_time":518.14,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":510.22,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"So yeah, it''s, it''s going to be hefty for sure.","index":135,"end_time":523.18,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":518.22,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Sounds like yeah, it''s going to be a much bigger, you know, project for sure, but more to come on it.","index":136,"end_time":531.94,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":523.18,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"But yeah, I just wanted to kind of wave the flag and just let you know that this is coming and we''ll of course do our very best to give you as much information as we possibly can once the brief goes in.","index":137,"end_time":542.32,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":531.94,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Yeah, yeah.","index":138,"end_time":546.8,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":544.64,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"So maybe do, maybe do some thinking about some creative ways to show automation because that''s where we''re stuck a little bit, you know, like, like workflows of course we can show and all the rest of it, but they are trying to show this, this automation and what''s going on in the background, you know, in conjunction not only with the press itself but also with all the software that drives it and all of those kinds of things without making it look too cartoony.","index":139,"end_time":581.85,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":548,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"So it''s similar.","index":140,"end_time":584.25,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":583.53,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Did you guys do, I think you guys did you helped out with that video for the, the reprint video that we did last year for that Japan meeting.","index":141,"end_time":596.93,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":584.81,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Oh God, what was it called?","index":142,"end_time":598.77,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":597.17,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Oh, I know you guys helped out with it.","index":143,"end_time":603.01,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":600.77,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"That''s gonna bug me now.","index":144,"end_time":607.33,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":605.89,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"It was like, it was like a very thousand foot view of a, the smart, smart print sort of cycle and it was, it looked like a, a workflow.","index":145,"end_time":621.5,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":609.41,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Yeah, here, hold on, I''ve got it.","index":146,"end_time":627.5,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":625.9,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Oh, factory, Factory automation.","index":147,"end_time":629.42,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":627.5,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"Yeah, it was the, yeah, it was the factory automation one.","index":148,"end_time":632.46,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":629.5,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"So it''s, it''s similar kind of concept to that, you know, where we''re trying to show like all the, the bits and pieces flying around in the background and I just, I don''t know of a slick way to kind of show that.","index":149,"end_time":646.42,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":632.54,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"I know when we did it for the, the factory automation that it was, you know, it was very kind of cartoony looking with the little, you know, the little pieces.","index":150,"end_time":658.18,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":648.02,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"So just a second, I''ll share and it will, you''ll be like, oh yeah, I remember that.","index":151,"end_time":664.98,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":660.82,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"So this thing, if you can see it.","index":152,"end_time":669.54,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":667.06,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Yeah, that thing.","index":153,"end_time":673.79,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":672.43,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"So it''ll be similar to this kind of thing.","index":154,"end_time":679.55,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":675.87,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"So I don''t know if you want to get together with like the video guys and, and gals as the case may be and maybe start to brainstorm some ways and maybe some samples of what this could look.","index":155,"end_time":692.43,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":679.63,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Something like this could look like but less cartoon tune like, like we''ll give you actual feed of what you know of what this machine looks like.","index":156,"end_time":701.21,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":692.43,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"This VC80000 just happens to be the same machine.","index":157,"end_time":704.09,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":701.21,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"We''ll give you some stuff about what that looks like.","index":158,"end_time":706.73,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":704.17,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"But it''s the, the challenge is showing all this stuff that''s happening Flying around in the air and inside the machine itself.","index":159,"end_time":715.37,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":706.73,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Right?","index":160,"end_time":718.17,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":717.77,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Yeah, yeah, yeah.","index":161,"end_time":722.27,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":718.97,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"So it''s like I said, I wanted to give you sort of a heads up.","index":162,"end_time":725.11,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":722.59,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"You can start thinking about it at least.","index":163,"end_time":727.07,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":725.11,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":164,"end_time":728.35,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":727.87,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"The initial email that we got from the gentleman who''s looking this, he''s.","index":165,"end_time":736.27,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":728.83,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"It''s so funny.","index":166,"end_time":736.95,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":736.27,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"He''s like, I''m looking to have a CGI video created.","index":167,"end_time":739.83,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":736.95,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"And we''re like, oh Cha Ching.","index":168,"end_time":741.31,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":739.83,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Like, no, I don''t think that''s gonna happen, but okay.","index":169,"end_time":747.03,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":744.35,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"This is not Hollywood, you know.","index":170,"end_time":748.59,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":747.03,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"I know.","index":171,"end_time":751.75,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":751.39,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Bless, bless, bless him.","index":172,"end_time":753.31,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":751.75,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"I''m looking to have a CGI video created that will demonstrate and explain the AI, namely the automation suite items described and explained to use as a marketing asset.","index":173,"end_time":764.51,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":753.79,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"The items I''m thinking to explain are automatic registration, uniformity, density, calibration.","index":174,"end_time":770.23,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":764.75,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"These are all things that happen like in the machine.","index":175,"end_time":772.59,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":770.23,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Most, really, most of the Smart Start functions.","index":176,"end_time":776.77,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":773.63,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"So that''s, it''s kind of like this that I''m showing you on my screen right now.","index":177,"end_time":783.17,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":778.37,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Just, it''s getting into more depth in the functionality of the, of the, the Smart Start.","index":178,"end_time":788.29,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":783.17,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"So yeah, it''s a challenge because I don''t know how else to show this other than like how we did it for the factory automation workflow.","index":179,"end_time":798.13,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":788.77,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":180,"end_time":799.65,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":799.09,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Is there, for this video, is there going to be like a script as well?","index":181,"end_time":803.81,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":800.05,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"Or maybe even if, even if there''s.","index":182,"end_time":809.03,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":806.71,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"No like voiceover, but just a, like a layout of like scene by scene.","index":183,"end_time":813.03,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":809.03,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"What you''d like to see?","index":184,"end_time":813.99,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":813.03,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Yeah, there''s going to have to be for sure because you guys won''t know what, you know, uniformity and density and calibration mean.","index":185,"end_time":820.87,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":814.31,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"We''re gonna have to do that for you.","index":186,"end_time":822.83,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":820.87,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Yeah, but maybe we can just use this factory automation just as a, a starting point because we did this already and this is, we did it quickly and on the fly because this is all we had and we had a really short time frame for it as well.","index":187,"end_time":841.44,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":822.83,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"So if there''s another way to show something like this, like what you''re seeing on our screen, that''s what, you know, I''m kind of looking to do.","index":188,"end_time":851.04,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":843.04,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Because the initial brief when we first spoke, we thought, oh, we''ll show this workflow and intersperse it with actual live, you know, feed if you will, from the, like the actual thing.","index":189,"end_time":864.31,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":851.04,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Like we''re going to actually show batch builder, we''re actually going to show the machine, we''re actually going to show the Cobot, but we just couldn''t get around to it because we had none of that.","index":190,"end_time":872.43,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":864.31,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"We just didn''t have Time to get that.","index":191,"end_time":874.35,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":872.51,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"That video done, like, on site, like in all the rest of it.","index":192,"end_time":878.39,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":874.51,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Right.","index":193,"end_time":878.67,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":878.39,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"So, like I said, for now, use this as kind of like an example and just be like, hey, guys, is there a way we can do this that isn''t the cartoon?","index":194,"end_time":890.42,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":878.83,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"And I just don''t.","index":195,"end_time":893.94,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":892.66,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Other than, like, how we did it for this or showing, you know, the.","index":196,"end_time":899.42,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":894.34,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"The live thing working, like the.","index":197,"end_time":902.58,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":899.42,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"The actual press, you know, running.","index":198,"end_time":904.74,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":902.58,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"I don''t know another way to show all the stuff that''s happening, you know, like, in the back end.","index":199,"end_time":910.5,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":905.3,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Because I think on here there''s, like, the messy ones.","index":200,"end_time":914.5,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":910.58,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Like, this was the actual thing that we.","index":201,"end_time":916.46,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":914.5,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"I think we kind of ended up with.","index":202,"end_time":917.66,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":916.46,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"And it''s all these lines.","index":203,"end_time":919.14,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":917.66,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"This is all the stuff that''s happening in the background.","index":204,"end_time":921.75,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":919.55,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"That''s really hard to show.","index":205,"end_time":923.23,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":921.75,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Yeah, yeah, it''s a challenge.","index":206,"end_time":929.23,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":926.67,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"That''s why I thought I would bring it up now before you guys see the brief, so that it''s not like, oh, God, what are you doing, Roz?","index":207,"end_time":935.07,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":929.23,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Yeah, yeah, yeah.","index":208,"end_time":939.79,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":936.03,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Okay.","index":209,"end_time":940.35,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":939.79,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":210,"end_time":940.79,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":940.43,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"I mean, I''ll take this to.","index":211,"end_time":942.03,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":940.79,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"To the experts, see what they can come up with.","index":212,"end_time":945.23,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":942.19,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"Yeah, Maybe some samples ahead of time would be helpful so we can at least get this.","index":213,"end_time":950.36,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":946.24,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"The look and feel down and then move from there.","index":214,"end_time":953.44,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":950.36,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Because I feel like storyboarding this is going to be difficult without a kind of a.","index":215,"end_time":959.96,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":953.44,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"A sample of some kind first.","index":216,"end_time":961.92,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":959.96,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Yeah, yeah, we should nail the style down first.","index":217,"end_time":964.8,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":962.08,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"Yeah, I think so as well.","index":218,"end_time":966.6,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":964.96,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"That''s my concern with it, is that you could take this and go in a thousand different directions with it.","index":219,"end_time":972.24,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":966.6,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Right.","index":220,"end_time":972.56,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":972.24,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"So, yeah, maybe if we can nail down a style first.","index":221,"end_time":975.8,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":972.64,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"And then we''re like, okay, we like how, you know, this one looks as opposed to that one and see, like, what, you know, what we can do.","index":222,"end_time":985.56,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":975.8,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"But, yeah, I had to smile when he said CGI video, because I''m like, oh, I don''t know how that''s gonna work.","index":223,"end_time":991.2,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":985.56,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Like.","index":224,"end_time":991.76,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":991.36,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Yeah, yeah, yeah.","index":225,"end_time":997.2,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":995.36,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"I mean, maybe there is some experimentation we can do with AI Maybe.","index":226,"end_time":1002.98,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":998,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"Yeah, like, we''re open.","index":227,"end_time":1004.66,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1003.06,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"You know what I mean?","index":228,"end_time":1005.54,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1004.82,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Like, this is sort of our first sort of, like, shot at this, where we''ve got.","index":229,"end_time":1009.14,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1005.54,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Hopefully he didn''t put a time.","index":230,"end_time":1010.82,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1009.14,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"He didn''t put a time, like, around it other than he wanted to kind of get this sussed out before the end of our fiscal year, which is January, February.","index":231,"end_time":1022.82,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1011.86,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"So end of March is our fiscal year end.","index":232,"end_time":1025.86,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1022.82,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"And then our new fiscal for 2026 starts in April.","index":233,"end_time":1029.87,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1026.83,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"So he just wanted to get it, like, at least sussed out and in air quotes, paid for within Our, you know, within our fiscal 25 budget, that''s the only time constraint we have.","index":234,"end_time":1042.27,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1031.87,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"So, you know, we''re in February now, so we got two months to at least suss out like a style and a brief and, you know, hopefully get that into our, you know, into the rotation by then.","index":235,"end_time":1057.77,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1043.07,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Yeah, yeah, yeah.","index":236,"end_time":1061.81,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1058.73,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"So maybe to start, if you could maybe do a little bit of research for me on some different styles of how to show, you know, something like this in a more engaging and less cryptic manner, I''m going to say that would be fantastic.","index":237,"end_time":1081.35,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1061.81,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Okay.","index":238,"end_time":1083.19,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1082.55,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":239,"end_time":1084.03,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1083.59,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Because this is, I mean, it makes an eminent amount of sense to me.","index":240,"end_time":1089.19,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1084.03,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"I get it.","index":241,"end_time":1089.99,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1089.35,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Because I look at these all day long.","index":242,"end_time":1091.67,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1089.99,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"But we''re really looking to, you know, use this would be for not only our, you know, our staff, but for customer audience as well.","index":243,"end_time":1100.55,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1091.83,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"So I''d really like it to be more engaging than the, than, than the factory automation video that we did.","index":244,"end_time":1107.66,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1100.55,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Excuse me.","index":245,"end_time":1109.1,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1108.46,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Because that was just, that was strictly like internal.","index":246,"end_time":1112.58,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1109.1,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"And so I felt okay with it because it was internal, but it needs to be jazzier for an external audience for sure.","index":247,"end_time":1120.3,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1112.58,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"So.","index":248,"end_time":1121.3,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1120.94,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Yeah, yeah, like it needs to be a full blown marketing asset.","index":249,"end_time":1125.42,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1121.3,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"You know what I mean?","index":250,"end_time":1126.22,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1125.42,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":251,"end_time":1127.34,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1126.86,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"And he said for the actual printers, you''ll have, you have a video of that, right?","index":252,"end_time":1134.49,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1129.34,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"Well, I mean, I do have, funnily enough, some of the video that you''ve been using already, like for the optimizer overview that, all that, that video, that is actually the VC80000.","index":253,"end_time":1146.49,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1134.97,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Okay.","index":254,"end_time":1148.09,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1147.61,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"But we had to, but we had to crop out a bunch of stuff because I didn''t have the original video.","index":255,"end_time":1152.73,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1148.09,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"And that''s what we''re asking for from this team is like, hey guys, you know, we need the RAW video.","index":256,"end_time":1157.77,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1152.73,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"We can''t be, you know, trying to cut out things that some other agency or, you know, whoever''s edited it has put in.","index":257,"end_time":1165.18,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1157.77,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Like I, you know, we need the raw stuff.","index":258,"end_time":1167.94,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1165.18,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"So that''s basically what we''re, you know, what we''re asking for from them is all of that RAW video and anything else that they can show.","index":259,"end_time":1177.22,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1168.1,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"And like I said, we, we will have, you know, absolutely will need like a, a workflow, workflow diagram of all the things they want to show.","index":260,"end_time":1186.9,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1177.54,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Similar to this.","index":261,"end_time":1189.01,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1188.29,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Frankly, it''ll look probably similar to this.","index":262,"end_time":1191.65,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1189.25,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"So at least we''ll be like, okay, we need to show, you know, automated job sorting.","index":263,"end_time":1195.97,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1191.65,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"We need to show job input.","index":264,"end_time":1197.49,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1195.97,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"We need to show, you know, like we''ll have these sections at least that we can show.","index":265,"end_time":1200.77,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1197.49,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":266,"end_time":1202.05,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1201.57,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"So that I think might drive like the, the flow of the Video at least.","index":267,"end_time":1206.37,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1202.53,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Okay.","index":268,"end_time":1208.77,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1208.13,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Yeah, yeah.","index":269,"end_time":1210.69,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1209.17,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"So, yeah, so think about it a little bit.","index":270,"end_time":1214.95,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1210.93,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Maybe like you say, go talk to the video folks and see what they have to say.","index":271,"end_time":1218.55,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1214.95,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Maybe again, a couple of like samples that we can look at would be good or something similar.","index":272,"end_time":1225.03,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1218.55,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"And it could be a workflow of anything.","index":273,"end_time":1227.99,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1226.39,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"It doesn''t need to be pressed.","index":274,"end_time":1229.31,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1227.99,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"It could be, you know, anything that you find.","index":275,"end_time":1231.67,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1229.31,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"As far as the sample, we''re just looking for kind of like a look and feel.","index":276,"end_time":1234.71,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1231.67,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Okay.","index":277,"end_time":1236.23,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1235.59,"speaker_name":"Nina Belina"},{"text":"Yeah, yeah.","index":278,"end_time":1237.99,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1236.87,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"So I will, I''ll maybe come back with a few videos that we find if we have enough time.","index":279,"end_time":1242.72,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1237.99,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"Maybe I''ll just have them create a few.","index":280,"end_time":1245.24,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1242.72,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"Like maybe try and recreate this factory automation workflow in those different styles and see what that looks like.","index":281,"end_time":1251.36,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1245.24,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"Let''s go with samples first before you put all that work in.","index":282,"end_time":1255.72,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1252.88,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Because I would hate for them to put in all that work and then be like, yeah, that''s not.","index":283,"end_time":1261,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1255.72,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"That sucks.","index":284,"end_time":1261.84,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1261,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"You know what I mean?","index":285,"end_time":1262.48,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1261.84,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Like, yeah, I''d rather go with the samples first because that will really drive everything else and then we can start fine tuning it.","index":286,"end_time":1269.84,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1262.48,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"So let''s go with some samples.","index":287,"end_time":1271.98,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1270.22,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"And I don''t care what the product is or, you know, or I mean it, I mean, as much as I would love for it to look like an Apple, you know, video, I don''t think we''ll get that.","index":288,"end_time":1284.78,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1272.86,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"It''s not that easy, unfortunately.","index":289,"end_time":1286.38,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1284.78,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"They can make it look so sexy and I just, I just.","index":290,"end_time":1289.3,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1286.38,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Printing presses are just not.","index":291,"end_time":1291.18,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1289.3,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"You never know.","index":292,"end_time":1292.54,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1291.58,"speaker_name":"Nina Belina"},{"text":"Well, you know how they do it where it''s like, oh, you know, and the, the slowly turning iPhone and they''re talking about all the features and I''m just like, oh, I''m in love.","index":293,"end_time":1306.47,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1297.43,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Right.","index":294,"end_time":1306.87,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1306.47,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"But they also have like a, you know, a marketing department and a budget that I, that, you know, that I would aspire to.","index":295,"end_time":1317.07,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1310.55,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Right.","index":296,"end_time":1317.43,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1317.07,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"So if only we had an Apple budget.","index":297,"end_time":1319.67,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1317.51,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"Yeah, well, that''s just it.","index":298,"end_time":1321.71,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1319.67,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Right.","index":299,"end_time":1321.95,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1321.71,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"And we don''t.","index":300,"end_time":1322.71,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1321.95,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"So, you know, it''s the same with Adobe.","index":301,"end_time":1324.71,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1322.79,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Adobe''s been doing some really great stuff with their ads as well.","index":302,"end_time":1327.63,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1324.71,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"They do, I think they do really nice job also.","index":303,"end_time":1329.89,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1327.63,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"But yeah, like I said, it could literally be anything.","index":304,"end_time":1334.77,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1331.33,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"I don''t care so much about the product as I do about the look and feel of the thing, but I think it does need to lean into a.","index":305,"end_time":1341.81,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1335.01,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Showing a process of some kind, if you will.","index":306,"end_time":1345.41,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1342.13,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":307,"end_time":1347.97,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1347.41,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Because this is what it''s going to look like.","index":308,"end_time":1349.89,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1348.21,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"It''s going to have a workflow, it''s going to look something like this.","index":309,"end_time":1353.01,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1349.89,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"It''s just going to lean heavier into you know, like the press and the, the smart start.","index":310,"end_time":1361.87,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1353.01,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"So let me see if they have it up online anywhere.","index":311,"end_time":1365.39,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1362.43,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"I''m just going to look real quick.","index":312,"end_time":1367.23,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1365.79,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Rico Smart.","index":313,"end_time":1369.95,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1368.35,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Well, maybe.","index":314,"end_time":1383.48,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1382.76,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Rico.","index":315,"end_time":1384.88,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1384.2,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Smart Start refers to the events, automation, setup and operational features found in the latest generation of printers and production presses.","index":316,"end_time":1392.12,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1384.88,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Yes.","index":317,"end_time":1392.6,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1392.12,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"So if you want to do like a little bit of research, This kind of at least will give you like a bit of an overview here.","index":318,"end_time":1413.85,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1398.36,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"I''m just going.","index":319,"end_time":1414.77,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1413.85,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Can you see this, this automation?","index":320,"end_time":1416.77,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1414.77,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Yeah, yeah, yeah.","index":321,"end_time":1418.53,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1417.25,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Okay, so this is the VC80000 that we''ll be talking about.","index":322,"end_time":1424.21,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1418.53,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"This is from 2023.","index":323,"end_time":1426.29,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1424.69,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"So this is kind of old, but it kind of goes through a few things.","index":324,"end_time":1431.09,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1426.29,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"This, funnily enough, the AI overview kind of gets me there.","index":325,"end_time":1436.4,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1433.2,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"So it''s a smart operational panel, a smart device connector, you know, for mobile device collection or connection, rather integration with the workflows and whatnot.","index":326,"end_time":1448.959,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1437.84,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"That''s our software that they''re talking about.","index":327,"end_time":1450.88,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1448.959,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"And then other smart start capabilities like automated color registration.","index":328,"end_time":1456.24,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1450.88,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Registration adjustments refers to the registration of like the, like along the edges, like around for color and whatnot anyway, and then faster startup times.","index":329,"end_time":1470.46,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1456.96,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"So with presses, like turning a press on, it''s not like you''re, you know, it''s not like your, your office little printer where it just pops on, you know, you hit print and it prints.","index":330,"end_time":1483.82,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1470.54,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"These, these larger presses take like, they can take up to 15 minutes to like warm up and get ready.","index":331,"end_time":1490.66,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1484.3,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"And you test them.","index":332,"end_time":1491.74,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1490.66,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Sure.","index":333,"end_time":1492.28,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1492.12,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Everything''s working correctly and all the rest of it.","index":334,"end_time":1494.12,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1492.28,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"So when they say smarter or.","index":335,"end_time":1495.76,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1494.12,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Sorry, when they say faster startup times, that''s like a.","index":336,"end_time":1498.2,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1495.76,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"It, it just gets the printer up and running faster.","index":337,"end_time":1503.48,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1499.64,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"So they''re not waiting for, you know, 15 minutes, a half an hour or whatever for their press to get up to speed.","index":338,"end_time":1510.28,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1503.72,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"So yeah, let me see what this has to say.","index":339,"end_time":1514.36,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1511.32,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Smart integration.","index":340,"end_time":1516.84,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1515.56,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Do more.","index":341,"end_time":1518.37,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1517.81,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Oh, well, Workflows.","index":342,"end_time":1527.81,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1521.81,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Advanced workflows.","index":343,"end_time":1529.73,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1528.21,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":344,"end_time":1533.09,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1532.53,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Anyway, you get the idea.","index":345,"end_time":1536.05,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1534.13,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Yeah, yeah.","index":346,"end_time":1539.25,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1537.41,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"So like I said this, actually, this.","index":347,"end_time":1541.81,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1540.21,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Weirdly, this AI thing kind of pulls it together relatively well.","index":348,"end_time":1545.6,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1541.81,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"If you need.","index":349,"end_time":1548.8,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1548.16,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":350,"end_time":1549.12,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1548.8,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"If you want to just take like, just do a Google search, I''m sure it''ll bring up the exact same thing for you.","index":351,"end_time":1553.52,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1549.12,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":352,"end_time":1557.04,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1556.56,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Okay, so if you could maybe just come back to me with some samples, that would be good.","index":353,"end_time":1564.56,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1557.44,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"I''d be all over that.","index":354,"end_time":1566.64,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1565.12,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"And also too, I would like to be guided by you in what the team can and can''t do.","index":355,"end_time":1573.04,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1567.68,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Because, you know, you know, I''ve got a gentleman saying CGI and I''m like, don''t know how that, like, don''t know, like, how much money do you have, my friend?","index":356,"end_time":1588.4,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1573.04,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Yeah, yeah, yeah, yeah, I''ll let you know.","index":357,"end_time":1593.52,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1589.28,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"I also see like they might want to get creative and I think when we did the.","index":358,"end_time":1599.6,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1594.72,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"What''s the product that has like the people walking with the lines?","index":359,"end_time":1603.39,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1600.59,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"Oh, ipm.","index":360,"end_time":1605.07,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1603.95,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Yeah, ipm.","index":361,"end_time":1606.23,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1605.15,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"And then we ended up using AI to connect those lines and ended up working out well.","index":362,"end_time":1610.35,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1606.23,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"So you want to experiment with a few things and see how, how.","index":363,"end_time":1613.95,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1610.75,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"Yeah, yeah.","index":364,"end_time":1614.95,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1614.11,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"And, and as far as the samples go, if there''s some kind of experimentation that they may want to show, I''m open, you know, obviously like open to that.","index":365,"end_time":1623.67,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1614.95,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"But I don''t want them going, you know, full blown down, down the path of something and wasting a bunch of time only for us to, you know, not like it.","index":366,"end_time":1630.59,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1623.67,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Right.","index":367,"end_time":1630.91,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1630.59,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"So if we want to use like that, that IPM AI thing as an example of things that can be done, that would be great.","index":368,"end_time":1640.57,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1631.07,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"But I just also want to set expectations with this gentleman because he''s like, woohoo.","index":369,"end_time":1645.61,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1641.29,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Cgi.","index":370,"end_time":1646.17,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1645.61,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"And I''m like, I don''t know, you know, like it''s yeah, yeah, yeah, okay.","index":371,"end_time":1654.17,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1646.17,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Like all of a sudden I have visions of like green screens and all the rest of it and I''m like no, no, no, no, no, no, we don''t have that kind.","index":372,"end_time":1662.17,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1654.57,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"I don''t even know what that would cost.","index":373,"end_time":1668.15,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1666.79,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"I, it''s, I mean, I have an idea of how much it costs for like a major motion picture and it''s obviously in the millions of dollars.","index":374,"end_time":1677.39,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1669.27,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"This, we''re obviously, you know, and that''s, that''s over the course of like an, you know, two hours or something for like a, you know, Lord of the Rings situation.","index":375,"end_time":1685.19,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1677.39,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Right.","index":376,"end_time":1685.75,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1685.35,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"And this is like a minute and I''m thinking like a minute and a half, maybe two.","index":377,"end_time":1691.67,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1686.79,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"And it would be, I would say like tens of thousands if we were actually going to CGI it in my head, that''s what I have.","index":378,"end_time":1701.22,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1691.91,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"I don''t know if I''m right, but it does take a lot of time to get it done.","index":379,"end_time":1705.62,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1701.22,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"And I happen to have a friend of mine who does like a lot of post production work here in, in Vancouver and he does do a lot of like literally frame by frame, just faces.","index":380,"end_time":1717.86,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1705.78,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"He just does frame by frame on the, on the movie faces, like removing blemishes and crap like that.","index":381,"end_time":1725.4,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1718.66,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Like yeah, yeah, it''s funny, he was working on this one movie, he''s like, I''m so sick and tired of looking at Scarlett Johansson.","index":382,"end_time":1733.2,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1726.12,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"I''m like, oh my God.","index":383,"end_time":1734.24,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1733.2,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Okay.","index":384,"end_time":1734.92,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1734.24,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"That''s all he does like it''s all he does is CGI people''s faces.","index":385,"end_time":1740.68,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1737,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Like that''s, it''s not the background stuff, it''s not anything else.","index":386,"end_time":1744.4,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1740.76,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"It is only faces that he does.","index":387,"end_time":1746.36,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1744.4,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"And I''m like, and he does this full time and he''s a senior graphic designer.","index":388,"end_time":1752.52,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1746.36,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"So it can''t be cheap.","index":389,"end_time":1754.04,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1753,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Yeah, yeah.","index":390,"end_time":1755.8,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1754.92,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"You know, it cannot be cheap.","index":391,"end_time":1758.12,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1756.04,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"So yeah, I did okay.","index":392,"end_time":1764.76,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1759.96,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"But that said, maybe there is, I.","index":393,"end_time":1769.64,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1766.92,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Thought all of that was like automated.","index":394,"end_time":1771.08,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1769.64,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"I didn''t know there was someone sitting there doing that manual.","index":395,"end_time":1774.68,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1771.08,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"Some of it, some of it is for sure.","index":396,"end_time":1776.77,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1774.76,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Right.","index":397,"end_time":1777.05,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1776.77,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Like that''s what the whole green screen thing is all about.","index":398,"end_time":1779.29,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1777.05,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Right.","index":399,"end_time":1779.61,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1779.29,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Like that''s definitely like the automation coming into play.","index":400,"end_time":1782.81,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1779.61,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Map out a face and then after it''s done, like they can do whatever.","index":401,"end_time":1786.97,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1783.29,"speaker_name":"Nina Belina"},{"text":"Yeah, yeah, exactly.","index":402,"end_time":1788.49,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1787.05,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"But someone has to go through and look at it all frame by frame.","index":403,"end_time":1791.61,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1788.49,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"And can you imagine a major motion picture like Scarlett Johansson in as an example and having to look at her face frame by frame for two hours, like for a two hour movie or an hour and a half movie?","index":404,"end_time":1802.17,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1792.25,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Well, for her face, yes.","index":405,"end_time":1804.35,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1802.71,"speaker_name":"Nina Belina"},{"text":"But you know, William Defoe, maybe not.","index":406,"end_time":1806.95,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1804.35,"speaker_name":"Nina Belina"},{"text":"He is an odd looking gentleman, isn''t he?","index":407,"end_time":1812.23,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1810.15,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"I, I, he''s got a look for sure.","index":408,"end_time":1815.03,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1812.23,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Yeah, yeah.","index":409,"end_time":1816.39,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1815.11,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"For independent cinema.","index":410,"end_time":1818.31,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1816.79,"speaker_name":"Nina Belina"},{"text":"Yeah, yeah, yeah, yeah.","index":411,"end_time":1820.91,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1818.95,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"He''s definitely got a look.","index":412,"end_time":1822.31,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1820.91,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"He''s definitely got a look, yeah.","index":413,"end_time":1825.39,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1822.79,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"So anyways, I''m open to some creativity, open to some samples.","index":414,"end_time":1830.15,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1825.39,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Tell me what you can and can''t do.","index":415,"end_time":1831.99,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1830.31,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"That will help guide, you know, the expectations on our end.","index":416,"end_time":1836.31,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1831.99,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Open to using AI, of course, for, you know, fun things.","index":417,"end_time":1842.79,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1838.63,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"The brief is still to come, but like I said, I just wanted you guys thinking about it now because I feel like this is going to take us a hot minute to get right.","index":418,"end_time":1853.03,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1844.79,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"You know, it''s going to take a while.","index":419,"end_time":1854.55,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1853.03,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"So.","index":420,"end_time":1855.43,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1855.03,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Yeah, yeah, I don''t, yeah, I don''t know what kind of movie magic they can do and with their editing, but I will happily take some thoughts on it from them.","index":421,"end_time":1868.79,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1855.75,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Yeah, that''ll be a fun project.","index":422,"end_time":1871.59,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1870.15,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"I feel like they always, they always come up with something cool that I''ve never seen them do before, so.","index":423,"end_time":1876.79,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1871.59,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"Yeah, well, and I know the overview video that you guys just did was very, you know, kind of wa wa.","index":424,"end_time":1883.99,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1877.03,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Right.","index":425,"end_time":1884.63,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1884.23,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"So for this I would love to see some creativity and some like just some different ways to be able to show basically all these dotted lines and what''s going on, you know, like in the background and within the actual printer itself.","index":426,"end_time":1901.53,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1884.71,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Yeah, yeah, yeah.","index":427,"end_time":1905.73,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1903.21,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"I don''t think it''ll have like the Cobot Stuff, but it might.","index":428,"end_time":1908.81,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1905.73,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"But regardless, it''s kind of, from what I''m reading from his email, it''s kind of focusing on this, like, job input and, and the, the screen and then, or, sorry, the printer and then an output of some kind.","index":429,"end_time":1921.94,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1909.37,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"But there''s still a lot of bits and pieces even moving around in here that you just don''t see, right?","index":430,"end_time":1928.62,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1921.94,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"So.","index":431,"end_time":1929.18,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1928.78,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"So you''ve got a customer sitting off screen over here putting in an order is what''s happening.","index":432,"end_time":1936.06,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1930.14,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"So an MIS is basically just a happy acronym for people putting in an order.","index":433,"end_time":1941.74,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1936.14,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Like, like if you, when you go online to buy something, these guys are putting in an order.","index":434,"end_time":1946.62,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1941.82,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"And then, so there''s all these bits and pieces around.","index":435,"end_time":1949.14,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1946.62,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"You know, what the print job is, what the colors should be, what the font should be.","index":436,"end_time":1954.26,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1949.54,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Like, all of that''s coming in online for the most part.","index":437,"end_time":1958.82,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1954.26,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"It gets pulled together in what''s called a print job, which is what this little button is here in the middle.","index":438,"end_time":1966.26,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1959.14,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"And then what''s happening is it goes into.","index":439,"end_time":1969.96,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1966.98,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"This is Optimizer now, but it goes into Optimizer and connects with Ultimate Impulse Strip as well.","index":440,"end_time":1976.64,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1969.96,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"And basically what this does is this piece of software here is pulling in all these jobs.","index":441,"end_time":1982.24,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1976.64,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Like there could be 50 jobs.","index":442,"end_time":1984.36,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1982.24,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Let''s say we have 50 different people asking for business cards as an example, right?","index":443,"end_time":1989.72,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1984.6,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"So instead of running each business card job one at a time, which can be very, very costly, you run 50 of them at once, especially if they''re all from the same company, then you''ve got the same size, the same fonts, the same colors, and you''re doing it all in one shot.","index":444,"end_time":2007.58,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1989.88,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"So you''re saving a lot on waste.","index":445,"end_time":2011.02,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2008.06,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"That''s what imposition means, is that you''re imposing the, the print job onto like a paper piece of paper, virtually like in the computer.","index":446,"end_time":2022.3,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2012.54,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"So if you''ve got a whole bunch of business cards, you''re not going to put, you know, you''re not going to put a job in the middle for, you know, for like a greeting card, because that shape and size, everything is different.","index":447,"end_time":2035.07,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2023.31,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"And then what it does is it batches those different things.","index":448,"end_time":2039.03,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2036.67,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"So you might have greeting cards in one, business cards in another, and, I don''t know, tent cards in yet a third, and they will print together, thereby saving on paper and ink.","index":449,"end_time":2051.21,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2039.03,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"And then it goes into the digital front end of the press and then it goes through all this fun stuff in the press and there''s scanning happening and all the rest of it.","index":450,"end_time":2060.29,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2052.65,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"And then it finally gets output in the end.","index":451,"end_time":2062.09,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2060.29,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"So there''s a lot of Things magically happening, like within all of these pieces of software and within the press itself.","index":452,"end_time":2068.49,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2062.17,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"That''s just, that''s going to be the challenge is how to show all of those bits and pieces moving, you know, and, and, and working in the background.","index":453,"end_time":2080.07,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2068.73,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Yeah, I''m almost seeing like, if we do have a, an actual video of the printer.","index":454,"end_time":2088.71,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2082.15,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":455,"end_time":2089.55,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2089.19,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Kind of like having some superimposed graphics on top of it, if that makes sense.","index":456,"end_time":2094.71,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2089.55,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"Yeah, yeah, yeah.","index":457,"end_time":2097.83,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2095.35,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"I''ve seen, I''ve seen that kind.","index":458,"end_time":2099.03,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2097.83,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"I think I understand where you''re going with that.","index":459,"end_time":2101.47,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2099.43,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"And I have seen something similar happening on Trying to remember.","index":460,"end_time":2108.44,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2101.47,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"I''m sure I''ve seen something similar to that, though.","index":461,"end_time":2110.2,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2108.44,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"It rings a bell.","index":462,"end_time":2111.12,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2110.2,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":463,"end_time":2112.32,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2111.92,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"That''s why I''m saying I think some samples would be a really good idea and just say, okay, you know, we can do this, we can do that.","index":464,"end_time":2120.56,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2112.32,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Here''s what, you know, here''s like our top three samples.","index":465,"end_time":2123.92,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2120.72,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"This is something that we can do and it''ll really help, I think, set the expectation on our hand end and be like, okay, they can do this, but not that.","index":466,"end_time":2132.91,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2124.24,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Yeah, yeah, because I don''t want to, you know, I don''t want to say, oh, yeah, no, we''ll go full blown green screen cgi.","index":467,"end_time":2140.11,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2133.63,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"We''ll get Scarlett Johansson in there.","index":468,"end_time":2142.99,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2141.07,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"You know what I mean?","index":469,"end_time":2146.19,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2145.39,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Like, that''s not going to happen.","index":470,"end_time":2147.47,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2146.19,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"So, and if they, if they do.","index":471,"end_time":2150.27,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2147.63,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Have like examples of what they mean, you can also send that to us and I can just confirm with the team, like, is this something we could achieve if they have examples of what they''re thinking?","index":472,"end_time":2161.38,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2150.27,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"Well, the, the, the, what they were suggesting was.","index":473,"end_time":2169.38,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2163.22,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"How did he put it?","index":474,"end_time":2171.22,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2170.26,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"I''m going back to my email.","index":475,"end_time":2172.42,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2171.22,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Let''s see.","index":476,"end_time":2176.9,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2176.1,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"We have candidly discussed having a video that included AI ninjas that spring into action fix the problem when a deficit is found by the scanner.","index":477,"end_time":2187.14,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2177.14,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"So.","index":478,"end_time":2188.76,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2188.52,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"We''re like, wait, what?","index":479,"end_time":2194.92,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2193.48,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Yeah, is that for real or.","index":480,"end_time":2200.44,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2198.84,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Oh, yeah, that''s in the email.","index":481,"end_time":2202.36,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2200.76,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"So they''re trying to show like, I get why they''re saying that.","index":482,"end_time":2207.32,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2204.36,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"They''re trying to figure out a creative way to show all these pieces that are moving around in the background that, that you don''t see.","index":483,"end_time":2215.78,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2207.32,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Right.","index":484,"end_time":2217.14,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2216.74,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"So it''s, again, it''s all of these, you know, it''s, it''s, it''s, it''s all of this stuff working together in.","index":485,"end_time":2224.94,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2217.3,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"And it''s, you know, if you were to stand there and look at a press doing its thing, all you see is paper moving in and out.","index":486,"end_time":2231.9,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2224.94,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Like all of these doors are closed.","index":487,"end_time":2233.78,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2231.9,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"You know, you don''t See anything, right?","index":488,"end_time":2235.3,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2233.78,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"You just, you just, you know, you just see the paper going in and something coming out the other end.","index":489,"end_time":2240.91,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2235.3,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"So we''re trying to show all these groovy bits of things that are happening like this, the internal scanners and the QR codes and all this stuff working together to make a better, you know, a better press run, faster press run, less costly press run, you know, all of that kind of thing.","index":490,"end_time":2260.99,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2240.91,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"So, yeah, to also make it easy to understand to people who might not exactly.","index":491,"end_time":2268.07,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2262.35,"speaker_name":"Nina Belina"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":492,"end_time":2268.55,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2268.15,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Like, for the most part, the audience we''re we''re talking to has at the very least a basic knowledge of what a press is doing and how it works and all the rest of it.","index":493,"end_time":2278.15,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2268.55,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Right.","index":494,"end_time":2278.47,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2278.15,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Like if we''re going to be showing, if someone''s going to be buying a VC80000, they have been running a press shop for a while.","index":495,"end_time":2287.75,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2278.47,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"So there is a level of understanding, at least the basic, you know, we get a job, it gets looked at in some way, it goes into the press and then it comes out the other end.","index":496,"end_time":2298.89,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2288.07,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"You know, even if it''s just as basic as that, they, I would say they understand that.","index":497,"end_time":2303.17,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2298.89,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"So I don''t know that we need to go into like that level of detail, but we do want to be able to show like, hey, all these pieces are working together and this is, you know, this is what you''re paying for.","index":498,"end_time":2315.29,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2303.17,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"You''re paying for this seamless end to end, you know, press run to show.","index":499,"end_time":2321.7,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2315.29,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"What makes it smart.","index":500,"end_time":2322.66,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2321.7,"speaker_name":"Nina Belina"},{"text":"Yeah, yeah, exactly.","index":501,"end_time":2325.54,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2323.46,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Exactly.","index":502,"end_time":2326.82,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2326.1,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Yeah, yeah, absolutely.","index":503,"end_time":2329.54,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2327.38,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"And it''s, it''s funny, it''s, it''s a lot of the, like, it''s a lot of the software that''s actually running all of this stuff.","index":504,"end_time":2335.779,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2329.54,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Because without the software you wouldn''t see, you know, you wouldn''t get the data out of the scanner to tell you that, oh, this, you know, part of the press, you know, run right here.","index":505,"end_time":2344.82,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2335.779,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Let''s say where the red is, is bad quality, you know, is bad pages.","index":506,"end_time":2347.9,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2344.82,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"They have a quality issue with them.","index":507,"end_time":2349.54,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2347.9,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"So that''s the kind of like automation they''re talking about is like, that''s not something like when I first started in the industry, the only way you could tell if there was a quality issue as a page was by doing like looking at literally every single page of a press run visually.","index":508,"end_time":2369.1,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2350.86,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"And now we have scanners that can do that for you.","index":509,"end_time":2372.38,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2369.5,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"So that means, you know, you''re getting a press run through with better quality.","index":510,"end_time":2377.03,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2372.38,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"And if there is a problem, then the system is going to tell you there''s a problem between Pages, you know, 2,020, 25.","index":511,"end_time":2385.63,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2377.59,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"There is, like a bad quality.","index":512,"end_time":2387.03,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2385.63,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"You need to look at that as opposed to having to look at 25,000 pages of whatever.","index":513,"end_time":2391.03,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2387.03,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Yeah, yeah.","index":514,"end_time":2393.51,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2392.23,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"So that''s.","index":515,"end_time":2394.67,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2393.91,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":516,"end_time":2395.11,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2394.67,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"So anyway, I''m glad I brought it up because I''d kind of forgotten about it, to be honest.","index":517,"end_time":2399.59,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2395.11,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"It''s just so much going on, but it will be coming your way.","index":518,"end_time":2403.23,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2399.67,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"So maybe, like I said, start thinking about what this could look like.","index":519,"end_time":2406.63,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2403.23,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Some samples would be good.","index":520,"end_time":2408.39,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2406.87,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Little, you know, it doesn''t need to be crazy.","index":521,"end_time":2410.75,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2409.19,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"It can be anything.","index":522,"end_time":2411.43,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2410.75,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Online links are fine.","index":523,"end_time":2413.15,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2411.43,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"It doesn''t need to be, like a made sample.","index":524,"end_time":2415.11,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2413.15,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"But it would be good to, you know, understand the, like, what we can and can''t do as well to set the expectation with the group.","index":525,"end_time":2424.23,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2415.51,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Yeah, Cool.","index":526,"end_time":2427.43,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2424.23,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Okay.","index":527,"end_time":2428.29,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2427.97,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":528,"end_time":2428.69,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2428.29,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Okay.","index":529,"end_time":2433.33,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2432.77,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Yeah, I think that''s it for now.","index":530,"end_time":2435.49,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2433.33,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Just when I thought I had nothing to talk to you guys about, I remembered this.","index":531,"end_time":2439.97,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2436.77,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":532,"end_time":2444.05,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2443.569,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":533,"end_time":2444.97,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2444.61,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Okay, so we''ll come back to you with.","index":534,"end_time":2446.49,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2444.97,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"With samples.","index":535,"end_time":2447.49,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2446.49,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"Yeah, sure.","index":536,"end_time":2449.57,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2448.77,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Yeah, that sounds good.","index":537,"end_time":2450.93,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2449.73,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"And if you.","index":538,"end_time":2451.57,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2450.93,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Even if you just go online, you''re like, okay, here''s some AI samples of.","index":539,"end_time":2454.73,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2451.65,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Of this or that or the next thing.","index":540,"end_time":2456.29,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2454.73,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"That would be helpful.","index":541,"end_time":2457.25,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2456.29,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"You know, I think that might be helpful as well, because you do bring up a good point.","index":542,"end_time":2461.3,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2457.62,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"The AI on that IPM intro, I know it''s only like a split second where you see it, but I know we had to kind of work through some challenges with that particular image because it was so fussy with all the little people and the lines and all the rest of it.","index":543,"end_time":2475.78,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2461.3,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"So.","index":544,"end_time":2476.34,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2475.94,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Yeah, yeah.","index":545,"end_time":2478.26,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2476.34,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"So if they''ve got some creative ideas, totally open.","index":546,"end_time":2481.3,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2478.34,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"But the challenge is going to be showing all of this stuff that can''t be shown, like trying to show WI fi, you know, like, how do you do that?","index":547,"end_time":2489.77,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2482.18,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"How to show Bluetooth?","index":548,"end_time":2492.25,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2490.81,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"Yeah, no, exactly.","index":549,"end_time":2493.93,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2492.57,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"That''s kind of it.","index":550,"end_time":2495.13,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2494.17,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":551,"end_time":2495.77,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2495.21,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"How do you show the thing that''s invisible kind of, you know.","index":552,"end_time":2499.13,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2495.77,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":553,"end_time":2500.81,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2500.33,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Which is where the AI Ninjas thing came into play.","index":554,"end_time":2503.77,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2501.21,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"I know exactly how that came up.","index":555,"end_time":2505.85,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2503.77,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"I know exactly how they came up with that.","index":556,"end_time":2507.73,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2505.93,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"And I''m like, oh, dear.","index":557,"end_time":2509.61,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2507.73,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Okay.","index":558,"end_time":2510.73,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2510.09,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Have you watched Inside Out?","index":559,"end_time":2513.46,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2512.1,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"No, I have not.","index":560,"end_time":2515.62,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2514.5,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Should I?","index":561,"end_time":2516.34,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2515.7,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Yeah, it kind of reminds me of that.","index":562,"end_time":2518.9,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2517.14,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"It''s like little people living inside your head.","index":563,"end_time":2521.06,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2518.9,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"Oh, the cartoon.","index":564,"end_time":2523.86,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2522.66,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Yes, I have seen it.","index":565,"end_time":2525.66,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2524.18,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Yes.","index":566,"end_time":2525.9,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2525.66,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"The emotions.","index":567,"end_time":2526.66,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2525.9,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Yes, yes, yes, yes.","index":568,"end_time":2530.3,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2526.74,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"That''s exactly it, actually.","index":569,"end_time":2532.1,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2530.3,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Well, and they went down the road of ninjas, because I think ninjas are very Japanese and we''re a Japanese company.","index":570,"end_time":2539.94,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2534.1,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"So that''s where that.","index":571,"end_time":2541.86,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2540.5,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"I''m like, I think that''s where that played in.","index":572,"end_time":2545.05,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2542.77,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Right.","index":573,"end_time":2545.41,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2545.05,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"So I kind of get where they, how they got to that.","index":574,"end_time":2548.81,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2545.57,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Which I find, you know, it makes me smile.","index":575,"end_time":2551.25,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2548.81,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"It made me smile reading that.","index":576,"end_time":2552.41,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2551.25,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"I''m like, wait, what?","index":577,"end_time":2553.41,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2552.41,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"AI ninjas?","index":578,"end_time":2554.81,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2553.73,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"What?","index":579,"end_time":2555.17,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2554.81,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"But that''s what they''re trying to show.","index":580,"end_time":2557.49,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2556.05,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"They''re trying to show, you know, all that stuff that''s happening in the background.","index":581,"end_time":2561.65,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2557.49,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Yeah, the inside out.","index":582,"end_time":2562.69,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2561.65,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"The inside out of printing.","index":583,"end_time":2564.77,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2563.25,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Yeah, kinda.","index":584,"end_time":2567.57,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2565.49,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":585,"end_time":2568.36,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2568.04,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Yeah, I like that movie.","index":586,"end_time":2572.16,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2570.12,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"I thought it was so cute.","index":587,"end_time":2573.48,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2572.16,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"It''s really good.","index":588,"end_time":2574.96,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2574.04,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"And a second one came out too.","index":589,"end_time":2576.76,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2574.96,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"Yeah, you''re right, it did.","index":590,"end_time":2579.12,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2577.48,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"I, I can''t remember if I saw the second one or not, but I definitely saw the first one and apparently I seem to remember reading later that a lot of like psychiatrists, psychologists actually use that movie with kids to help them sort through.","index":591,"end_time":2594.69,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2579.12,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Like, are you feeling this?","index":592,"end_time":2596.69,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2595.09,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Are you feeling that?","index":593,"end_time":2597.69,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2596.69,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"You know, like, which, which, which little person are you, you know, are you sad?","index":594,"end_time":2602.01,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2597.69,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Are you happy?","index":595,"end_time":2602.85,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2602.01,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Are you angry?","index":596,"end_time":2603.69,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2602.85,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"You know, like, which little, you know, cartoon character are you feeling?","index":597,"end_time":2607.81,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2603.69,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Like, I seem to recall reading that and I was like, oh, that''s kind of brilliant, actually.","index":598,"end_time":2611.33,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2607.81,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":599,"end_time":2613.33,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2612.85,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":600,"end_time":2614.21,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2613.73,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"He is an adult too.","index":601,"end_time":2615.73,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2614.45,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"I know, right?","index":602,"end_time":2617.41,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2616.45,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":603,"end_time":2618.05,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2617.49,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Well, I have to, I have to hand it to animators and the cartoonists and animators and people of that elk because I gotta tell you, when Shrek came out, I was blown away.","index":604,"end_time":2630.74,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2618.05,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"I thought it was the funniest thing I had ever seen.","index":605,"end_time":2634.06,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2630.74,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"And I thought it was so brilliantly done that you could take a family to it and the kids would enjoy it because, ooh, an ogre, green donkey, it''s all funny.","index":606,"end_time":2644.38,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2635.179,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"But then you''re like, wait a minute, it''s, it''s King Farquaad.","index":607,"end_time":2648.22,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2644.82,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"And you can''t tell me that that isn''t, Forgive me, fuck wad.","index":608,"end_time":2652.02,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2648.22,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"You can''t tell me that that isn''t it.","index":609,"end_time":2654.18,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2652.18,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Right.","index":610,"end_time":2657.22,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2656.82,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"You can''t tell me that they didn''t, you know, and the other, like, there''s a whole bunch of other more adult jokes that run through it that I, I killed myself.","index":611,"end_time":2670.38,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2659.22,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"I thought it was the funniest, a funniest thing ever.","index":612,"end_time":2673.27,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2670.38,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"I just, I was like, it was brilliant that the writers and you know, they just did such a great job of it.","index":613,"end_time":2678.91,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2673.27,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"And, and I like that, that legacy of kind of Shrek in my mind kind of started those feature length cartoon animation type movies for me and I was just like, yeah, those guys over there, Lord Farquaad will live in infamy in my head.","index":614,"end_time":2695.47,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2678.91,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"It lives rent free.","index":615,"end_time":2696.99,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2695.87,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"It does.","index":616,"end_time":2697.84,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2697.48,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"It lives rent free.","index":617,"end_time":2698.92,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2697.84,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"But you can''t tell me that Isn''t it?","index":618,"end_time":2702.84,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2700.76,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"And apparently Lord Farquaad was.","index":619,"end_time":2705.48,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2703.08,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"They, they.","index":620,"end_time":2707,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2705.96,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Well, the, the, the running joke is that they modeled it after the, the CEO at the time of Walt Disney because he was not a, not, not a nice man.","index":621,"end_time":2717.72,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2707.08,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Oh dear.","index":622,"end_time":2719.24,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2718.36,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"Yeah, so he kind of has a look of that.","index":623,"end_time":2723.25,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2719.56,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"I can''t remember the CEO''s name, but he looks like that.","index":624,"end_time":2726.61,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2723.41,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"What do you call it?","index":625,"end_time":2730.13,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2729.41,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"He looks like that.","index":626,"end_time":2731.09,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2730.13,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"CEO.","index":627,"end_time":2731.81,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2731.09,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"That''s funny.","index":628,"end_time":2734.21,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2733.33,"speaker_name":"Nina Belina"},{"text":"Oh yeah, it''s, it''s like a thing.","index":629,"end_time":2736.93,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2734.45,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"It was just, Yeah, I just thought it was so funny.","index":630,"end_time":2740.61,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2737.01,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"And Mike Myers I love at the best of times.","index":631,"end_time":2743.09,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2740.61,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"So him as the, as Shrek just.","index":632,"end_time":2745.65,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2743.17,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":633,"end_time":2746.29,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2745.81,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Sent me over the edge.","index":634,"end_time":2747.69,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2746.77,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"I thought it was hysterical because it was DreamWorks, like DreamWorks Animation.","index":635,"end_time":2754.51,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2747.69,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"They''ve since been bought.","index":636,"end_time":2755.59,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2754.51,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"But at the time it was kind of like a startup.","index":637,"end_time":2759.27,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2755.59,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Like it was a bunch of people from Disney that were sort of disenfranchised, if you will.","index":638,"end_time":2763.99,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2759.51,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"And they, they started DreamWorks and I think one of their first ones was Shrek.","index":639,"end_time":2769.83,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2764.31,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":640,"end_time":2771.03,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2770.55,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"And Pixar.","index":641,"end_time":2773.71,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2772.87,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"That was the other one.","index":642,"end_time":2774.55,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2773.71,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"They were, they were direct competition with Pixar.","index":643,"end_time":2777.03,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2774.55,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"So I think they started at the same time.","index":644,"end_time":2781.93,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2779.37,"speaker_name":"Nina Belina"},{"text":"Yeah, they did.","index":645,"end_time":2783.33,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2782.49,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"More or less.","index":646,"end_time":2784.09,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2783.33,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":647,"end_time":2784.49,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2784.09,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"About the same time.","index":648,"end_time":2785.61,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2784.49,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":649,"end_time":2786.09,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2785.61,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":650,"end_time":2787.77,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2787.21,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"So yeah, yeah.","index":651,"end_time":2792.69,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2788.01,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Anyway, so yeah, it lives rent free.","index":652,"end_time":2795.45,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2792.69,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Shrek, Lord Farquaad.","index":653,"end_time":2798.41,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2795.45,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Do you think he''s compensating for something?","index":654,"end_time":2804.09,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2801.93,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"I died.","index":655,"end_time":2805.05,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2804.33,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"I didn''t.","index":656,"end_time":2805.77,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2805.13,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"It still makes me laugh.","index":657,"end_time":2807.13,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2805.85,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"They''re actually so many adult themes in those movies.","index":658,"end_time":2814.56,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2811.92,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"They really are.","index":659,"end_time":2816,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2815.12,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Like go back and watch the first Shrek again with that in mind and you''ll be like, oh my God.","index":660,"end_time":2821.28,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2816,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"When they come up, when Shrek and Donkey come up to the castle and the castle''s just like this tall building.","index":661,"end_time":2829.84,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2824.32,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Like it''s just a tall tower.","index":662,"end_time":2832.24,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2830.16,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"It''s very phallic.","index":663,"end_time":2833.16,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2832.24,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Right.","index":664,"end_time":2833.4,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2833.16,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"And he''s like, just think he''s compensating for something and then, and then he gets off the horse and he''s like three feet tall.","index":665,"end_time":2841.21,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2833.4,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"So funny.","index":666,"end_time":2849.05,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2848.17,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"And relatable if you look at some people.","index":667,"end_time":2853.77,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2851.13,"speaker_name":"Nina Belina"},{"text":"Yeah, my friends and I, we saw it like a few times.","index":668,"end_time":2859.77,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2855.69,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"We were laughing.","index":669,"end_time":2860.37,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2859.77,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"So we''re just like, oh.","index":670,"end_time":2861.33,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2860.37,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"We told everyone.","index":671,"end_time":2861.97,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2861.33,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"You''re like, you gotta see it.","index":672,"end_time":2863.29,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2861.97,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"We don''t want to tell you anything, but you have to see it.","index":673,"end_time":2866.04,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2863.96,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Natalie, you''re gonna go back and watch it.","index":674,"end_time":2871.88,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2869.64,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"I know you are.","index":675,"end_time":2872.56,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2871.88,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"I will actually.","index":676,"end_time":2873.56,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2872.56,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"So funny.","index":677,"end_time":2881.92,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2881.16,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Oh my God.","index":678,"end_time":2882.56,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2881.92,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"And again, Mike Myers is stand up comedian of many, many years standing.","index":679,"end_time":2887.84,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2882.56,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"And the way he delivered that entire role, I just loved him even more.","index":680,"end_time":2894.1,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2887.84,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Yeah, yeah, yeah.","index":681,"end_time":2896.9,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2895.54,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Who is Donkey?","index":682,"end_time":2898.26,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2897.22,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"Is it Chris?","index":683,"end_time":2899.14,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2898.26,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"Oh, It.","index":684,"end_time":2900.02,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2899.38,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"No, Donkey was Eddie.","index":685,"end_time":2902.26,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2900.58,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":686,"end_time":2903.22,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2902.74,"speaker_name":"Nina Belina"},{"text":"Oh, Eddie Murphy.","index":687,"end_time":2904.34,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2903.22,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":688,"end_time":2904.82,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2904.34,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":689,"end_time":2905.7,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2905.3,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"So we have.","index":690,"end_time":2906.42,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2905.7,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"So we have a, you know, a Scottish ogre, and for all intents and purposes, an African American donkey.","index":691,"end_time":2914.5,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2906.74,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"I''m just like, oh, my God.","index":692,"end_time":2916.14,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2914.5,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Okay.","index":693,"end_time":2916.82,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2916.14,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"And then Prince Charming.","index":694,"end_time":2921.88,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2920.36,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Isn''t he British?","index":695,"end_time":2923,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2921.88,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"I think it''s.","index":696,"end_time":2926.2,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2925.4,"speaker_name":"Nina Belina"},{"text":"He''s Justin Timberlake.","index":697,"end_time":2927.72,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2926.28,"speaker_name":"Nina Belina"},{"text":"Yeah, I think it was Justin.","index":698,"end_time":2930.04,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2928.36,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Yeah, I think you''re right.","index":699,"end_time":2931.16,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2930.04,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":700,"end_time":2931.88,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2931.32,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Well, and I have a place in my heart for Mike Myers because he''s Canadian.","index":701,"end_time":2935.2,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2932.2,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Right.","index":702,"end_time":2935.48,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2935.2,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Like, there''s a lot of Canadian, like, comics that, you know, they do well.","index":703,"end_time":2941.08,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2935.48,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Right.","index":704,"end_time":2941.36,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2941.08,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Like, they do.","index":705,"end_time":2941.92,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2941.36,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":706,"end_time":2942.28,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2941.92,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"He''s also unproblematic.","index":707,"end_time":2943.8,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2942.28,"speaker_name":"Nina Belina"},{"text":"Like, there''s nothing negative about him.","index":708,"end_time":2946.3,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2944.06,"speaker_name":"Nina Belina"},{"text":"Yeah, he''s pretty.","index":709,"end_time":2947.82,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2946.62,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"He''s pretty chill, I think.","index":710,"end_time":2949.94,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2948.06,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Well, most Canadians, I think, tend to be.","index":711,"end_time":2952.38,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2949.94,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"But yeah.","index":712,"end_time":2954.54,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2953.9,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"No, so let me.","index":713,"end_time":2955.62,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2954.54,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Let me look.","index":714,"end_time":2956.22,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2955.62,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"So it was so the cat.","index":715,"end_time":2959.42,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2956.38,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"So Mike Myers was Shrek, Eddie Murphy was Donkey.","index":716,"end_time":2963.1,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2959.42,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"And I think Cameron Diaz was Fiona.","index":717,"end_time":2968.38,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2966.06,"speaker_name":"Nina Belina"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":718,"end_time":2968.94,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2968.46,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"And John Lithgow was Lord Farquaad, which makes it somehow even better.","index":719,"end_time":2973.42,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2968.94,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":720,"end_time":2976.71,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2976.47,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"And you''re right.","index":721,"end_time":2977.19,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2976.71,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Cameron Diaz was the princess, or whatever we''re calling her.","index":722,"end_time":2980.79,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2977.19,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":723,"end_time":2984.07,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2983.51,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"So Princess Diona.","index":724,"end_time":2988.07,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2985.35,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"And then, of course, they added more people as it.","index":725,"end_time":2992.03,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2990.07,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"I mean, Shrek just blew up.","index":726,"end_time":2993.47,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2992.03,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"I think it did, like, it did amazingly well for the.","index":727,"end_time":2997.83,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2993.47,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"For DreamWorks.","index":728,"end_time":2999.81,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2998.63,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Yeah, yeah, yeah.","index":729,"end_time":3003.48,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":3000.68,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"When it came out, I don''t think they were expecting it to go, you know, to do as well as it did, frankly.","index":730,"end_time":3011.24,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":3003.48,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"So.","index":731,"end_time":3011.8,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":3011.4,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":732,"end_time":3014.04,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":3013.56,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Yeah, I thought so.","index":733,"end_time":3016.96,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":3016.12,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"It was kind of the first of its.","index":734,"end_time":3018.48,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":3016.96,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Of its kind, really, you know, like, really getting into it.","index":735,"end_time":3021.36,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":3018.48,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"I mean, there''s.","index":736,"end_time":3022.48,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":3021.36,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"I''m not having, like, stereotypically, you know, main characters that are just like fairy tale characters.","index":737,"end_time":3029.34,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":3022.48,"speaker_name":"Nina Belina"},{"text":"Well, that''s what I found entertaining about it, was that they based them off the fairy tale characters, and then they were, like, totally, like, the opposite.","index":738,"end_time":3038.14,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":3030.06,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Like, when they go to town and all the princesses are there, like, rapunzel''s there, Snow White''s there.","index":739,"end_time":3044.86,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":3038.14,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"And, you know, unlike the.","index":740,"end_time":3046.38,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":3045.1,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"The fairy godmother, which I think she shows up in.","index":741,"end_time":3049.5,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":3046.86,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"In number two in the second Shrek.","index":742,"end_time":3051.77,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":3049.66,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Like, she''s a cow.","index":743,"end_time":3053.84,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":3052.4,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"It''s not.","index":744,"end_time":3056.68,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":3056,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"You know, she''s just so mean and evil.","index":745,"end_time":3059.68,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":3056.68,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Okay.","index":746,"end_time":3061.68,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":3061.04,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"I think he''s compensating for something.","index":747,"end_time":3068.64,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":3066.64,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Oh, it''s never gonna get old.","index":748,"end_time":3070.16,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":3068.64,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":749,"end_time":3071.84,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":3071.36,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"So the budget for Shrek was 60 million estimated, and its gross worldwide was 488 million.","index":750,"end_time":3081.69,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":3071.92,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Oh, so they made it back in spades.","index":751,"end_time":3086.41,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":3082.57,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Yeah, yeah.","index":752,"end_time":3089.61,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":3087.05,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"If we only had that budget.","index":753,"end_time":3092.25,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":3090.57,"speaker_name":"Nina Belina"},{"text":"Oh, seriously?","index":754,"end_time":3094.17,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":3092.73,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Right?","index":755,"end_time":3094.49,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":3094.17,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"60 million.","index":756,"end_time":3095.29,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":3094.49,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Well, so there you go, Natalie, in answer to your question, how much would it cost a fully animated movie.","index":757,"end_time":3101.85,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":3095.53,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"And this is back in 2001, mind you, 60 million.","index":758,"end_time":3106.01,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":3101.85,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Estimated budget for Shrek.","index":759,"end_time":3108.97,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":3106.01,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"So, yeah, to give you an idea.","index":760,"end_time":3117.21,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":3111.69,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"We can dream.","index":761,"end_time":3119.21,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":3118.17,"speaker_name":"Nina Belina"},{"text":"Yeah, indeed.","index":762,"end_time":3121.049,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":3119.61,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"So you''re in an inside out one.","index":763,"end_time":3125.53,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":3121.13,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Let''s see, does it.","index":764,"end_time":3126.93,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":3126.01,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Will it tell me?","index":765,"end_time":3127.65,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":3126.93,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Oh, it won''t tell me.","index":766,"end_time":3128.73,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":3127.65,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"No, there''s no budget on that one.","index":767,"end_time":3132.46,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":3130.7,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Sorry.","index":768,"end_time":3133.1,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":3132.54,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"It won''t tell me.","index":769,"end_time":3136.46,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":3135.5,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Oh, interesting.","index":770,"end_time":3137.5,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":3136.46,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":771,"end_time":3142.86,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":3142.38,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Inside out.","index":772,"end_time":3144.54,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":3143.66,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Anyway, if Shrek was 60 million, I can only imagine it''s gone up from there, so.","index":773,"end_time":3149.9,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":3145.34,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":774,"end_time":3151.1,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":3150.62,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":775,"end_time":3152.14,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":3151.58,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"All right, well, if there''s any questions, Natalia, about this, please let me know.","index":776,"end_time":3155.78,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":3152.22,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"I. Hopefully that just gives you at least a little jumping off point to start to maybe do a bit of research in those samples and all the rest of it.","index":777,"end_time":3162.27,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":3155.78,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Yeah, yeah.","index":778,"end_time":3163.83,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":3162.83,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"If there''s anything else, let me know.","index":779,"end_time":3165.55,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":3163.83,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"And then, of course, like I said, the brief will be forthcoming, but I just wanted to give you guys a bit of a heads up about it and start thinking about it and.","index":780,"end_time":3173.95,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":3166.99,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Because it is coming.","index":781,"end_time":3174.99,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":3174.03,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Okay, sounds good.","index":782,"end_time":3177.79,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":3176.03,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Okay.","index":783,"end_time":3178.75,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":3178.19,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"And then you said I should cancel next week''s meeting, right?","index":784,"end_time":3183.31,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":3179.71,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":785,"end_time":3184.42,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":3184.02,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"I will be in Denver and I think I''ll be running around like a chicken with my head chopped off, quite frankly.","index":786,"end_time":3189.78,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":3184.5,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"I mean, if there''s anything and you need me.","index":787,"end_time":3192.42,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":3189.86,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Yeah, by all means, please, like, you know, don''t hesitate, like, email me.","index":788,"end_time":3196.9,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":3192.42,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"It just.","index":789,"end_time":3197.46,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":3196.98,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"I may not be quite as.","index":790,"end_time":3198.66,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":3197.46,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"What''s the word I''m looking for?","index":791,"end_time":3200.5,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":3199.379,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"I may not be quite as like, reactive as I normally would be because I''ll be at.","index":792,"end_time":3206.5,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":3200.5,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"In actual meetings.","index":793,"end_time":3207.78,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":3206.5,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"So.","index":794,"end_time":3208.26,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":3207.86,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":795,"end_time":3209.46,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":3208.98,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":796,"end_time":3210.51,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":3210.19,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"So if you can maybe make it tentative or, I don''t know, you can get rid of it completely.","index":797,"end_time":3218.19,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":3210.83,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"I mean, you know where I am.","index":798,"end_time":3219.27,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":3218.19,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"So if you need any, just email me or whatever if you need something and we can go from there.","index":799,"end_time":3223.39,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":3219.27,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Yeah, sure.","index":800,"end_time":3224.83,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":3224.11,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"And I will.","index":801,"end_time":3225.63,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":3224.91,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"I will actually be off the week after.","index":802,"end_time":3228.27,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":3226.19,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"Okay.","index":803,"end_time":3229.47,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":3228.91,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"So.","index":804,"end_time":3230.59,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":3230.19,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Okay.","index":805,"end_time":3231.27,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":3230.91,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"I mean, I''ll.","index":806,"end_time":3231.87,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":3231.27,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"I''ll continue to deliver things via email and then we''ll see if maybe the week after you want to meet a few days earlier than Thursday to catch up.","index":807,"end_time":3240.5,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":3231.87,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"Okay, yeah, let''s.","index":808,"end_time":3242.18,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":3240.9,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Yeah, let''s see where we get to.","index":809,"end_time":3244.26,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":3242.66,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Because I''ll be doing catch up from a.","index":810,"end_time":3247.94,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":3244.26,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Like a. I''ll be in the office, but not in my office, you know, and I''ll be traveling Monday and Thursday night and all the rest of it.","index":811,"end_time":3255.66,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":3248.26,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"So I know I''ll be doing a bunch of catch up the following week, so that''s fine.","index":812,"end_time":3260.66,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":3255.66,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"And while I''m thinking about it, since you mentioned it, for the most of April, I will be gone I''m going to Australia, so.","index":813,"end_time":3271.98,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":3260.98,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Yeah, it''s a combination of my husband''s annual work trip and I''m going to visit with family as well while I''m there, so.","index":814,"end_time":3282.22,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":3273.02,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Nice.","index":815,"end_time":3283.82,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":3283.34,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":816,"end_time":3284.78,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":3284.3,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"So will you be working or month?","index":817,"end_time":3287.1,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":3284.78,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"No, I absolutely will not be working.","index":818,"end_time":3289.82,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":3287.1,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"So I leave.","index":819,"end_time":3291.58,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":3290.22,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":820,"end_time":3293.29,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":3293.09,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"So I''ll be out from like the 9th until the 30th.","index":821,"end_time":3299.57,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":3293.29,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Okay.","index":822,"end_time":3301.41,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":3300.85,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"So a good like two and a half weeks.","index":823,"end_time":3305.65,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":3301.57,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Ish.","index":824,"end_time":3306.13,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":3305.65,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"I say that only because I lose an entire day in a plane.","index":825,"end_time":3311.49,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":3307.97,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"So.","index":826,"end_time":3312.13,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":3311.73,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":827,"end_time":3316.13,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":3315.65,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"So anyways, more to come, but just so you''ve got it on your calendar, I''m just trying to get a bunch of things done sooner rather than later.","index":828,"end_time":3324.42,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":3316.37,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":829,"end_time":3326.98,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":3326.42,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"So anyway, just so you guys are aware about that as well, and I hope you''re going somewhere lovely, Natalie.","index":830,"end_time":3333.38,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":3327.46,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Yeah, I''m going to Thailand for a week.","index":831,"end_time":3336.82,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":3334.18,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"Oh, good for you.","index":832,"end_time":3338.74,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":3337.3,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Lovely.","index":833,"end_time":3340.1,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":3339.46,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Very fun.","index":834,"end_time":3341.38,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":3340.66,"speaker_name":"Nina Belina"},{"text":"A week, though.","index":835,"end_time":3343.14,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":3342.34,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"That''s a long way to go for a week.","index":836,"end_time":3345.54,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":3343.14,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Well, I''m so I''m in Hong Kong right now, so.","index":837,"end_time":3349.32,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":3346.26,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"Oh, you are?","index":838,"end_time":3349.92,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":3349.32,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"A couple hours.","index":839,"end_time":3350.64,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":3349.92,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"Oh, well, yeah, yeah.","index":840,"end_time":3352.84,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":3350.96,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Oh, well, okay.","index":841,"end_time":3354.28,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":3352.84,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"I don''t feel bad From Chicago.","index":842,"end_time":3355.92,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":3354.28,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"I don''t feel bad for you at all then.","index":843,"end_time":3359.6,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":3357.52,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":844,"end_time":3362.72,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":3362.24,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Oh, I''m in Hong Kong.","index":845,"end_time":3364.839,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":3363.6,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Oh, okay.","index":846,"end_time":3365.6,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":3364.839,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Yeah, that would be a long way to go.","index":847,"end_time":3370.8,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":3368.96,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"I was just gonna say I''m like, wow, from Chicago.","index":848,"end_time":3373.68,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":3371.2,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"That''s a really, like, good for you, but that''s a long way to go.","index":849,"end_time":3376.48,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":3373.68,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":850,"end_time":3377.5,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":3377.26,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Okay.","index":851,"end_time":3377.86,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":3377.5,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"No, I. Hong Kong makes way more sense now.","index":852,"end_time":3381.78,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":3377.86,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Like.","index":853,"end_time":3382.06,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":3381.78,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Okay.","index":854,"end_time":3382.62,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":3382.06,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Oh, dear.","index":855,"end_time":3386.22,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":3385.34,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"What time is it then for you this time?","index":856,"end_time":3388.74,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":3386.7,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Must be icky.","index":857,"end_time":3390.46,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":3388.74,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Yeah, it is 2:00am oh, good Lord.","index":858,"end_time":3393.98,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":3390.46,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Okay.","index":859,"end_time":3394.78,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":3394.22,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"I had no idea you were in Hong Kong, so.","index":860,"end_time":3398.9,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":3396.46,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":861,"end_time":3399.3,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":3398.9,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"All right, well, you''re very.","index":862,"end_time":3400.38,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":3399.3,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"You''re very sprightly for 2am yeah, you''re already fresh.","index":863,"end_time":3404.16,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":3400.54,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Oh, dear.","index":864,"end_time":3407.84,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":3407.12,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Okay, well, then I will let.","index":865,"end_time":3409.8,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":3408.4,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"I will let you ladies go.","index":866,"end_time":3411,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":3409.8,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Thank you so much.","index":867,"end_time":3412,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":3411,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Emails, if you need me.","index":868,"end_time":3414.24,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":3412.8,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"I''m happy to try and keep the call next week if we can.","index":869,"end_time":3418.72,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":3414.48,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"I just, you know, like we said with like the video stuff and with you being away the following week, I mean, we can try and keep it, but I just wanted to set the expectation that I will be running around and if you get sort of like a.","index":870,"end_time":3430.8,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":3419.12,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"A last minute, oh, my God, I can''t make it.","index":871,"end_time":3433.59,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":3431.83,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"You''ll know why.","index":872,"end_time":3434.15,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":3433.59,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"So maybe leave it for now and we''ll go from there.","index":873,"end_time":3436.63,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":3434.15,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Okay.","index":874,"end_time":3437.67,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":3437.19,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"We''ll do.","index":875,"end_time":3438.19,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":3437.67,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"Okay.","index":876,"end_time":3438.67,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":3438.19,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"All right.","index":877,"end_time":3439.19,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":3438.67,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Very good, ladies.","index":878,"end_time":3440.27,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":3439.35,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Thank you so much and enjoy your day and we will talk soon.","index":879,"end_time":3443.99,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":3440.27,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"You too.","index":880,"end_time":3445.19,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":3444.63,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"Thanks.","index":881,"end_time":3445.59,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":3445.19,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"Take care.","index":882,"end_time":3446.63,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":3446.07,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Bye Bye.","index":883,"end_time":3447.269,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":3446.63,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Bye bye.","index":884,"end_time":3449.03,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":3447.67,"speaker_name":"Roz"}],"dateString":"2026-02-05T17:30:00.000Z","host_email":"nathalie.mintjens@marketersindemand.com","meeting_link":"https://us02web.zoom.us/j/85828735088?pwd=b9W3cDKwB