  '[{"text":"Send video briefs for IPM and RPD projects to the design team (02:50)","completed":false},{"text":"Follow up with colleague on RPD overview video script status and sales guide content shift to new template (03:50)","completed":false},{"text":"Provide current RPD sales guide version to the team promptly (04:56)","completed":false},{"text":"Coordinate with Linnea Wolken to clarify project scope and requirements for the Automation Suite video (06:30)","completed":false},{"text":"Request raw video footage of VC80000 press and workflow diagrams from the relevant internal teams (19:00)","completed":false},{"text":"Collaborate with video production team to gather and review style samples for automation workflow demonstration (20:37)","completed":false},{"text":"Communicate budget and feasibility constraints to stakeholders regarding CGI expectations (16:38)","completed":false},{"text":"Coordinate schedules and manage meetings during upcoming Denver business trip and April travel (53:00)","completed":false},{"text":"Initiate brainstorm with video experts to explore creative approaches for Automation Suite video visualization (15:40)","completed":false},{"text":"Source or create stylistic samples re-imagining previous factory automation video with different looks and feels for client review (20:37)","completed":false},{"text":"Confirm technical feasibility of client-proposed video concepts with video production team and relay feedback (36:00)","completed":false},{"text":"Manage meeting scheduling adjustments considering Roz’s and her own upcoming travel plans (53:44)","completed":false}]'::jsonb,
