e Ragno"},{"text":"And we could see what we need to update.","index":93,"end_time":339.31,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":337.55,"speaker_name":"Joe Ragno"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":94,"end_time":340.83,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":340.35,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"So I think it would be good if we went into Lovable and you just show me kind of where you''re at currently.","index":95,"end_time":345.87,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":341.39,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"And then if you could also send over screenshots just so we have them.","index":96,"end_time":348.75,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":345.87,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"But I want to, we have to, before designing the website, land on like the brand as well.","index":97,"end_time":354.99,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":349.71,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"I know you had mocked up a logo that you had shown us.","index":98,"end_time":358.03,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":355.39,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Yeah, go ahead.","index":99,"end_time":360.11,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":359.31,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"I actually kept it so much simpler and I think it works.","index":100,"end_time":364.91,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":360.11,"speaker_name":"Joe Ragno"},{"text":"Bear with me one second here while I''m logging in.","index":101,"end_time":369.11,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":366.79,"speaker_name":"Joe Ragno"},{"text":"It''s very simple, very simple.","index":102,"end_time":372.51,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":369.99,"speaker_name":"Joe Ragno"},{"text":"But I think it kind of gives the vibe of what we''re trying to do here.","index":103,"end_time":379.51,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":372.51,"speaker_name":"Joe Ragno"},{"text":"Let me share my screen.","index":104,"end_time":384.47,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":382.71,"speaker_name":"Joe Ragno"},{"text":"So it''s just this little route piece.","index":105,"end_time":393.84,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":