aker_id":1,"start_time":431.82,"speaker_name":"Joe Ragno"},{"text":"I don''t mind doing that.","index":121,"end_time":435.86,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":434.86,"speaker_name":"Joe Ragno"},{"text":"We already have that color palette, so.","index":122,"end_time":437.58,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":435.86,"speaker_name":"Joe Ragno"},{"text":"Yeah, I mean, that.","index":123,"end_time":443.14,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":442.14,"speaker_name":"Joe Ragno"},{"text":"That could.","index":124,"end_time":443.62,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":443.14,"speaker_name":"Joe Ragno"},{"text":"Maybe we do that.","index":125,"end_time":444.26,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":443.62,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Maybe we introduce this green as like a.","index":126,"end_time":445.94,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":444.26,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Just an extra color option in there.","index":127,"end_time":448.86,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":445.94,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Oh.","index":128,"end_time":449.43,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":449.27,"speaker_name":"Joe Ragno"},{"text":"I mean, I don''t care about the green.","index":129,"end_time":450.79,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":449.43,"speaker_name":"Joe Ragno"},{"text":"Yeah, I don''t care about.","index":130,"end_time":452.07,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":450.79,"speaker_name":"Joe Ragno"},{"text":"I literally don''t care about any of this.","index":131,"end_time":454.43,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":452.07,"speaker_name":"Joe Ragno"},{"text":"This was just what lovable generated.","index":132,"end_time":456.23,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":454.43,"speaker_name":"Joe Ragno"},{"text":"So is very healthcare based.","index":133,"end_time":461.19,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":456.23,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"That''s the only reason I feel like.","index":134,"end_time":462.47,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":461.27,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Is it okay?","index":135,"end_time":463.51,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":462.47,"speaker_name":"Joe Ragno"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":136,"end_time":463.99,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":463.51,"speaker_name":"Joe Ragno"},{"text":"Awesome.","index":137,"end_time":465.63,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":465.19,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Okay, so Santi, what we''ll do then is we''ll take this and create some EPS files for that logo.","index":138,"end_time":471.99,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":465.63,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"So we have like white and dark options and everything.","index":139,"end_time":474.07,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":471.99,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"And then we''ll start putting together this website.","index":140,"end_time":477.57,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":475.97,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"So yeah, go ahead and go through this, Joe.","index":141,"end_time":479.41,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":477.57,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Okay.","index":142,"end_time":480.37,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":479.81,"speaker_name":"Joe Ragno"},{"text":"And then what else are we gonna do?","index":143,"end_time":484.09,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":482.45,"speaker_name":"Joe Ragno"},{"text":"Okay, so this over the computer battery.","index":144,"end_time":487.37,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":484.09,"speaker_name":"Joe Ragno"},{"text":"Is stressing me out.","index":145,"end_time":488.21,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":487.37,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Oh, Joe, would you mind sending us an image of the logo later?","index":146,"end_time":494.05,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":489.41,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Yeah, yeah, absolutely.","index":147,"end_time":495.81,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":494.61,"speaker_name":"Joe Ragno"},{"text":"Give me one second.","index":148,"end_time":497.01,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":496.21,"speaker_name":"Joe Ragno"},{"text":"I just had a slack come through.","index":149,"end_time":498.69,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":497.01,"speaker_name":"Joe Ragno"},{"text":"Yeah, So go and sign in.","index":150,"end_time":508.54,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":498.69,"speaker_name":"Joe Ragno"},{"text":"Say we''ll use Jim Doe.","index":151,"end_time":512.7,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":510.62,"speaker_name":"Joe Ragno"},{"text":"So this is the treatment center portal.","index":152,"end_time":520.62,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":518.62,"speaker_name":"Joe Ragno"},{"text":"They have their, you know, onboarding stuff and everything like that.","index":153,"end_time":525.46,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":522.14,"speaker_name":"Joe Ragno"},{"text":"The one thing I need to do is add in a little bit more in terms of like a setting.","index":154,"end_time":530.3,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":525.46,"speaker_name":"Joe Ragno"},{"text":"So like when we, you know, send over a patient profile, how, you know, how do you want that to be dropped?","index":155,"end_time":537.62,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":530.3,"speaker_name":"Joe Ragno"},{"text":"Do you want it to be dropped directly into your CRM?","index":156,"end_time":539.66,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":537.62,"speaker_name":"Joe Ragno"},{"text":"Do you want a PDF, like some, some settings like that?","index":157,"end_time":542.38,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":539.66,"speaker_name":"Joe Ragno"},{"text":"But then this will show up when they get referrals.","index":158,"end_time":546.78,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":542.38,"speaker_name":"Joe Ragno"},{"text":"They can list out all their different treatment centers, the levels of care that they have.","index":159,"end_time":551.9,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":547.02,"speaker_name":"Joe Ragno"},{"text":"So we go in and we edit.","index":160,"end_time":554.46,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":552.7,"speaker_name":"Joe Ragno"},{"text":"This is just the basic information for the treatment center.","index":161,"end_time":558.3,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":555.42,"speaker_name":"Joe Ragno"},{"text":"What the total bed capacity is, available capacity, what they specialize in.","index":162,"end_time":563,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":558.3,"speaker_name":"Joe Ragno"},{"text":"And then the insurances that they accept and all that kind of stuff, what levels of care they treat.","index":163,"end_time":569.48,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":565.16,"speaker_name":"Joe Ragno"},{"text":"This is a broader insurance.","index":164,"end_time":573.56,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":571.64,"speaker_name":"Joe Ragno"},{"text":"So say for example, there''s, you know, the overall company is in network with all of these, but they.","index":165,"end_time":583.08,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":573.88,"speaker_name":"Joe Ragno"},{"text":"So they would be able to just do this here and then it applies to all treatment centers.","index":166,"end_time":588.92,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":584.68,"speaker_name":"Joe Ragno"},{"text":"And then if they go to the individual treatment center, say, you know, they accept a couple more plans than at a specific location, they can go and indicate that on the, on that page.","index":167,"end_time":602.26,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":589.88,"speaker_name":"Joe Ragno"},{"text":"Then there''s a Team invite and all that kind of stuff so that they can invite people, select what level of access that they have, all that kind of stuff and then the integrations.","index":168,"end_time":613.38,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":603.06,"speaker_name":"Joe Ragno"},{"text":"So Khipu for the EMR Salesforce Best notes.","index":169,"end_time":617.74,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":613.94,"speaker_name":"Joe Ragno"},{"text":"Sunwave is another EMR CRM kind of thing.","index":170,"end_time":621.18,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":617.74,"speaker_name":"Joe Ragno"},{"text":"So that''s where we''re at on that side.","index":171,"end_time":623.9,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":621.18,"speaker_name":"Joe Ragno"},{"text":"Awesome.","index":172,"end_time":624.78,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":624.22,"speaker_name":"Joe Ragno"},{"text":"This is looking great.","index":173,"end_time":625.74,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":624.78,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"There''s still some work that needs to be done, I think, on the fine tuning of things in terms of like some preferences and some settings.","index":174,"end_time":633.22,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":627.34,"speaker_name":"Joe Ragno"},{"text":"But it''s, it''s a start.","index":175,"end_time":635.26,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":633.22,"speaker_name":"Joe Ragno"},{"text":"It''s something that''s actionable, that we can onboard people with.","index":176,"end_time":639.18,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":635.339,"speaker_name":"Joe Ragno"},{"text":"Right.","index":177,"end_time":640.06,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":639.66,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Have you ever heard of the Orenda center of Wellness or Rinda?","index":178,"end_time":646.35,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":640.7,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"No.","index":179,"end_time":646.63,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":646.35,"speaker_name":"Joe Ragno"},{"text":"Okay.","index":180,"end_time":647.35,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":646.79,"speaker_name":"Joe Ragno"},{"text":"You and I could probably dive into it more of offline, but I know when we were going through the aligned growth engine, I told you that this has a, this new business that you''re starting has a personal meaning to me.","index":181,"end_time":660.39,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":649.75,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"My brother''s getting put in there, so I was just seeing if that was on your radar at all.","index":182,"end_time":665.27,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":660.39,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Well, I''m sorry to hear that because I know that that''s a very stressful time for anybody, but glad that you.","index":183,"end_time":673.22,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":665.35,"speaker_name":"Joe Ragno"},{"text":"He''s actually at the point, you know, of getting the help.","index":184,"end_time":676.93,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":673.37,"speaker_name":"Joe Ragno"},{"text":"Some people don''t make it that far anymore.","index":185,"end_time":678.85,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":676.93,"speaker_name":"Joe Ragno"},{"text":"So.","index":186,"end_time":679.13,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":678.85,"speaker_name":"Joe Ragno"},{"text":"Yeah, unfortunately the court had to step in and back up our decision there.","index":187,"end_time":682.41,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":679.13,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"But I think it''s the best, best option.","index":188,"end_time":685.29,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":682.41,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Usually it is.","index":189,"end_time":686.97,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":686.01,"speaker_name":"Joe Ragno"},{"text":"Usually it is.","index":190,"end_time":688.33,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":687.45,"speaker_name":"Joe Ragno"},{"text":"Awesome.","index":191,"end_time":690.41,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":689.93,"speaker_name":"Joe Ragno"},{"text":"Okay, so.","index":192,"end_time":691.09,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":690.41,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"All right, so we have the center dashboard.","index":193,"end_time":692.89,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":691.09,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Have we built out anything else like for the quiz or.","index":194,"end_time":699.17,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":693.93,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Not the quiz, the intake forms that they need to fill out, things like that.","index":195,"end_time":701.93,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":699.17,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"So I haven''t dove that deep into that.","index":196,"end_time":706.33,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":702.65,"speaker_name":"Joe Ragno"},{"text":"I have the questions and everything that I want to add, but I haven''t added like the pre admission assessment to it just yet.","index":197,"end_time":715.85,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":706.73,"speaker_name":"Joe Ragno"},{"text":"Just because I. I''m trying to make sure that the questions that I ask don''t have, they''re not redundant because that''s the problem with a lot of the treatment centers is they''ll ask the same question like two or three different times thinking it''s different, and then we''re seeing.","index":198,"end_time":729.98,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":716.65,"speaker_name":"Joe Ragno"},{"text":"If they''re lying, I guess.","index":199,"end_time":731.46,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":729.98,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Right.","index":200,"end_time":731.78,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":731.46,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"I mean, it could be.","index":201,"end_time":732.94,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":731.94,"speaker_name":"Joe Ragno"},{"text":"But whenever I''ve gone and turned around and been like, hey, this question kind of answers this other thing.","index":202,"end_time":738.66,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":732.94,"speaker_name":"Joe Ragno"},{"text":"Usually they''re like, oh, yeah, you''re right, you know, let''s get that one out of here because we don''t want to piss people off.","index":203,"end_time":743.06,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":738.66,"speaker_name":"Joe Ragno"},{"text":"Which I understand.","index":204,"end_time":743.78,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":743.06,"speaker_name":"Joe Ragno"},{"text":"But yeah.","index":205,"end_time":745.62,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":743.86,"speaker_name":"Joe Ragno"},{"text":"So let me see if I can.","index":206,"end_time":748.06,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":745.62,"speaker_name":"Joe Ragno"},{"text":"Show you the patient side.","index":207,"end_time":750.42,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":748.06,"speaker_name":"Joe Ragno"},{"text":"What was the user on the patient side.","index":208,"end_time":758.12,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":752.82,"speaker_name":"Joe Ragno"},{"text":"So we had our Jim Doe, John.","index":209,"end_time":760.28,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":758.12,"speaker_name":"Joe Ragno"},{"text":"Smith, very creative naming here.","index":210,"end_time":763.36,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":760.28,"speaker_name":"Joe Ragno"},{"text":"You know, hey, they''re, they''re working out of Gotham City, Florida.","index":211,"end_time":766.76,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":763.36,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Exactly.","index":212,"end_time":767.64,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":766.92,"speaker_name":"Joe Ragno"},{"text":"Coming up with the BS placeholder stuff is kind of like for developers it''s such like a nice, just little thing to do.","index":213,"end_time":776.12,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":769.799,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"So this is some of the stuff that they had put in.","index":214,"end_time":781.07,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":776.6,"speaker_name":"Joe Ragno"},{"text":"Obviously this is not a full assessment or anything like that insurance.","index":215,"end_time":786.43,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":781.39,"speaker_name":"Joe Ragno"},{"text":"So this, this is good to go.","index":216,"end_time":788.39,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":786.43,"speaker_name":"Joe Ragno"},{"text":"You know, you can go in, input all your insurance information, all that kind of stuff.","index":217,"end_time":791.95,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":788.39,"speaker_name":"Joe Ragno"},{"text":"Right.","index":218,"end_time":792.35,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":791.95,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"And then once all these other things are done, then you can find a center and all that kind of stuff.","index":219,"end_time":798.43,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":792.59,"speaker_name":"Joe Ragno"},{"text":"You know, obviously there needs to be some more settings and things in here and this is just from the web portal perspective, as you know, we had talked about initially.","index":220,"end_time":810.39,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":799.23,"speaker_name":"Joe Ragno"},{"text":"One of the things that I''m really focused on that I think is going to make users feel a lot more comfortable using something like this is the mobile app.","index":221,"end_time":818.15,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":810.39,"speaker_name":"Joe Ragno"},{"text":"Right.","index":222,"end_time":818.55,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":818.15,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Because then they''ll be able to, they''ll be in charge of their own data.","index":223,"end_time":822.23,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":818.55,"speaker_name":"Joe Ragno"},{"text":"You know, we''ll be, we''ll have some, I guess, liability in terms of like making sure that our encryption on the app is good and everything like that.","index":224,"end_time":831.23,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":822.23,"speaker_name":"Joe Ragno"},{"text":"So all their data at rest is, is as safe as it can be.","index":225,"end_time":834.87,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":831.23,"speaker_name":"Joe Ragno"},{"text":"But, but that is something that, from my understanding at least it''s a reason why a lot of people don''t utilize mental health and substance abuse resources when it comes to EAP programs is they want that they don''t want their employer to find out about this type of stuff.","index":226,"end_time":853.91,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":836.23,"speaker_name":"Joe Ragno"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":227,"end_time":854.39,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":853.91,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"And just ease of use of like a platform or a website or something like that.","index":228,"end_time":857.91,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":854.39,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Yeah, yeah, for sure.","index":229,"end_time":859.99,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":858.23,"speaker_name":"Joe Ragno"},{"text":"But that''s like a major deterrent for them.","index":230,"end_time":863.39,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":860.39,"speaker_name":"Joe Ragno"},{"text":"So I wanted to make sure that, you know, we do, we obviously we have to have something here, but I.","index":231,"end_time":870.13,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":863.39,"speaker_name":"Joe Ragno"},{"text":"Once we kind of get the UI and everything updated in here, then I was going to use that to go ahead and finish up the mobile app.","index":232,"end_time":883.25,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":870.77,"speaker_name":"Joe Ragno"},{"text":"Yep, that makes sense.","index":233,"end_time":884.69,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":883.25,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"So it feels like we''re gonna have to.","index":234,"end_time":887.41,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":885.09,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"I don''t know if we''re gonna need like a shared lovable instance or really the infrastructure set up because I, I know we had planned on us setting up a Supabase database so we could have like a CMS functionality that just ties into lovable, but since you''re going to be working on the back end, we''re probably going to have to have some sort of combined environment.","index":235,"end_time":906.19,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":888.05,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Yeah, I mean, I can probably add you guys as usual.","index":236,"end_time":909.11,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":906.75,"speaker_name":"Joe Ragno"},{"text":"I don''t think it, I think it''s Just a matter of, you know, paying.","index":237,"end_time":913.55,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":909.11,"speaker_name":"Joe Ragno"},{"text":"In terms of credit utilization, I don''t think there''s anything really there in terms of, like, user access.","index":238,"end_time":919.6,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":913.55,"speaker_name":"Joe Ragno"},{"text":"Correct.","index":239,"end_time":920.2,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":919.76,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":240,"end_time":920.56,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":920.2,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"It''s all credit based, so.","index":241,"end_time":921.72,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":920.56,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Okay, perfect.","index":242,"end_time":922.48,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":921.72,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"And then they have this, the Supabay.","index":243,"end_time":927.24,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":924.88,"speaker_name":"Joe Ragno"},{"text":"Like this is all based on Supabase and all that kind of stuff.","index":244,"end_time":930.12,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":927.24,"speaker_name":"Joe Ragno"},{"text":"So I just plan on utilizing this until it becomes a thing where.","index":245,"end_time":936.88,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":930.12,"speaker_name":"Joe Ragno"},{"text":"Because the one thing I don''t think that they have is HIPAA compliance.","index":246,"end_time":942.56,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":937.52,"speaker_name":"Joe Ragno"},{"text":"I don''t know that Supabases or not Supabase, I know Supabase is HIPAA compliant at a thousand dollars a month, but I don''t know that Lovable shares that same compliance.","index":247,"end_time":954.05,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":942.72,"speaker_name":"Joe Ragno"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":248,"end_time":955.89,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":955.49,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"So we may have to explore it.","index":249,"end_time":957.33,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":955.89,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"So, you know, there''s like, Manus, there''s.","index":250,"end_time":959.49,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":957.33,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"I''m not a big fan of cursor so far, I think.","index":251,"end_time":962.29,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":960.13,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Have you used cursor?","index":252,"end_time":963.33,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":962.29,"speaker_name":"Joe Ragno"},{"text":"I love cursor, but I love cursor for Salesforce Development.","index":253,"end_time":967.41,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":963.57,"speaker_name":"Joe Ragno"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":254,"end_time":968.13,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":967.65,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"When it comes to its limitations in other ways.","index":255,"end_time":970.85,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":968.13,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":256,"end_time":971.77,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":971.25,"speaker_name":"Joe Ragno"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":257,"end_time":972.17,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":971.77,"speaker_name":"Joe Ragno"},{"text":"And I think a lot of the limitations, at least what I''ve run into, usually we can get around with, you know, the appropriate MCP server.","index":258,"end_time":982.81,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":972.17,"speaker_name":"Joe Ragno"},{"text":"Right.","index":259,"end_time":983.21,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":982.81,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"But yeah, for Salesforce Development, it''s great.","index":260,"end_time":986.49,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":984.41,"speaker_name":"Joe Ragno"},{"text":"I get stuff done so fast.","index":261,"end_time":988.01,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":986.49,"speaker_name":"Joe Ragno"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":262,"end_time":988.49,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":988.01,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Awesome.","index":263,"end_time":989.25,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":988.73,"speaker_name":"Joe Ragno"},{"text":"Okay.","index":264,"end_time":989.61,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":989.25,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"So we''ll just have to explore some options there.","index":265,"end_time":991.21,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":989.61,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"But that all sounds good, but I''m not.","index":266,"end_time":993.89,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":991.21,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"I mean, I''m not married to it.","index":267,"end_time":995.29,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":993.89,"speaker_name":"Joe Ragno"},{"text":"I think it''s just more about the overall, you know, what.","index":268,"end_time":1000.01,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":995.85,"speaker_name":"Joe Ragno"},{"text":"What we''re trying to accomplish.","index":269,"end_time":1002.33,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1000.97,"speaker_name":"Joe Ragno"},{"text":"Yeah, absolutely.","index":270,"end_time":1003.53,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1002.41,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Awesome.","index":271,"end_time":1004.8,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1004.48,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Any other new conversations with any treatment centers or anything?","index":272,"end_time":1008.24,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1004.8,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"No, but I did get added to a group on LinkedIn.","index":273,"end_time":1013.76,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1008.72,"speaker_name":"Joe Ragno"},{"text":"Okay.","index":274,"end_time":1014.48,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1013.92,"speaker_name":"Joe Ragno"},{"text":"Called the Real.","index":275,"end_time":1015.44,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1014.48,"speaker_name":"Joe Ragno"},{"text":"And their thing is all they.","index":276,"end_time":1018.8,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1016.16,"speaker_name":"Joe Ragno"},{"text":"They focus on men''s mental health and mental health in general.","index":277,"end_time":1021.76,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1018.8,"speaker_name":"Joe Ragno"},{"text":"So I''ve started having meetings with some of them and some of the guys on there because a lot of them are CEOs and angel investors and things like that.","index":278,"end_time":1030.699,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1023.04,"speaker_name":"Joe Ragno"},{"text":"And I''m also trying to find some HR people to kind of have the conversation.","index":279,"end_time":1037.779,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1030.699,"speaker_name":"Joe Ragno"},{"text":"And you know, I''ve been saying, like, listen, I''m not trying to sell you on anything.","index":280,"end_time":1041.059,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1037.779,"speaker_name":"Joe Ragno"},{"text":"I just want you to see what I''m doing here and tell me what about something like this would make you want to buy.","index":281,"end_time":1047.339,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1041.059,"speaker_name":"Joe Ragno"},{"text":"Right.","index":282,"end_time":1047.739,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1047.339,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Right now.","index":283,"end_time":1049.259,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1048.779,"speaker_name":"Joe Ragno"},{"text":"But this mostly just like, trying to understand the market.","index":284,"end_time":1052.059,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1049.259,"speaker_name":"Joe Ragno"},{"text":"Also love the Mandalorian Cup.","index":285,"end_time":1054.739,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1053.019,"speaker_name":"Joe Ragno"},{"text":"That''s awesome.","index":286,"end_time":1055.419,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1054.739,"speaker_name":"Joe Ragno"},{"text":"Thank you.","index":287,"end_time":1056.17,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1055.69,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"I. I can''t remember.","index":288,"end_time":1058.61,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1056.33,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"I think I got this, like a couple Christmases ago.","index":289,"end_time":1060.97,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1058.61,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"A massive mug.","index":290,"end_time":1062.81,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1061.85,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"It''s awesome.","index":291,"end_time":1063.45,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1062.81,"speaker_name":"Joe Ragno"},{"text":"Okay.","index":292,"end_time":1066.21,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1065.77,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Yeah, that all sounds great.","index":293,"end_time":1067.21,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1066.21,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"I mean, you''re doing Basically focus groups, which is awesome.","index":294,"end_time":1070.17,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1067.21,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Okay, cool.","index":295,"end_time":1071.57,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1070.89,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"So our next steps then are once you send over just some screenshots of what you have on level and the logo, we''ll start building all of that together and then put a framework and a design together for the website and then we can start moving forward with everything else.","index":296,"end_time":1085.14,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1071.57,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Would it just be easier for.","index":297,"end_time":1086.34,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1085.14,"speaker_name":"Joe Ragno"},{"text":"Do you want the screenshots or would it just be easier to give you guys user access?","index":298,"end_time":1089.82,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1086.34,"speaker_name":"Joe Ragno"},{"text":"Yeah, if you just want to invite production at Marketers In Demand as a user, that would be great.","index":299,"end_time":1094.78,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1089.9,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Let''s do that right now because that''s.","index":300,"end_time":1097.66,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1095.42,"speaker_name":"Joe Ragno"},{"text":"That should be pretty quick here.","index":301,"end_time":1100.22,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1097.98,"speaker_name":"Joe Ragno"},{"text":"Yeah, I''ve been playing around, so I do a lot of cloud code, obviously, but then I''ve been recently playing around with Cowork and that''s been kind of cool to test.","index":302,"end_time":1114.55,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1107.03,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Never heard of Cowork Claude Cowork.","index":303,"end_time":1116.87,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1114.79,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"It''s like a.","index":304,"end_time":1117.51,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1116.87,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"It''s more of a simple like AI agent just to have on your desktop.","index":305,"end_time":1122.55,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1118.15,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"You said production at Marketers in Demand.","index":306,"end_time":1125.83,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1123.11,"speaker_name":"Joe Ragno"},{"text":"Dot com.","index":307,"end_time":1130.23,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1129.51,"speaker_name":"Joe Ragno"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":308,"end_time":1130.87,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1130.39,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Okay.","index":309,"end_time":1132.55,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1131.99,"speaker_name":"Joe Ragno"},{"text":"It may be only on Mac right.","index":310,"end_time":1135.62,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1134.14,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Now, but that''s okay.","index":311,"end_time":1137.7,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1135.62,"speaker_name":"Joe Ragno"},{"text":"I pretty much run Mac.","index":312,"end_time":1138.94,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1137.7,"speaker_name":"Joe Ragno"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":313,"end_time":1139.74,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1139.18,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Across everything.","index":314,"end_time":1141.18,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1140.46,"speaker_name":"Joe Ragno"},{"text":"I, I ended up.","index":315,"end_time":1142.3,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1141.26,"speaker_name":"Joe Ragno"},{"text":"So one of the investments that I did make last year was AI training rig.","index":316,"end_time":1148.7,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1142.3,"speaker_name":"Joe Ragno"},{"text":"So I have this really nice thread Ripper Pro with 128 gigs of RAM and nice Nvidia RTX Pro.","index":317,"end_time":1157.98,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1149.02,"speaker_name":"Joe Ragno"},{"text":"Blackwell GPU is like 96 gigs of VRAM and everything.","index":318,"end_time":1162.67,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1157.98,"speaker_name":"Joe Ragno"},{"text":"So like I can actually train models because as you know, we talked about in previous calls, one of the things that I do want to do is train some models and get like a. I don''t know that Tim called it a crisis companion.","index":319,"end_time":1174.19,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1162.67,"speaker_name":"Joe Ragno"},{"text":"I think that might, the, the wording on that might be kind of more towards like a therapist kind of kind of thing.","index":320,"end_time":1181.67,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1174.19,"speaker_name":"Joe Ragno"},{"text":"I don''t want to be.","index":321,"end_time":1182.79,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1181.67,"speaker_name":"Joe Ragno"},{"text":"Have it misconstrued as that, but I think having our own proprietary models will be beneficial.","index":322,"end_time":1190.73,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1183.11,"speaker_name":"Joe Ragno"},{"text":"Yeah, definitely.","index":323,"end_time":1191.97,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1190.89,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"I just dropped the Cowork link in the chat.","index":324,"end_time":1194.97,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1191.97,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"So yeah, it looks like it''s only for Mac right now, but it''s just, it''s.","index":325,"end_time":1199.01,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1195.05,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"It''s just like a task, A task based thing that happens in the background and I think it''s going to learn over time from what I''ve understood to know like where I want documents placed, how I want language used, like things like that.","index":326,"end_time":1211.69,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1199.01,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"So it just starts automating for me in the background.","index":327,"end_time":1213.37,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1211.69,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Like an AI agent.","index":328,"end_time":1214.3,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1213.37,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Yeah, I was gonna play with.","index":329,"end_time":1216.21,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1215.17,"speaker_name":"Joe Ragno"},{"text":"And it''s changed its name so many times in like the last two weeks, but they had Claude Bot and then Molt Bot and then something else.","index":330,"end_time":1222.65,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1217.01,"speaker_name":"Joe Ragno"},{"text":"Yeah, I''m a little scared to install that, if I''m being honest.","index":331,"end_time":1225.49,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1222.65,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"So I''m not going to install it on my regular computer.","index":332,"end_time":1227.65,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1225.57,"speaker_name":"Joe Ragno"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":333,"end_time":1227.93,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1227.65,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"That''s going to get installed on a virtual machine and I will add certain things in there.","index":334,"end_time":1233.57,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1227.93,"speaker_name":"Joe Ragno"},{"text":"Like I''ll give it access to Claude code or something like that on the virtual machine.","index":335,"end_time":1239.17,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1233.57,"speaker_name":"Joe Ragno"},{"text":"Right.","index":336,"end_time":1239.57,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1239.25,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"And let it build stuff in the background and all that kind of stuff.","index":337,"end_time":1242.69,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1239.57,"speaker_name":"Joe Ragno"},{"text":"But I''m not.","index":338,"end_time":1243.81,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1242.69,"speaker_name":"Joe Ragno"},{"text":"It''s.","index":339,"end_time":1244.54,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1244.3,"speaker_name":"Joe Ragno"},{"text":"It''s not going on anything important.","index":340,"end_time":1245.9,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1244.54,"speaker_name":"Joe Ragno"},{"text":"Yeah, I. I had the same feeling when I was reading through all of that on Twitter as I did with Deep Seek.","index":341,"end_time":1251.26,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1246.14,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"It''s like, I don''t know, I feel a little sketchy about it.","index":342,"end_time":1254.14,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1251.42,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Deep Seek, I just don''t trust because it''s kind of run by the Chinese government.","index":343,"end_time":1258.7,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1254.22,"speaker_name":"Joe Ragno"},{"text":"It literally is.","index":344,"end_time":1259.74,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1258.94,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"I mean, it''s.","index":345,"end_time":1260.26,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1259.74,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"And it''s also like tick tock, where they''re just storing your information.","index":346,"end_time":1262.62,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1260.26,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Yeah, I don''t.","index":347,"end_time":1263.9,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1263.1,"speaker_name":"Joe Ragno"},{"text":"I don''t like that at all.","index":348,"end_time":1264.94,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1263.9,"speaker_name":"Joe Ragno"},{"text":"I don''t like information being stored and the Chinese government just doesn''t give a.","index":349,"end_time":1268.62,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1264.94,"speaker_name":"Joe Ragno"},{"text":"So, yeah, there''s no regulation over there for that.","index":350,"end_time":1271.65,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1269.02,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"No.","index":351,"end_time":1272.21,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1271.81,"speaker_name":"Joe Ragno"},{"text":"Awesome.","index":352,"end_time":1273.57,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1272.93,"speaker_name":"Joe Ragno"},{"text":"Okay, cool.","index":353,"end_time":1275.17,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1274.53,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"And then we can talk offline, too, about your travel plans this month and if we can meet up.","index":354,"end_time":1282.37,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1275.17,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Yeah, yeah.","index":355,"end_time":1283.33,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1282.69,"speaker_name":"Joe Ragno"},{"text":"I''ll be down there on the 21st.","index":356,"end_time":1284.77,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1283.33,"speaker_name":"Joe Ragno"},{"text":"The 21st, through, I think the 24th or 25th or something like that.","index":357,"end_time":1288.37,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1285.01,"speaker_name":"Joe Ragno"