  '[{"text":"Coordinate with Jane and branch managers to finalize and send location lists for postcard mail campaigns (05:05)","completed":false},{"text":"Sync with business team leads to define key qualifying questions for web forms that determine marketing funnel or direct sales routing for leads (19:20)","completed":false},{"text":"Discuss with Colin options for Salesforce fields to store marketing campaign flags, customer journey data, and related engagement notes for sales visibility (27:09)","completed":false},{"text":"Follow up and communicate any scheduling or project delays promptly to the team via email (40:09)","completed":false},{"text":"Continue development to implement API security for MuleSoft HTTP listener endpoint, ensuring payload encryption and validation against HubSpot standards (07:58)","completed":false},{"text":"Refactor current large MuleSoft flows into manageable modular subflows for better maintainability and debugging (07:11)","completed":false},{"text":"Define specifics of data fields and payload transformations to manage bi-directional sync and avoid duplicate records or unwanted overwrites, including immutable fields like VIS key (09:17)","completed":false},{"text":"Engage with Salesforce and HubSpot system admins to establish proper validation rules and field-level restrictions compatible between platforms (10:44)","completed":false},{"text":"Provide ongoing updates to the team on API integration progress and contribute to refining the integration process diagrams for team clarity (14:03)","completed":false},{"text":"Lead in setting up logic to create Salesforce cases for data anomalies detected during sync (12:20)","completed":false},{"text":"Assist Gabriel and the team in implementing HubSpot-side automation and validation rules, clarifying technical requirements and platform capabilities (10:52)","completed":false},{"text":"Support lead form design by suggesting multi-step HubSpot forms to incrementally collect customer info and improve lead qualification (23:52)","completed":false},{"text":"Collaborate with Christina on Salesforce campaign and customer profile field mapping to enrich sales insights from marketing data (27:09)","completed":false},{"text":"Provide expertise on duplicate detection logic within Salesforce and options for improvements in data quality and matching rules (28:25)","completed":false},{"text":"Advise on lead scoring model designs and organic growth of integrated marketing-sales workflows (39:50)","completed":false},{"text":"Assist with creation of Salesforce fields, sections, or related lists to display marketing and engagement data linked to leads and customers (37:10)","completed":false}]'::jsonb,
